NK109(dze)002:1: // yi ge med pa'i rgyud kyi 'grel ba pad+ma kha 'byed bzhugs so //
NK109(dze)002:3: pad+ma mus li na 'gu ya a k+sha ti ka na ma /
NK109(dze)002:5: pad+ma kha 'byed ces bya ba gsang ba yi ge med pa'i tika /
NK109(dze)002:6: bcom ldan 'das dpal sna tshogs tshig gi bcud sel
NK109(dze)002:7: ba'i dpa' bo rdo rje 'chang chen po grol ba
NK109(dze)002:8: rnams kyi yang grol ba'i mnga' bdag nyid la phyag
NK109(dze)002:9: 'tshal lo // dpal ldan ye shes lnga yi tshogs kyis rab rgyas pa'i /
NK109(dze)002:10: 'jig rten rnams la gzigs pa'i rang shugs mchog gi thugs rje can /
NK109(dze)002:11: rnam rtog tha dag gcod pa spu gri lta bu'i gsungs mnga' ba /
NK109(dze)002:12: 'gro drug gnas nas 'dren pa'i thugs rje'i lcags kyu'i gzung nas ni /
NK109(dze)002:13: 'khor ba'i 'ching byed brgyad las grol bar byed pa'i ston pa nyid /
NK109(dze)002:14: rdo rje 'chang chen rgyud kyi ston pa bla med yang sangs rgyas /
NK109(dze)002:15: dug gsum drung nas 'don par mdzad pa sman pa'i gtso /
NK109(dze)002:16: dri mas rnam gnyis yang dag nges bral don gnyis rdzogs mdzad pa /
NK109(dze)002:17: 'gro rnams yang dag nges pa'i sar bkod phyir na rgyud gnyis ni /
NK109(dze)002:18: nyid kyi thugs las 'khrul pa med pa'i tshig tu nges bsam ste /
NK109(dze)002:19: rdo rje'i mgur las phyung nas pad+ma'i ljags las bkrams /
NK109(dze)002:20: 'khrul par rtsad gcod ral gri lta bu'i tshig gnyis kyis /
NK109(dze)002:21: 'gro rnams yang dag sa la drang ba'i don chen nyid du yang /
NK109(dze)002:22: gdul bya tha dad rnams la 'dul byed skur sprul nas /
NK109(dze)002:23: gzhan don rdzogs par mdzad pa'i sprul pa'i rgyud 'chang ba /
NK109(dze)002:24: rdo rje 'chang ba sangs rgyas rnams kyi rje btsun nyid la yang /
NK109(dze)002:25: rab tu g.yo ba med pa'i sems kyis mos byas la /
NK109(dze)002:26: yan lag lnga yi rtsol bas phyag 'tshal rab tu bstod /
NK109(dze)002:27: de rjes 'dzin pa'i rim brgyud bla ma'i tshogs nyid las /
NK109(dze)002:28: dad gus mos pa'i rtsol bas rab tu phyag 'tshal bstod /
NK109(dze)002:29: bdag gis rnam rtog zad mdzad rang snang ston pa'i rje btsun nyid /
NK109(dze)002:30: dz+ny+aa na s+au tra dpa' bo 'khor g.yul bzlog pa'i
NK109(dze)002:31: dam pa drin can nyid la nyin mtshan thams cad
NK109(dze)002:32: du / 'bral ba med pa'i sems kyis rab tu bstod cing mchod par bgyi /
NK109(dze)002:33: de ltar drin can 'khor ba'i 'ching ba gcod pa'i mnga' bdag rnams la ni /
NK109(dze)002:34: btud nas rgyud kyi tshig rnams rim par gsal bar byed pa'i bcud 'di nyid /
NK109(dze)002:35: ma 'ongs skal ldan rnams kyi don nyid du /
NK109(dze)002:36: bdag gis 'khrul pa spang ba'i blo dang mos pas gzhan don du /
NK109(dze)002:37: 'khor srid gcod pa'i don du gsag ba'i gnad rnams dang /
NK109(dze)002:38: tshig gi rgyud rnams rim par gsal bar bkod pa'i sgron ma'i 'od /
NK109(dze)002:39: ma shes rmongs pa'i sgro 'dogs the tshom rnam bcad phyir /
NK109(dze)002:40: yang dag nges pa'i bcud 'di bstan par bya 'os sems kyi bu /
NK109(dze)002:41: rga&a&a&ananyar+g+aah de la yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK109(dze)002:42: ston pa bcom ldan 'das 'gro ba thams cad kyi
NK109(dze)002:43: bla ma / drug pa rdo rje 'chang chen po des //
NK109(dze)002:44: 'gro ba ma rig pa'i rgyas 'thus pa rnams la /
NK109(dze)002:45: thugs rje ye shes kyi snang bas lam du gzung ba'i don du /
NK109(dze)002:46: bka' phyin ci ma log pa dpag tu med pa gcig gsungs pa las /
NK109(dze)002:47: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po 'bad rtsol dang bral ba'i don /
NK109(dze)002:48: rang snang chig rdzogs su ston pa 'di ni /
NK109(dze)002:49: rang gi rig pa mngon sum du ston par byed
NK109(dze)002:50: pa'i yang 'byed sbas pa'i don rnams legs par ston
NK109(dze)002:51: par byed pas / nges pa'i snying po gsang ba rnams kyi nang nas yang gsang mchog gi rgyud /
NK109(dze)002:52: snying po man ngag bsdus pa'i bcud du 'bum phrag
NK109(dze)002:53: drug cu rtsa bzhi nas legs par btus shing phyungs
NK109(dze)002:54: te sdud pa po rang snang thabs kyi 'khor gyi
NK109(dze)002:57: sprul pa'i sku dga' rab rdo rjer dbyings kyi mkha' 'gro ma rnam pa gnyis kyis /
NK109(dze)002:58: tshig dang yi ger dkar chag la btab nas /
NK109(dze)002:59: ma 'ongs pa'i dus kyi skal ldan rang bzhin rdzogs
NK109(dze)002:60: pa chen po'i don la mos pa rnams kyi don
NK109(dze)002:61: du bkod de / bar skabs der mkha' 'gro ma
NK109(dze)002:62: rnams kyis rgyas btab te mi snang bar byas so
NK109(dze)002:63: du bkod de / // de lta bu'i bka' phyin ci ma log pa yang dag pa 'di ni /
NK109(dze)002:64: 'gro ba rnams kyi mig lta bu /
NK109(dze)002:65: ston pa nyid kyis gsungs pas ni /
NK109(dze)002:66: gsang ba yi ge med pa'i rgyud yin pa la /
NK109(dze)002:67: 'di la le'u drug gi bdag nyid du gnas pa las /
NK109(dze)002:68: gzhung gi don rdzogs pa yin no //
NK109(dze)002:69: de la mtshan bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:70: gzhung gi don pad+ma kha phye ba ltar bshad pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:72: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don 'di nyid theg
NK109(dze)002:73: pa gzhan las 'phags pa dang sbyar te bshad pa
NK109(dze)002:74: dang / thabs che ba nyid dang sbyar dang /
NK109(dze)002:75: thabs sla ba dang sbyar ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:76: thabs myur ba dang sbyar ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:77: theg pa gzhan las khyad par du 'phags pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:78: lta bas khyad par 'phags te tshig dang yi ge la mi re ba /
NK109(dze)002:79: rang bzhin gnas lugs kyi don phyin ci ma log
NK109(dze)002:80: par rtogs pas bud+d+ha bas na yi ge med ces
NK109(dze)002:81: bya'o // 'di nyid kyi gong na theg pa gzhan
NK109(dze)002:82: med thabs kyi gnad mi 'dra ba mang pos gang
NK109(dze)002:83: zag gi rgyud grol bar byed pas rgyud chen po
NK109(dze)002:84: bya'o // zhes bya'o // rin po che zhes pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:85: dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che 'chang ba'i gang zag gis /
NK109(dze)002:86: rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo la btags te mchod pa byas na /
NK109(dze)002:87: de ma thag tu dgos 'dod ci 'byung ba thogs pa med par 'byung ba dang 'dra bar /
NK109(dze)002:89: nyams su blang pas tshe gcig la sangs rgyas na /
NK109(dze)002:90: rang gzhan gyi don la thogs pa med par 'byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:92: dper na rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo dang 'dra bar /
NK109(dze)002:93: dus thams cad du nub pa med pa rig pa'i
NK109(dze)002:94: ye shes 'gyur ba med pa nyid 'bad rtsol ci
NK109(dze)002:96: 'di nyid du mngon sum du rtogs pas na /
NK109(dze)002:97: rgyal mtshan gyi rgyud ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:98: de yang lta ba'i don de tshig dang yi ge
NK109(dze)002:99: gang gis kyang gtan la mi phebs pa'i don lta
NK109(dze)002:101: rgyal po'i gdung rgyud lta ba nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud ces pas so //
NK109(dze)002:102: de lta bu'i don de bsgom pas khyad par du
NK109(dze)002:103: 'phags pa'i thabs che ba ste rgyal po lta bu'o
NK109(dze)002:104: // spyod pas khyad par du 'phags te thabs sla
NK109(dze)002:105: ba ste rig pa mngon sum du gtan la phab
NK109(dze)002:107: de nyid dang gnyis su med par spyod pas nam mkha'i mtha' dang zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:108: 'bras bu khyad par du 'phags pa'i don nyid thabs myur ba nyid de //
NK109(dze)002:109: mnyam nyid bde ba chen po la brten nas da
NK109(dze)002:110: lta nyid du thob pas na mnyam pa'i rgyud ces
NK109(dze)002:111: bya'o // nang ltar bshad pa ni rang gi lus la rtsa stong phrag mang po gnas pas /
NK109(dze)002:112: de dag gi nang na rang bzhin gyi yi ge re re gnas pas yi ge zhes bya /
NK109(dze)002:113: de yang dngos po rdzas su med de 'od kyi gong bur gnas pa'i nang na /
NK109(dze)002:114: rang bzhin gyi kun tu bzang po yab yum gnas pas /
NK109(dze)002:115: rags pa rdzas su med pas na med ces bya /
NK109(dze)002:116: de la brten nas mi rtog pa'i ye shes kyi
NK109(dze)002:117: bde ba chen po rang gi rgyud nyid la skye
NK109(dze)002:118: bas na chen po'i rgyud zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:119: de nyid la brten nas dus thams cad du nyams
NK109(dze)002:120: su blangs pas yon tan sna tshogs 'byung ste skyon
NK109(dze)002:121: las 'das te snang ba'i yon tan sna tshogs pa
NK109(dze)002:122: la spyod pas rin po che zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:123: de yang lus kyi rtse mo dbang po'i dwangs ma
NK109(dze)002:124: mig la brten nas skyes pas rgyal mtshan gyi rgyud
NK109(dze)002:125: ces bya'o // de nyid kyang thog ma nas 'gyur ba med par gnas pas rgyal po zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:126: de lta bu'i rig pa'i ye shes nyid /
NK109(dze)002:127: 'khor ba ngan song gang na gnas kyang /
NK109(dze)002:128: ngo bo la bzang ngan med par 'pho 'gyur med
NK109(dze)002:129: cing kun khyab tu gnas pas na gdung rgyud ces
NK109(dze)002:130: bya'o // de yang gtad pa dngos rig pa gtad pa'i yul nam mkha'/
NK109(dze)002:131: de ltar gtad pa'i lta ba rgyud dang gtad pa gnyis 'dres pas /
NK109(dze)002:132: mngon gsum la lta ba nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud ces pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:133: gsang ba ltar bshad pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:134: dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul de /
NK109(dze)002:136: phyogs gang du ma lhung ba /
NK109(dze)002:137: dus thams cad du rtag par bzhugs pa'i rig pa'i ye shes kyi gzhi nyid la /
NK109(dze)002:138: sgro 'dogs pas yi ge'i tshul du byung ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:139: de'ang yi ge'i mtha' ni dngos po rags pa las 'jal bar byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:140: rtsol ba'i sna khrid pa dang 'bad pa'i don mtshon pa dang 'du byed sna tshogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:141: dran bsam sna tshogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:142: gzung 'dzin gyi yul sna tshogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:143: ming sna tshogs pa'i rjes sgrub pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:144: yid dpyad kyi lta sgom spyod pa 'bras bu'i tshogs du ma dang /
NK109(dze)002:145: yin min gyi rtog pa 'dus pas na yi ge ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:146: rang gi dngos po'i 'dug tshul la /
NK109(dze)002:147: de dag rnams dang bral nas med pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:148: thugs rje'i cha sna tshogs su snang ba la zhen pa med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:150: phyogs med de gtad pa med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:151: ris med de ngos bzung med pas na yi ge med pa zhes bya'o /
NK109(dze)002:152: de'ang ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum du bzhugs pas /
NK109(dze)002:153: ngo bo'i cha nas cir yang grub pa med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:154: rang bzhin gyi cha nas rdzas su grub pa ci yang med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:155: rgyud ni dag pa dang ma dag pa gnyis so //
NK109(dze)002:156: dag pa ni rang bzhin gshis kyi rgyud dag pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:157: rten pa yul gyi rgyud dag pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:158: rang rig gom pa'i gnad kyis rgyud dag pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:159: rang bzhin gshis dag pa'i dngos po 'dug tshul gyi rgyud dag pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:160: ngo bo ka dag pa'i gzhi gang gis kyang gtan
NK109(dze)002:161: la dbab tu med cing brjod bya du ma las
NK109(dze)002:162: 'das shing / 'khrul bya ba tsam du yang /
NK109(dze)002:163: brdas gdags su yang med pa nyid la bya /
NK109(dze)002:164: rang bzhin gnas tshul la shes pas bsdus pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:167: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi rgyud kyis bsdus pas so //
NK109(dze)002:168: shes bya ni mtshon bya'i rgyud dang /
NK109(dze)002:169: mtshon byed kyi rgyud la sogs pa rnams kyi dbye ba yin no //
NK109(dze)002:170: brten pa'i yul gyi rgyud dag pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:171: byang chub sems dpa'i rgyud dang /
NK109(dze)002:172: dgra bcom pa rnams yin no //
NK109(dze)002:173: rang rig gom gnad kyis rgyud dag pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:174: bla ma'i man ngag la brten nas mngon sum gyi gnad gzir ba /
NK109(dze)002:176: snang ba dag pa rnams dang 'du 'bral med par spyod pa nyid do //
NK109(dze)002:177: mdor na nyams gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i dus la spyod pa dag pa yin no //
NK109(dze)002:178: ma dag pa ni rang bzhin lung du ma bstan pas ma dag pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:179: byas pa'i rnam smin gyi 'bras bu ma dag pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:180: phyin ci log tu gol bas rang gi rgyud ma dag pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:181: rang bzhin lung du ma bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:182: so so'i skye bo'i shes pas bsdus pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:183: dag pa phyogs ma mthong ba nyan thos la sogs pa'i shes pas bsdus pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:184: byas pa'i rnam smin la gnyis te /
NK109(dze)002:185: snga ma dang da lta'i las so //
NK109(dze)002:186: las sngar byas pa'i rnam par smin pas /
NK109(dze)002:187: dbang po ma gsal zhing shes rab zhan pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:188: shes pa mi gsal zhing brjed ngas pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:189: dri mas bcing pa ni rgyud ma dag pa sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa dang 'phrad kyang /
NK109(dze)002:190: de lta bu dang yun ring bar 'gyur te /
NK109(dze)002:191: sangs rgyas kyi sgra grags pa med pa'i tha 'khob kla klo'i yul du skyes pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:192: ngan song gsum gyis rgyud kyis bsdus pa rnams yin no //
NK109(dze)002:193: da lta byas pa'i rnam smin gyis rgyud ma dag pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:194: sa shu zhes bya ste shan pa la sogs pa sdig can rnams kyi rgyud yin no //
NK109(dze)002:195: phyin ci log gol ba ma dag pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:196: cha mthun rjes 'dzin gyi ma dag pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:197: rang gzhung 'dod pas ma dag pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:198: bla ma log bas ma dag pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:199: rang gi 'bad rtsol gyis ma dag pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:200: cha mthun rjes 'dzin gyis ma dag pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:201: sangs rgyas kyi lta ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:204: bdag dang bcas pas mngon par zhen pas phyin ci
NK109(dze)002:205: log gis rgyud ma dag par gyur pa nyid rnams
NK109(dze)002:206: te / skye mched kyi las sogs pa'i shes pas bsdus pa rnams yin no //
NK109(dze)002:207: rang gzhung 'dod pas rang gi rgyud ma dag pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:208: phyi rol mu stegs pa rnams yin no //
NK109(dze)002:209: bla ma phyin ci log gis ma dag pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:210: bslab nyes phyin log can gyi rgyud ces bya /
NK109(dze)002:211: thog mar bla ma man ngag med pa zhig gis ci thod thod bslab pas /
NK109(dze)002:212: dngos po gshis kyi don la phyin ci log tu song nas /
NK109(dze)002:213: phyis yang dag pa'i man ngag bstan kyang /
NK109(dze)002:214: de blor mi tshud pa rnams yin no //
NK109(dze)002:215: rang gi 'bad rtsol las phyin ci log tu song nas ma dag pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:216: bka' dang bla ma'i man ngag la ma bsten par
NK109(dze)002:217: rang byung du byed pa rnams lam log par 'gro
NK109(dze)002:218: bas na / phyin ci log tu song nas rang rgyud ma dag pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:219: de yang skal ldan gyis de rnams spangs pas rang gi rgyud dag pa yin no //
NK109(dze)002:220: gzhan gyi rgyud ma dag pa ni grub pa'i mthas
NK109(dze)002:221: bsdus pa'i nyan thos la sogs pa'i theg pa rim
NK109(dze)002:223: shes pas bsdus te le los rang gi rgyud ma dag pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:224: gzugs dang gzugs med pa rnams kyi rgyud las ltung byed dang gol sar 'gyur bas ma dag pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:225: de dag legs par gtan la phebs shing don mtshon pas na /
NK109(dze)002:226: chos sku nas longs skur rgyud pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:227: longs sku nas sprul pa'i skur rgyud kyi ston pa
NK109(dze)002:228: drug pa rdo rje 'chang du dag par brgyud pas
NK109(dze)002:230: de lta bu'i skyon dang bral ba'i rang rgyud rnam par dag pa la /
NK109(dze)002:231: yon tan dpag tu med pa 'phel pas yid bzhin
NK109(dze)002:232: gyi nor bu rin po che dang mtshungs pas na
NK109(dze)002:234: de lta bu'i rgyud dag pa nyid kyis 'bras bu
NK109(dze)002:235: chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba la dbang thob pas
NK109(dze)002:236: na / rgyal mtshan gyi rgyud ces pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:237: rgyud 'di ni gzhan rgyud dri ma dang bcas pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:238: grub mtha' bsdus pa'i rgyud theg pa rim pa brgyad po yin la /
NK109(dze)002:239: shes pas bsdus pa khams gsum gyi lha rnams yin pas rgyud ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:240: de lta bu'i rang rgyud dag pa des nyon mongs pa'i tshogs zil gyis gnon pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:241: de nyid la dbang bsgyur bas rgyal po'i gdung brgyud ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:242: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po ma dag pa'i rang bzhin gyi rgyud de dag las 'das te /
NK109(dze)002:243: mtshan ma min pa'i yon tan nam mkha' dang mnyam
NK109(dze)002:244: pa spel bas nas lta ba nam mkha'i mtha' dang
NK109(dze)002:246: rgyud bzhi byung ba zlos pa'i skyon ni ma yin te /
NK109(dze)002:247: phyi'i rgyud tshig la brten pas dngos po'i gnas lugs mtshon pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:248: nang gi rgyud brda' dang rten 'brel la brten pas 'byung ba'i byer zug mnyam pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:250: tshig dang yi ge rang bral ba la brten nas
NK109(dze)002:251: ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gtan la phab
NK109(dze)002:252: pa dang / yongs su rdzogs pa gsang ba bla na med pa'i rgyud rang gi rig pa /
NK109(dze)002:253: ye nas gnas pa la brten nas mngon sum du lam khyer bas rgyud ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:254: rgyud bzhir gtan la phab pa ni mtshan dngos ma yin te /
NK109(dze)002:255: mtshan gyi yon tan 'char tshul zhar byung du bstan pa'i /
NK109(dze)002:256: mtshan gsang ba bla na med pa yongs su rdzogs pa chen po dang sbyar te bshad pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:259: don 'gyur du bshad pa yin no //
NK109(dze)002:261: rtogs te sangs rgyas ma byung /
NK109(dze)002:262: ma rtogs te sems can ma byung ba'i sngon rol gyi dngos po 'dug tshul gyi gzhi la /
NK109(dze)002:263: 'khrul dang ma 'khrul bya ba'i tha snyad gang du yang med pas a yin la /
NK109(dze)002:264: de las yang ma rig pa lhan cig skyes pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:265: rgyud bdag nyid gcig pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:268: yid drug la sogs pa med par rang bzhin ye dag tu bzhugs pas ha zhes bya /
NK109(dze)002:269: de lta bu'i gzhi de la skyes ba med pas a zhes bya /
NK109(dze)002:270: skye ba med pa'i don de skal ldan gyi mngon
NK109(dze)002:271: sum gyi lam la brten nas thob pas 'greng bur
NK109(dze)002:272: byung ba'o // lam de yang rang bzhin dag pa'i shes rab kyis shes pa na sha /
NK109(dze)002:273: ji ltar shes pas sku gsum lam snang du shes pas ka zhes bya /
NK109(dze)002:274: de yang ye nas skye ba med pa'i don de /
NK109(dze)002:275: sngar chad shes ma myong ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:276: sku gsum lam gyi snang ba la brten nas skye med nyams su myong bas +aa zhes bya /
NK109(dze)002:277: de ltar skye med du rtogs shing shes pas rang don khong du chud pas /
NK109(dze)002:278: gdul bya'i yul mi 'dra ba tha dad pas /
NK109(dze)002:279: 'gro ba rigs drug la sogs pa la /
NK109(dze)002:280: 'dul byed kyi sku mi 'dra ba tha dad pa thub pa drug la sogs par sprul nas /
NK109(dze)002:281: gzhan don rdzogs par byed pas zhabs klud du byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:282: de'ang lam gyi sku gsum po de da lta nyid
NK109(dze)002:283: du shes rab rang byung gi sgron ma la brten
NK109(dze)002:284: nas nyams su blangs pas skye bas na k+sha zhes
NK109(dze)002:285: bya'o // de'ang yul nam mkha' stong pa la da yin /
NK109(dze)002:286: de nyid la rig pa'i ye shes 'char bar byed pas gong ma'i yin no //
NK109(dze)002:287: de yang 'das pa'i dus las kyang sngar 'char byed
NK109(dze)002:288: kyi sgo ma 'gags par shar bas na r+aa zhes
NK109(dze)002:289: bya'o // de ltar shar ba'i rig pa ye shes nyid la sku ste zhal phyag gi rnam pa'am /
NK109(dze)002:291: 'od dang ye shes kyi tshogs dpag tu med par snang bar byed pa /
NK109(dze)002:292: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur snang bas na tsa /
NK109(dze)002:293: de yang dus thams cad du rtag par bzhugs pas na /
NK109(dze)002:294: gnas gang na rang gi lus kyi dkyil tsi ta rin po che'i gzhal yas khang na /
NK109(dze)002:295: rtag par bzhugs pa'i ye shes nyid rang gi mig nas 'char bas t+r+aa zhes bya /
NK109(dze)002:296: de ltar rang gi lus kyi gnad la brten pas na na yin la /
NK109(dze)002:297: de nyid la brten nas 'khrul pa thams cad thog gzhi la log pas na ma yin no //
NK109(dze)002:298: de yang bla ma'i thabs 'gags pa med pa la brten nas thob pas na de las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:300: gnas pa'i sgra rang gi rtsa gnas kyi yi ge'i brda' ci brjod pa /
NK109(dze)002:304: snang ba'i brda don gyi man ngag go /
NK109(dze)002:305: brjod pa sgra yi snang ba thams cad gtan la
NK109(dze)002:306: 'bebs pa'i brda' sgra don rang bzhin med par snang
NK109(dze)002:307: bas / med pa zhes bya ste mi snang ba'i brda don man ngag go /
NK109(dze)002:308: de nyid ma bcos rang bzhin gnas lugs kyi sgra'i
NK109(dze)002:309: brdar lus ngag yid gsum gyi gnas che bas chen
NK109(dze)002:311: lag gi 'du byed kyi brda' don man ngag tu phyung ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:312: rgyud ni gsang ba bla na med pa'i rang rgyud
NK109(dze)002:313: dag pa la brten nas rig pa'i ye shes mngon
NK109(dze)002:314: sum du nyams su myong ba skye ba ni snang
NK109(dze)002:315: srid thams cad sgra don gyi man ngag tu gyur
NK109(dze)002:316: pas spang bya ci'ang med la /
NK109(dze)002:317: sgrub bya ci 'ang med pa'i ming du thogs pa'i brda yi rnam pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:318: ming du med pa'i brda yi rnam pa'i don gyi man ngag du phyung bas na rgyud ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:319: rin po che la sogs pa 'di man chad ni /
NK109(dze)002:320: rgyud kyi mtshan gyi che ba 'am /
NK109(dze)002:321: yon tan du zhar la byung bas na bshad pa
NK109(dze)002:322: gong gi rnams kyi chog /'o na yang rgyud rang
NK109(dze)002:323: gi ngo bo dang sbyar na //
NK109(dze)002:324: de'ang le'u dag po las nga nyid la /
NK109(dze)002:325: gnas lugs dang snang thabs gnyis ma spang bar rdzogs pa'o bya ste /
NK109(dze)002:326: yi ge med pa'i rgyud 'di las /
NK109(dze)002:327: yon tan 'phel nas byung bas na rin po che yin la /
NK109(dze)002:328: de'ang rang byung gi ye shes la 'du 'bral med pas sku mngon par snang ba nyid do //
NK109(dze)002:329: zhes pas yi ge med pa'i rgyud 'di rgyal mtshan ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:330: de yang 'di nyid las gsang bas chos rnams rdzogs pa rgyud yin la /
NK109(dze)002:331: 'di nyid rgyud thams cad kyi nang nas rgyal po lta bur 'dug pas rgyal po'o //
NK109(dze)002:332: 'gyur med rig pa'i don 'di nyid kyis ston pas gdung /
NK109(dze)002:333: 'di nyid la nang gi chos rnams thams cad rdzogs pas rgyud /
NK109(dze)002:334: 'di nyid mig dang 'brel bas lta ba /
NK109(dze)002:335: yul nam mkha' la spyod cing rgyud kyi che ba
NK109(dze)002:336: nam mkha' dang mnyam par gnas pas nam mkha'i mtha'
NK109(dze)002:337: dang mnyam pa'o // rgyud 'di nyid la phyi'i chos thams cad rdzogs pas rgyud ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:340: de ltar rgyud kyi mtshan bstan pa de dag rnams ni /
NK109(dze)002:341: shes bya skye ba med pa'i tshig tu bkod yin te /
NK109(dze)002:342: shes bya'i chos so don gyi ye shes zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)002:343: shes pa la dgos pa ci yod na phyin log
NK109(dze)002:344: par mi 'gyur bas na de dag dang sbyar te
NK109(dze)002:345: bshad pa'o // nyams su blang bya skye med a la brten nas bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:346: yi ge med pa'i rgyud kyi don dri ma gang yang med pa'i skye med kyi don /
NK109(dze)002:347: nyams su len pa'i skal ldan gyis /
NK109(dze)002:348: thog mar rang gi bla ma la gdams pa yang nas yang du zhu dgos pas na /
NK109(dze)002:349: 'di'i le'u drug pa nas chos kyi sku gdam ngag la thug go /
NK109(dze)002:351: de yang grogs spangs te phyi nang gi bya ba btang ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:352: le'u dang po nas phyi nang gi bya ba btang na snang ba rgya yis thebs /
NK109(dze)002:354: de nas dgon par gnas pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:356: grong khyer chen po las 'das te nags kyi klong chen po'i dgon par gnas par gyis shig /
NK109(dze)002:358: de'ang grogs spang la gnas de nyid du bsgrub pa ni //
NK109(dze)002:360: phyi'i longs spyod thams cad la ma chags par grogs med par nags khrod dag tu /
NK109(dze)002:361: de nyid la gnas par gyis shig /
NK109(dze)002:363: de nas sngon 'gro'i man ngag gis nyams su blang ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:364: lugs kyi sngon du 'gro ba'i man ngag gis /
NK109(dze)002:365: bya byed ma 'gags dmigs pa yongs kyi med /
NK109(dze)002:369: gsung gi rol pa cir yang ston /
NK109(dze)002:371: de nas sems kyi spyod pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:373: sems kyi rtog pa sna tshogs pa'o /
NK109(dze)002:374: zhes pa ni sngon du lus ngag yid kyi spyod pa bya /
NK109(dze)002:375: de nas rnal du 'beb pa'i cho ga bya ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:377: lus rnal du 'bebs pa'i cho ga ni //
NK109(dze)002:378: ye shes kyi rtsa dal bas grub /
NK109(dze)002:380: ngag gi sor 'jug pa'i cho ga ni /
NK109(dze)002:382: tshig thams cad dang bral ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:384: sems rnal du 'bebs pa le'u gsum pa nas /
NK109(dze)002:385: thugs kyi ci'ang med ces pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:386: de ltar sngon du 'gro ba dang tshad du 'byor na /
NK109(dze)002:387: dngos gzhi'i don nyams su myong ba mtshan gyi yon
NK109(dze)002:388: tan skye med a'i don 'gyur du bshad pa ni
NK109(dze)002:390: mig zur nyid las dbyings su 'byung bas /
NK109(dze)002:393: skye med a yi snang ba ngos bzung med /
NK109(dze)002:395: gting dpag med pa'i rgya mtsho chen po nas /
NK109(dze)002:396: nub pa med pa'i rgyal mtshan rtse mor ltos /
NK109(dze)002:399: rig pa lu gu rgyud mig nas drangs ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:400: de nas yul nam mkha' ste /
NK109(dze)002:402: dag pa'i nam mkha' ngos bzung kun las 'das /
NK109(dze)002:404: yul nam mkha' gtad pa lta ba'i mig yin nam mkha'i mtha' dang zhes pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:405: de ltar nyams su blang ba las snang ba'i 'phel 'byung ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:407: rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyi sku ni grangs med pa'i snang ba chen po ste /
NK109(dze)002:408: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:410: de yang de ltar snang ba'i 'phel rdzogs nas rig
NK109(dze)002:411: pa tshad la phebs pa ni rgyal po lta bu'o
NK109(dze)002:414: de nyid dgongs pa'i drod rnyed nas /
NK109(dze)002:416: de ltar sku gsum lam du snang ba yin pas na rgyud gsum du byung ba ste /
NK109(dze)002:418: sku dang bcas pa snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:420: de yang skye ba med pa'i a la brten nas
NK109(dze)002:421: rig pa'i ye shes mngon sum du bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)002:424: skye ba med pa'i mngon sum sangs rgyas kyis /
NK109(dze)002:426: chos rnams zad pa'i snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:428: 'khor 'das gnyis med du mnyam pas na /
NK109(dze)002:430: de ltar yang le'u bzhi pa las /
NK109(dze)002:435: rang grol ba la sogs pas bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:436: de ltar mtshan bstan nas gzhung ston te /
NK109(dze)002:439: phyag btsal bar mdor bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:440: gzhung gi don rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:441: phyag btsal ba la mdor bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK109(dze)002:442: sngon byung du sdud pa pos /
NK109(dze)002:443: rgyud kyi ston pa la mos pas rang gzhan gyi
NK109(dze)002:444: don gnyis rdzogs par bya ba'i phyir phyag btsal ba
NK109(dze)002:446: bsod nams kyi tshogs rdzogs par bya ba'i don du bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:447: sngon byung rang don rtogs pa nyid la nyid phyag btsal ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:448: sngon du 'gro ba lus ngag yid gsum gyi spyod pa byas pas /
NK109(dze)002:449: lus ngag yid gsum gyi zhen pa rang log pas /
NK109(dze)002:450: lus ngag yid gsum gyi bcom pas na bcom /
NK109(dze)002:451: de ltar bcom pas lus ngag yid gsum la lus sprul skur ldan pa dang ngag longs skur ldan /
NK109(dze)002:452: yid chos kyi skur ldan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:453: 'das pa na 'khor ba'i lus las 'das te /
NK109(dze)002:454: sprul pa'i sku nyid kyi yon tan rdzogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:455: ngag 'khor ngag las 'das nas longs sku'i yon tan rdzogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:456: yid 'khor ba'i yid las 'das te byung tshor rnams
NK109(dze)002:457: rang 'gags pas chos kyi sku'i klong du rang 'das
NK109(dze)002:458: pa'o // sku ni de ltar 'jig rten gyi lus ngag gi zhen pa log pas sku gsum mo //
NK109(dze)002:460: chos kyi sku'i snang ba mtshan ma'i spros pa dang bral bas chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:461: longs sku'i snang ba sna tshogs bkod pa lhun grub yon tan rdzogs pa'i tshul yin no //
NK109(dze)002:462: sprul pa'i sku'i snang ba rang ni cog bzhag gi snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:464: de ltar snang ba gsum gyi bdag nyid sangs rgyas can thams cad la khyab pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:465: ston pa rang gi rig pa dri ma dang bral
NK109(dze)002:466: ba nyid yin pas de nyid la de nyid kyis
NK109(dze)002:467: phyag 'tshal ba'o // phyag btsal ba la dgos pa ci yod na /
NK109(dze)002:468: rang don mngon sum du khong du chud par bya ba'i dgos pa yod do //
NK109(dze)002:469: gzhan don rdzogs pa'i phyir phyag btsal ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:470: gsang ba yi ge med pa'i rgyud kyi mtshan bstan pa tsam gyis /
NK109(dze)002:471: dbang po rab rnams kyis 'khor gsum gyi rnam rtog bcom nas ye shes lnga dang ldan pas /
NK109(dze)002:472: nyon mongs pa lnga las 'das pas /
NK109(dze)002:473: gzhar gyi 'bras bu sku gsum ye shes lnga snang ba rgya chen po /
NK109(dze)002:474: ston pa nyid rgyud kyi mtshan du byung ba ste /
NK109(dze)002:475: de nyid la phyag btsal ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:476: 'bring gi don bsdus pa la brten nas /
NK109(dze)002:478: yi ge rdzogs par bstan pas /
NK109(dze)002:479: rnam par rtog pa bcom nas /
NK109(dze)002:480: ye shes lnga dang ldan te /
NK109(dze)002:481: nyon mongs pa lnga las 'das pas dbang po 'bring
NK109(dze)002:482: po'i 'bras bu longs sku'i snang ba rgya chen po
NK109(dze)002:483: / chos nyid kyi bar ma do la ston pa nyid /
NK109(dze)002:486: dbang po tha mas rgyud kyi gzhung rdzogs par bshad
NK109(dze)002:487: pa bla ma'i man ngag la brten nas bstan pas
NK109(dze)002:488: / rnam par rtog pa bcom nas ye shes lnga dang ldan te /
NK109(dze)002:489: nyon mongs pa lnga las 'das pas /
NK109(dze)002:490: tha ma'i 'bras bu sprul pa'i sku snang ba rgya
NK109(dze)002:491: chen pos rang bzhin sprul pa'i sku'i zhing khams su
NK109(dze)002:492: ston pa rgyud 'di nyid yin pas rgyud las phyag
NK109(dze)002:494: rjes 'jug gi rgyud kyi ston pa drug pa rdo rje 'chang /
NK109(dze)002:495: de nyid kyis ma rig pa la sogs pa bcom pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:497: mi gnas pa'i ye shes dang drug dang ldan pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:498: yang dbang phyug phun sum tshogs pa la sogs pa drug dang ldan pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:499: 'khor ba'i rnam rtog tha dad du 'dzin pa las 'das nas /
NK109(dze)002:500: nyid kyi sku las 'od zer gyi tshogs shin tu
NK109(dze)002:501: rgya che bar gdul bya rnams la ston par byed
NK109(dze)002:502: pa las / rjes su 'jug pas rgyud bsod nams
NK109(dze)002:503: kyi tshogs rdzogs par bya ba'i don du phyag 'tshal
NK109(dze)002:505: da ni gzhung gi don rgyas par bshad pa la /
NK109(dze)002:506: le'u drug gis bdag nyid du gnas pa las //
NK109(dze)002:507: le'u dang po'i don ston te /
NK109(dze)002:509: 'di la bsdus pa'i don bcur gnas pa las /
NK109(dze)002:510: dang po gleng gzhi dngos bstan pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:511: de la thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi rang
NK109(dze)002:512: gi mtshan nyid du gtan la phab nas bstan pa
NK109(dze)002:513: dang / de'i tshig don nges par bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:514: thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi rang gi mtshan nyid du bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:515: 'di skad bdag gis bstan pa'i dus gcig na /
NK109(dze)002:518: bdag gis bstan pa mi rigs zer ba yod de /
NK109(dze)002:520: chos kyi sku las longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku nyid la nyid sprul byung bas /
NK109(dze)002:521: de nyid la sprul pa'i sku /
NK109(dze)002:522: nyi ma las 'od kyi tshul du byung ba las ston pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:524: 'khor dang thams cad nyid kyi snang sprul du byung bas /
NK109(dze)002:525: bdag gis bstan pa zhes bstan pa yin pas skyon med do //
NK109(dze)002:526: don dam pa la gzung 'dzin gyi nyan pa dang sdud pa por mngon pa med pas /
NK109(dze)002:528: gnas lugs kyi rig pa snang thabs kyi 'khor la bka' stsal pa /
NK109(dze)002:530: mu tig phreng ba las kyang /
NK109(dze)002:531: rang gi 'khor sdud nyan pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:533: kha sa mun+ta tan+t+ra las kyang /
NK109(dze)002:538: bshad par bya ba dang chos kyang nga /
NK109(dze)002:539: zhes pas 'gal ba med de rab tu 'thad do //
NK109(dze)002:540: de bas gleng gzhi rang gi ngo bo de nyid gang bstan pa dang gang du bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:544: gang bstan na rgyud 'di bstan pa thams cad 'dul bar bstan pas 'di ci bya la /
NK109(dze)002:545: tshul lam thabs ci bstan na tshangs pa'i skad dang ldan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:546: gang du bstan na chos dbyings kyi pho brang /
NK109(dze)002:547: snang ba nyid sku yis brgyan pa'i pho brang du bstan no //
NK109(dze)002:549: bdag dngos po'i gnas lugs ston pa 'dzin pa'i rig la 'byed pa med pas so //
NK109(dze)002:550: gang la bstan na gis zhes bya ste snang ba thabs kyi 'khor la bstan /
NK109(dze)002:551: gang tshe bstan na dus zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)002:552: rig pa'i ye shes mngon du snang ba'i tshe bstan la /
NK109(dze)002:553: de yang rig pa'i ye shes mngon du snang bar ma gyur gyi bar la /
NK109(dze)002:554: rgyud 'di bshad cing bstan kyang don med pa'i phyir /
NK109(dze)002:555: rig pa'i ye shes mngon du snang ba'i dus na
NK109(dze)002:556: rgyud kyi don rnams ji lta bar rtogs shing khang
NK109(dze)002:561: dus dang thams cad rang byung gi rig pa'i ye
NK109(dze)002:562: shes gcig pu las gzhan su yang med ces pa
NK109(dze)002:563: ni / gcig na zhes bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:564: tshig don nges pa bstan pa la gnyis las /
NK109(dze)002:565: 'dir rgyud lung gi zhen pa dgag par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:566: rgyud thams cad bshad du med do zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:567: rgyud ni rang bzhin gnas lugs kyi rgyud dang /
NK109(dze)002:569: rang bzhin dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul /
NK109(dze)002:572: thugs rje gsum du bzhugs pa de la /
NK109(dze)002:573: tshig dang yi ge gang du'ang grub pa med pas /
NK109(dze)002:574: rang bzhin dang thabs thams cad bshad du med do //
NK109(dze)002:576: thabs kyi rgyud ni mtshon bya thabs kyi rgyud kyi
NK109(dze)002:577: dngos po de nyid gnas lugs ji lta bar gnas
NK109(dze)002:578: tshul ye nas rang grol du bzhugs pas bshad du
NK109(dze)002:579: med / mtshon byed thabs kyi rgyud la don gyi
NK109(dze)002:580: rgyud rang gi rigs pa nyid kyang de ltar bzhugs
NK109(dze)002:581: pas tshig las 'das te bshad du med pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:582: tshig gi rgyud kyi dbang du byas na /
NK109(dze)002:583: 'dir rig pa mngon sum du grol bas na /
NK109(dze)002:584: shes rab kyi spyod yul lam tshig la mi brten pas na /
NK109(dze)002:585: rgyud kyi dbye ba de dag bshad du med pas
NK109(dze)002:586: bshad du med do zhes la bzla ba dang bcas
NK109(dze)002:587: nas bstan pa'o // do ci'i phyir bshad du med na /
NK109(dze)002:588: mtshan ma'i rnam par rtog pa /
NK109(dze)002:589: rig pa'i ye shes nyid la ye nas yod ma myong bas /
NK109(dze)002:590: de nyid kyi klong la tshig dang yi ge ru med pas /
NK109(dze)002:591: rang gi rang bzhin tu 'das nas bshad du med do //
NK109(dze)002:593: mi 'gyur ba rtsa ba'ii lung dang /
NK109(dze)002:594: spros gzhi tha snyad pa'i lung ngo //
NK109(dze)002:595: mi 'gyur ba ni rang gi rig pa'i ye shes dngos po'i 'dug tshul nyid yin te /
NK109(dze)002:596: 'di la tha snyad yod ma myong bas /
NK109(dze)002:597: lung bstan du med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:598: spros pa tha snyad pa'i lung la dbye na mang po yod kyang /
NK109(dze)002:599: 'di dag gis tshig gis bud+d+ha bar mi 'gyur bas /
NK109(dze)002:600: lung thams cad bstan du med do //
NK109(dze)002:602: de yang gtan tshigs gang gis phyir bstan du med na /
NK109(dze)002:603: ma bcos pa'i klong du 'das shing rtsol sgrub med pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:605: de'ang rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po bas /
NK109(dze)002:606: rang bzhin du ma bcos par /
NK109(dze)002:607: so mar bzhag pas gnas lugs kyi dgongs pa dang mi 'bral ba yin la /
NK109(dze)002:612: 'bras bu ji lta yin pa mang por spros pas /
NK109(dze)002:613: rtsol ba dang sgrub pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:619: bsgrub pa chen po la sogs pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:621: rang bzhin rang lugs kyi dgongs pa dang mi 'bral
NK109(dze)002:622: bar gnas pas de nyid kyi klong du rtsol bsgrub
NK109(dze)002:623: rnams 'das pas rim par brgyad po'i rtsol sgrub med
NK109(dze)002:624: pas so // man ngag rgyud la brten pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:625: bla ma'i man ngag la brten pa'o /
NK109(dze)002:626: rgyud ni kha 'thor ba'i tshul du gsungs pa la sogs pa yin te /
NK109(dze)002:627: 'di dag kyang mtshon bya gnas lugs las ma grub pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:628: mtshon byed tshig tu ma grub pas mtshon du med do //
NK109(dze)002:629: bla ma'i man ngag la brten pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:630: snyan rgyud rim pa nas rim par brgyud pa dag yin no //
NK109(dze)002:631: 'di dag kyang tshig la brten pas na /
NK109(dze)002:632: tshig gis sangs rgyas la phan ma btags /
NK109(dze)002:634: man ngag de dag mtshon du med do //
NK109(dze)002:636: gtan tshigs gang gi phyir mtshon du med na ma slad pa ni dngos po'i gnas lugs la /
NK109(dze)002:637: sus kyang bsgyur du mi btub pas /
NK109(dze)002:638: de nyid kyi klong phyogs gang yang ma ltung ba nyid yin pas /
NK109(dze)002:639: rnam rtog rang bzhin gyis nub pas na 'das pa yin la /
NK109(dze)002:640: de lta bu'i gnas lugs la /
NK109(dze)002:641: gud du bcas pa'i lta sgom gyis bsgrub tu med pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:642: stong pa nyid kyis gnas lugs dngos po brgyad pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:644: snang ba dam pa'i 'khor rnams zhes pa la sogs pas bstan to //
NK109(dze)002:649: bstan pa'i tshig dang yi ger bkod pa 'di sus
NK109(dze)002:650: nyan na snang ba rang bzhin dag pa'i snang ba
NK109(dze)002:651: dang / 'gro drug 'khrul pa'i snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:652: bde gshegs gdul bya la sogs pa'i snang ba dam pa bzhin dag la /
NK109(dze)002:654: ye shes phyogs dag pa'i snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:656: de dag 'khor du byung bas rdzogs pa chen po'i yo gas /
NK109(dze)002:657: ci ltar spyad kyang 'tshang rgya 'ong rnams ni snang ba de rnams so //
NK109(dze)002:659: phyi rol gyi de rnams yin la de la /
NK109(dze)002:660: ye ji bzhin pa'i rim pa /
NK109(dze)002:661: gzhi 'dzin gyis khyab par gnas pa de la /
NK109(dze)002:662: gnas lugs dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul mngon sum du shar bas /
NK109(dze)002:663: rig pa la phra rags kyi dri mas ma bsgribs pas ma 'gags pa zhes bya /
NK109(dze)002:664: gsal lugs ji ltar gsal na /
NK109(dze)002:665: 'od dang sku dang thig le la sogs par gsal lo //
NK109(dze)002:666: gleng ba'i rgyu bstan pa la gnyis las /
NK109(dze)002:669: brjod bya dgag pa bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:670: de skad ces rig pa'i gnas nas /
NK109(dze)002:672: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:674: gong du thun mong ma yin pa'i gleng gzhi'i skabs gzugs su bkod la /
NK109(dze)002:675: zhal phyag gi rnam pa'i ston pa ma yin par /
NK109(dze)002:677: de yang nyid rig pa rang yin par 'dir gsal
NK109(dze)002:678: bas gong gi sgro 'dogs bcad gnas ni bya rgod
NK109(dze)002:679: phung po la sogs pa yin te /
NK109(dze)002:680: thog ma dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul la byas /
NK109(dze)002:681: da lta gnas tshul dang sbyar na /
NK109(dze)002:682: tsit+ta rin po che'i gzhal yas khang ngo //
NK109(dze)002:683: sngar chos skus tshig tu ma gsungs /
NK109(dze)002:684: da lta nyid du longs skus /
NK109(dze)002:685: tha snyad rags pa dang bcas par mi gsungs /
NK109(dze)002:686: phyis sprul pa'i skus phyi log tu gsung bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)002:688: as chos nyid skye ba med pa'i don mtshon la /
NK109(dze)002:689: 'as 'gags pa med pa'i thugs rje'i don mtshon la /
NK109(dze)002:690: zag med kyis chos nyid stong pa nyid kyi don mtshon /
NK109(dze)002:691: klad kor gyis mnyam nyid du rtogs la /
NK109(dze)002:692: na ros chos nyid dang rig pa 'du 'bral med par rtogs so //
NK109(dze)002:693: gleng gzhi'i dgos ched la lnga las /
NK109(dze)002:694: thun mong gi gleng gzhi dngos bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:695: 'di skad sus thos na sdud pa po lag na rdo rjes thos /
NK109(dze)002:696: thos pa gang thos na 'dis tshig dang yi ger bkod pa'i rgyud 'di thos /
NK109(dze)002:697: gang las thos na rgyud kyis ston pa drug pa rdo rje 'chang las thos /
NK109(dze)002:698: gang gis thos na rna ba'i dbang pos phyin ci ma log par thos /
NK109(dze)002:699: thos lugs ci ltar thos na /
NK109(dze)002:700: rgyud 'di brten pa'i yo gi tshe gcig la sangs rgya bar thos /
NK109(dze)002:701: gnas gang du thos na chos nyid rang snang gi nam mkha' klong du thos /
NK109(dze)002:702: dus ci tsam na thos na /
NK109(dze)002:703: dus gcig la yang yang ma thos te //
NK109(dze)002:704: sdud pa po nyid shes rab che ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:705: gsang ba'i rgyud 'di nyid 'byung dka' zhing dkon pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:706: grogs gang dang lhan cig tu thos na /
NK109(dze)002:707: mi snang ba'i snang ba chen po ste //
NK109(dze)002:709: thub pa drug la sogs dang lhan cig tu thos /
NK109(dze)002:710: thos pa la dgos pa ci yod na /
NK109(dze)002:711: rang don du rig pa mngon sum gyi ye shes dbang po la brten nas mthong ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:712: gzhan don du 'pho ba chen mo la brten nas
NK109(dze)002:713: sems can thams cad skad cig la 'tshangs rgya ba'i
NK109(dze)002:714: dgos pa yod pas thos pa byas pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:715: chos nyid rnam par rtog pa dang bral ba de
NK109(dze)002:716: nyid rang la snang ba las gzhan la ma yin
NK109(dze)002:717: pa'o // nam mkha' ni rang bzhin 'dug tshul gyi nam mkha' ngo bo ka dag yin la /
NK109(dze)002:718: gtad sa yul gyi nam mkha' phyi rol stong pa 'di nyid la /
NK109(dze)002:719: gud bcad rdzas kyi nam mkha' bu ga la sogs
NK109(dze)002:720: pa snod kyi nam mkha' dang bu ga rnams so
NK109(dze)002:721: // btags pa ming gi nam mkha' mtshon pa'i nam mkha' la brten pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:722: mtshon pa'i gnas mtshon par byed pa'i nam mkha'/
NK109(dze)002:723: dpal nam mkha' med pa'i rgyud ces pa'am /
NK109(dze)002:724: nam mkha' che zhes pa la sogs pa rnams so //
NK109(dze)002:727: nam mkha' sems kyi khyab byed du ming btags pa rnams so //
NK109(dze)002:728: brten pa dpe la brten pas so so'i mtshan nyid
NK109(dze)002:729: 'tsho ba stong pa'i nam mkha' zhes ming du grags
NK109(dze)002:730: pa dang / ming la sogs pa ming du btags pa /
NK109(dze)002:732: de nyid kyi mtshan nyid shes par byed pas na nam mkha'o //
NK109(dze)002:736: 'khor ba'i g.yul bzlog par byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:737: 'jig rten pa ni rigs drug so so'i stobs rnams so //
NK109(dze)002:738: de yang 'khor ba'i g.yul bzlog pa'i stobs brten nas rig pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:739: ming du grags pa'i rig pa brdas btags pa rnams dang /
NK109(dze)002:740: cha mthun 'jig rten gyi rig pa gso ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:742: bstan bcos la sogs pa rig pa'i gnas lnga dang /
NK109(dze)002:743: shes pa yan lag gi rig pa 'jig rten gyi rig pa rno rtul la sogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:744: snying po kun khyab gyi rig pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:745: ma rig med pa la sogs pa 'di nyid do //
NK109(dze)002:746: ma rig pa la sogs pa'i sgrib byed rnams kyis ma bsgribs pa /
NK109(dze)002:747: ma 'gags par shar ba'i tshe zhes pa dus smos pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:748: shar lugs ji ltar na rdo rje lu gu rgyud du shar ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:749: ston pa bstan pa ni ston pa nyid snang ba med pa'i zhes pa la sogs pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:750: ston pa sngon byung du ngo bo ston par byung la /
NK109(dze)002:755: chos kyi dbyings su byung bas so //
NK109(dze)002:756: rjes la brgyud kyi ston pa nyid drug pa rdo rje 'chang yin no //
NK109(dze)002:757: de yang sku gsum tha ma sprul pa'i skur byung bas so //
NK109(dze)002:758: snang ba ni ma dag pa'i snang ba med pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:759: sku ni gzugs kyi sku la /
NK109(dze)002:763: zhal phyag gi rnam par byung bas so //
NK109(dze)002:767: de'i tshe 'khor ni lag na rdo rje'i grogs sangs rgyas bdun /
NK109(dze)002:768: mi snang ba'i snang ba chen po'i gzugs su sprul pas na phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:769: bstan pa phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:770: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po 'di nyid thabs che ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:773: thabs rno zhing myur myur bas /
NK109(dze)002:775: bstan pa nyid phun sum tshogs pas so //
NK109(dze)002:776: dus phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:779: 'khor dang bstan pa rnams dus gcig tu 'tshogs bas na gcig tu bzhugs te zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:780: zhu bar spobs pa lags pa ste //
NK109(dze)002:781: zhus te 'khod pa bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:782: de nas de'i tshe 'khod de rtog pa dang bcas pas 'di skad ces gsol to //
NK109(dze)002:783: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:784: de nas ni gleng gzhi rdzogs pa'i tshe dus nges pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:785: yid la drug te kun tu 'tshol byed kyi yid
NK109(dze)002:786: ni yul rnams la rjes su 'gro zhing de'i rjes
NK109(dze)002:787: gleng pa'o // nges par 'jog pa'i yid ni yul
NK109(dze)002:788: de la blo'i 'jug pa yan lag dang bcas pa'o
NK109(dze)002:789: gleng pa'o // // gtan la 'debs pa'i yid ni
NK109(dze)002:790: yul de'i ming la sogs pa'i mtshan nyid gtan la
NK109(dze)002:791: gleng pa'o // // 'bebs pa'o // yid kyi rnam par shes pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:792: nges pa dang bcas nas yul bdag gir bzung ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:793: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid ni /
NK109(dze)002:794: de ltar yul dang yul can gyi rnam pa de lta bu la /
NK109(dze)002:795: rang dang gzhan gyi rnam par phye ste /
NK109(dze)002:800: phrag dog rnams kyi rgyu nye bar byas pa rnams so //
NK109(dze)002:801: rtog pa dang bcas pa'i yid ni de ltar gong rnams 'dus pas /
NK109(dze)002:802: rang gi la rtog pa rags shing gzhan gyi la rlom par byed pa nyid do //
NK109(dze)002:803: de ltar yid drug 'dus pa'i tha ma rtog pa
NK109(dze)002:804: dang bcas pa'i yang yid kyi yul drug la bya
NK109(dze)002:806: de'i mtshan nyid shes pas rig pa rang snang du gyur pa'i don no //
NK109(dze)002:807: de yang sngon byung du sdud pa po'i yid la rtog pa bzhugs pas /
NK109(dze)002:808: de'i tshe the tshom bcad pa'i don du rgyud kyi ston pa la zhus so //
NK109(dze)002:809: kye ma ni nges pa kho nar ston pa la
NK109(dze)002:810: gsang sngags kyi srid zhu khyad par can gyi bos
NK109(dze)002:811: pa'o // de'ang sngon byung du ston pa nyid kyis 'di dag gi don rig pas na /
NK109(dze)002:812: rig pa'i rgyal po 'di nyid ces bos nas yang
NK109(dze)002:813: dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams kyi lta ba'i
NK109(dze)002:814: don gang lags / bdag gis 'di ma 'tshal bas bstan par zhu /
NK109(dze)002:815: dgongs pa zhes bgyi pa de'i don ji lta bu lags /
NK109(dze)002:816: bdag gis sngar ma 'tshal bas ston pas lung ma nor bar bdag la bstan du gsol /
NK109(dze)002:817: de'i thabs gang la brten nas shes pa lags /
NK109(dze)002:818: thabs de nyid bdag la mdzad du gsol /
NK109(dze)002:820: nyid ston pa la lag na rdo rjes sngon byung du zhus la /
NK109(dze)002:822: rig pa'i ye shes la yid kyi snang tshul tha dad par shar bas /
NK109(dze)002:823: ston pa dang mthun pas zhu ba'i tshul tsam du snang tshul la byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:825: de nas yang snang ba med pa'i klong nas /
NK109(dze)002:826: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:827: de nas zhu ba pos zhus pa'i //
NK109(dze)002:828: de nas yang ni gong gi stobs kyi rig pa la smos pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:829: snang ba yid drug gi the tshom dang bcas pa med pa'i klong /
NK109(dze)002:830: chos nyid 'khrul pa med pa nas /
NK109(dze)002:832: rang rgyud pa'i gzugs su med pas /
NK109(dze)002:833: rig pa gong gi rnam pa rig pas de nyid las grol ba'i don /
NK109(dze)002:834: lta ba dang dgongs pa yin pas /
NK109(dze)002:835: de gnyis kyi don gsungs pas na /
NK109(dze)002:836: bka' phyin ci ma log pa /
NK109(dze)002:837: rdzogs pa chen po 'bum tsho drug cu rtsa bzhi
NK109(dze)002:838: las khyad par du gsang ba yi ge med pa'i
NK109(dze)002:839: rgyud 'di sngon byung du lag na rdo rje'i rna
NK109(dze)002:840: bar rtsal la / rjes 'jug tu rang bzhin rdzogs
NK109(dze)002:841: pa chen po'i don la mos pa rnams kyi yid
NK109(dze)002:842: drug gi yul gyi zhen ldog pa'i don du de
NK109(dze)002:844: kye ma khyed kyi rang don nges par rtogs par gyis shig /
NK109(dze)002:845: kye ma khyed kyis gzhan don du nges par rtogs par gyis shig /
NK109(dze)002:846: yid drug gi snang ba ni yang dag par med pa yin pa las /
NK109(dze)002:847: ma rtogs pas snang ba bzhin du rang las 'khor zhing 'byung ste /
NK109(dze)002:848: de yang yul drug tu snang ba rnams rang bzhin
NK109(dze)002:849: rdzogs pa chen po'i lta ba la brten nas dag
NK109(dze)002:850: par byed pa'i thabs ngas bstan gyis /
NK109(dze)002:851: rna ba'i dbang po yul gzhan la ma yengs par /
NK109(dze)002:852: rang gi blo'i skyon zhabs rdol ba lta bu dang /
NK109(dze)002:855: dug can la sogs spong la nyon cig ces nyan
NK109(dze)002:856: pa po la gdams pa dang bcas te bstan pa'o
NK109(dze)002:857: // da ni ston pa'i lan dngos /
NK109(dze)002:858: stong pa nyid tshig gis mtha' bcad nas /
NK109(dze)002:859: dngos po dgag par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:860: nga rang byung gi ye shes lta ba la bcad pa'i yul med do //
NK109(dze)002:861: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:862: nga ni thog ma gzhi gnas kyi ye shes ngo
NK109(dze)002:863: bo ka dag gi ye shes la dri ma gang
NK109(dze)002:865: rang bzhin kun snang gi ye shes la dngos po rags pa'i 'byung ba las log ste /
NK109(dze)002:866: rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i 'od lnga 'gags pa med par 'char ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:867: thugs rje kun khyab kyi ye shes la 'bad rtsol
NK109(dze)002:868: med par gdul bya'i rigs mi 'dra ba tha dad
NK109(dze)002:869: ba la / de 'dul bar byed pa'i sprul pa'i sku mi 'dra ba tha dad par sprul nas /
NK109(dze)002:870: gzhan don mthar phyin par byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:871: mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i ye shes lnga ste go sla'o //
NK109(dze)002:872: de ltar ye shes gnyis po de /
NK109(dze)002:873: dbang po la brten nas bltar yod pas na lta ba la /
NK109(dze)002:875: gud du blos bcad pa med par ma bcos rang
NK109(dze)002:876: bzhag chen por gnas pas gong gi yid drug gi
NK109(dze)002:877: yul med pa'o // de yang sngar zhen gyi bag
NK109(dze)002:878: chags rgyu la gleng ba'i yid kyi rnam par shes
NK109(dze)002:879: yul med pa'o // pa dang / nyon mongs pa
NK109(dze)002:880: can gyi yid med pas sngar 'das pa la rjes
NK109(dze)002:882: phyis 'byung ba'i bag chags nye bar slong ba /
NK109(dze)002:883: kun du 'tshol byed kyi yid dang /
NK109(dze)002:884: rtog pa dang bcas pa'i yid med pas phyis 'byung ba'i bag chags rnams med pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:885: da ltar gyi bag chags rgyu la brten pa'i nges par 'jog pa'i yid dang /
NK109(dze)002:886: gtan la 'bebs pa'i yid gnyis med pas /
NK109(dze)002:887: da ltar snang ba'i yid drug gis yul la 'dzin
NK109(dze)002:888: pa'i bag chags gang yang rig pa nyid la med
NK109(dze)002:889: do // de ltar yid drug med pas las kyi mtshams sbyor ba yang med do //
NK109(dze)002:890: las kyi mtshams ma sbyar bas bag chags snga phyi gsum gtan med do //
NK109(dze)002:891: de dag med pas rgyu bdag nyid gcig pa'i ma rig pa med de /
NK109(dze)002:892: thams cad rig pa'i snang bar shar bas /
NK109(dze)002:894: lhan cig skyes pa'i ma rig pa med de rig
NK109(dze)002:895: pa'i ye shes las ma gtogs pa'i lta ba gzhan
NK109(dze)002:896: med pas / kun du brtags pa'i ma rig pa med de /
NK109(dze)002:897: yid drug gi yul la song ba med pas na'o //
NK109(dze)002:898: sems ni bag chags gsum 'tshogs pa'i gzhi yin pas /
NK109(dze)002:899: bag chags sngar med zin pas /
NK109(dze)002:901: bcu drug gi byung tshor 'gags nas med do //
NK109(dze)002:902: yid ni gong gi yul drug po med par nan tan du bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:903: de lta ba yid kyi byung tshor btsal du ma rnyed pas /
NK109(dze)002:904: yid kyi gnyen po shes rab la 'os pa med pas /
NK109(dze)002:907: sgom pa'i shes rab kyang med do /
NK109(dze)002:908: de rang gi rigs pa ye shes kyi blta ba
NK109(dze)002:909: dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul de las thams cad
NK109(dze)002:910: med pas 'khor ba zhes bya ba grub pa med
NK109(dze)002:911: do // de ltar 'khor ba med par shes pas mya ngan /
NK109(dze)002:912: phyi lus kyi sdug bsngal la brten nas /
NK109(dze)002:913: sems sgyid lug cing dub pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:914: lus ngag yid kyi 'khor ba myang pas /
NK109(dze)002:915: ngan song gsum du 'khor ba de las 'das pa yang med do //
NK109(dze)002:916: de gnyis med pas gzhi 'dzin pa'i rig pa ka dag pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:917: lhag mthong gi rig pa lu gu rgyud kyang btags
NK109(dze)002:918: pa tsam las med par shes pas na de nyid
NK109(dze)002:920: rig pa'i ngo bo med pas rtsal dang yon tan
NK109(dze)002:921: gyi byung tshul gnyis gzhi gnas kyi ye shes dang
NK109(dze)002:922: / mtshan nyid 'dzin pa yang med do //
NK109(dze)002:923: de dag kyang rang gi rig pa'i ye shes kyi
NK109(dze)002:924: snang ba mngon gsum du mthong ba'i skyes bu la
NK109(dze)002:925: ci'i ngo bor yang grub pa med pa chos nyid
NK109(dze)002:927: stong pa nyid lta ba ngos bzung ba la bcus
NK109(dze)002:928: bstan pa'i dang po las dkar nag sun dbyung bar
NK109(dze)002:929: bstan pa ni / kye ma rang byung gi ye shes la zhes pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:930: kye ma ni rang la rang nges pa rnyed pa'i tshig go /
NK109(dze)002:931: nga ni gnas pa gzhi 'dzin gyis 'khor 'das gang gi yang phyogs su ma lhung ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:932: gzhan las ma yin pas rang las byung ba'i ye
NK109(dze)002:933: shes gnyis po la skye ba dang 'chi ba med
NK109(dze)002:935: 'byung cha rten gyi srog med pas sdug bsngal gang gis kyang mi gos te /
NK109(dze)002:936: gnas pa rnam shes kyi srog med pas gang gis kyang gnad la mi phebs /
NK109(dze)002:937: dran pa 'gyu byed kyi srog med pas skye ba dang 'chi ba med pa'i gnad kyis /
NK109(dze)002:938: de nyid la las dge ba'i mtha' las 'das te phan ma btags /
NK109(dze)002:939: sdig pa'i mtha' las 'das pas gnod ma bskyal ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:940: gzung 'dzin dgag par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:942: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan pa yin te /
NK109(dze)002:944: de ltar srog med pa'i gnas pa gzhi 'dzin gyi nga rig pa'i ye shes skye 'chi med pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:945: de yang dri ma'i mtha' thams cad rang bzhin gyis dag pas 'a yin /
NK109(dze)002:946: de yang chos kyi dbyings stong par 'dug pas ho zhes bya la /
NK109(dze)002:947: nga ni gnas pa gzhi 'dzin gyi nga yin la /
NK109(dze)002:948: de lta bu'i rang byung gi ye shes de nyid
NK109(dze)002:949: las lus kyi zhen pa dang bral bas lus kyi
NK109(dze)002:951: de bzhin ngag dang sems kyi bya byed las 'das pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:952: dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul yin pas theg pa
NK109(dze)002:953: thun mong pa rnams kyi 'bad rtsol gyi bya byed
NK109(dze)002:954: med pas / phyi sgo lnga'i yul dang /
NK109(dze)002:955: nang sgo lnga so so'i lta sems gyi rten gnyis las /
NK109(dze)002:957: yul sun dbyung bar bstan pa'i tshig gnyis ni /
NK109(dze)002:958: de ltar skye ba med pa la rig pa'i lam
NK109(dze)002:959: ma 'gags pa sna tshogs su mtshon du btub pas
NK109(dze)002:960: e zhes bya / de yang thog ma'i gzhi las
NK109(dze)002:961: ma g.yos pas gnas pa gzhi 'dzin gyi nga rang
NK109(dze)002:962: byung gi ye shes gnyis po dngos po 'dug tshul
NK109(dze)002:963: la ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum gyi gzhi
NK109(dze)002:964: las ma g.yos pas 'khrul pa'i snang ba la sogs
NK109(dze)002:966: ye ge phyogs dag pa'i rang snang gi mtshan nyid /
NK109(dze)002:968: de nyid rtogs pa zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)002:970: rtags ngos bzung ba bstan pa la tshig gnyis ni
NK109(dze)002:971: a skye ba med pa'i don ye nas gnas pa
NK109(dze)002:972: / de nyid skye med 'gags med du gnas par shes pas a +aa zhes bya /
NK109(dze)002:973: de ltar skye med gnyis sbyar ba'i gnas pa gzhi
NK109(dze)002:974: 'dzin gyi rang byung gi ye shes gnyis rang gi
NK109(dze)002:975: rgyud la ye nas 'du 'bral med par yod pas
NK109(dze)002:976: / rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyi sku
NK109(dze)002:977: rgyun 'dabs sbyor du dbang po'i yul du mngon par
NK109(dze)002:979: bsam pa'i zhen yul bcad pa'i tshig gnyis ni /
NK109(dze)002:980: de ltar ye nas gnas pa'i rig pa nyid /
NK109(dze)002:981: lung rgyud rang dag chen po 'gags pa med par
NK109(dze)002:982: shar pa la brten nas yang dag pas na ha
NK109(dze)002:983: h+aa / zhes gnas pa gzhi 'dzin gyi rang byung
NK109(dze)002:984: gi ye shes nyid la sgo lnga'i zhen yul 'gags
NK109(dze)002:985: pas yul can so so la gzigs gyi mtha' yod
NK109(dze)002:986: h+aa / pas dang / med pa snang ba dang
NK109(dze)002:987: stong pa la sogs pa dang bral bas rnam par
NK109(dze)002:988: rtog pa tha dad du 'dzin pa'i yul kun la
NK109(dze)002:989: rang bzhin ye dag tu 'das pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:990: dri ma dang bral ba nyid do //
NK109(dze)002:991: yid kyi rnam shes gcod par ston pa'i tshig gnyis ni /
NK109(dze)002:992: gnas pa gzhi 'dzin gyi rig pa skye ba med pa la /
NK109(dze)002:993: lam lhag mthong gi rig pa 'gags pa med par
NK109(dze)002:994: shar bas rnam rtog gi dri ma thams cad rang
NK109(dze)002:995: dag bas e h+aa zhes bya /
NK109(dze)002:996: gnas sa gzhi 'dzin gyi rang byung gi ye shes gnyis la /
NK109(dze)002:997: 'khrul pa gtan 'bebs kyi rang rtsis kyi tshig dang yi ge med pa /
NK109(dze)002:1000: 'byung ba rang gnad kyi rtsis med pas dang 'dzin
NK109(dze)002:1001: pa sems kyi rnam par rtog pa tha dad pa
NK109(dze)002:1002: las rang ngo cer mthong du 'dod pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1003: yin min gyi ltung ba dgags par bstan pa la tshig gnyis ni /
NK109(dze)002:1004: a skye ba med pa'i chos nyid ye nas gnas
NK109(dze)002:1005: pa de las rig pa skye ba med pa las
NK109(dze)002:1006: / 'gags med kyi cho 'phrul cir yang ston pas sngags kyi lam sna tshogs su snang bas +ae /
NK109(dze)002:1007: gnas pa gzhi 'dzin gyi rang byung gi ye shes gnyis la'o //
NK109(dze)002:1008: phyi rol du snang ba'i zhen yul yin no snyam pa shar /
NK109(dze)002:1009: nang gzung yul min no snyam pa gnyis dang bral bas /
NK109(dze)002:1010: skyon min pa'i phyogs spang ba dang yon tan yin
NK109(dze)002:1011: pa'i phyogs bsgrubs pa gnyis ka skyon yon du gyur
NK109(dze)002:1012: pas / yon tan btsal du ma rnyed par yin min gnyis ka las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1013: rig pa nyid mtha' gang du'ang ma ltung bar bstan pa'i tshig gnyis ni //
NK109(dze)002:1014: chos sku skye ba med pa la /
NK109(dze)002:1015: longs sku lam sna tshogs su shar nas //
NK109(dze)002:1016: sprul sku 'gags pa med par don byed pas na +aa /
NK109(dze)002:1017: de ltar shar nas don byed kyang /
NK109(dze)002:1018: yod pa'i mtha' dang med pa'i mtha' dang /
NK109(dze)002:1019: rtag chad kyi mtha' gang du'ang ma ltung bar gzhi las g.yos pa med pas ma /
NK109(dze)002:1020: de ltar gnas pas gzhi 'dzin gyi nga rang byung gi ye shes gnyis la /
NK109(dze)002:1021: thog mar 'khrul pa yod ma myong par ka nas dag pas yod pa'i mtha' ma ltung la /
NK109(dze)002:1022: da 'khrul mi srid pas med pa'i mthar ma ltung pas /
NK109(dze)002:1023: 'di kho na ltar yin bya ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:1024: chad par min bya ba'i mtha' gnyis las /
NK109(dze)002:1025: ngo bo ka dag pa'i ye shes su 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1026: chos las 'das par bstan pa'i tshig gnyis ni /
NK109(dze)002:1027: de ltar ka nas dag pa'i rang gi rig pa nyid ye dag tu bzhugs pas ha zhes bya /
NK109(dze)002:1028: de bla ma'i man ngag la brten nas rang dag
NK109(dze)002:1029: chos las 'das pas 'gags med kyi lam du byung
NK109(dze)002:1030: bas te / gnas pa gzhi 'dzin gyi nga rang byung gi ye shes nyid la /
NK109(dze)002:1031: tshig dang yi ger ris su bris pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1032: theg pa rim pa so sor phye ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:1036: 'bras bu nga bdag can gyi chos yod ma myong bas /
NK109(dze)002:1037: rtsa yi thabs la brten pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1038: rlung gi thabs la brten pa rnams las /
NK109(dze)002:1039: rang bzhin ye dag chen por 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1040: shes rab ngos bzung ba'i tshig gnyis ni /
NK109(dze)002:1041: rig pa'i ye shes nyid ye nas ka dag chen por bzhugs pa de /
NK109(dze)002:1042: shes rab phyin ci ma log pas lam ka dag
NK109(dze)002:1043: skye ba med par rtogs pa e ha zhes bya
NK109(dze)002:1044: la / gnas pa gzhi 'dzin gyi nga rang byung gi ye shes gnyis la /
NK109(dze)002:1045: rnam par rtog pa 'gyu byed rtog bcas kyi yid dang //
NK109(dze)002:1047: 'khrul pa de ma yin la der 'dzin gyi 'gyu byed gang yang med pas /
NK109(dze)002:1048: thos pas rang gi de nyid la sgra tshig dang bral ba dang //
NK109(dze)002:1049: bsam pa'i yul med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1050: bsgom pa'i don mi rnyed pa'i phyir /
NK109(dze)002:1051: shes rab gsum las 'dzin med kyi klong du 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1052: rig pa gnyis med du bstan pa la bcus bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)002:1053: snang stong shan phye ba tshig gcig gis bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1055: zhes pa ngo mtshar ba dang bcas pa'i tshig tu rang la rang bstan nas //
NK109(dze)002:1056: 'khor 'das gnyis 'dzin pa'i nga las stong pa dngos
NK109(dze)002:1057: po las log pa ste stong pa nyid bco brgyad
NK109(dze)002:1058: dang / snang ba bzung ba'i yul du snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:1059: zhen pa'i yul du snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:1060: yang dag pa'i snang ba dang gsum dang /
NK109(dze)002:1061: stong pa rnams ye nas ma spangs par rang gi rang bzhin gyis rdzogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1062: yul dang shes pa shan dbye ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1064: gnas lugs dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul rang gi shes pas bsdus pa dang //
NK109(dze)002:1065: snang thabs sems kyi byung tshor sna tshogs yul dngos
NK109(dze)002:1066: po dang bcas pas bsdus pa gnyis ma spangs par
NK109(dze)002:1067: sa bon myu gu'i tshul du rdzogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1068: yul sems shan dbye ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1069: 'khor 'das gnyis 'dzin gyi nga nyid la yul dngos pos bsdus pa'i yul dang /
NK109(dze)002:1070: shes pas bsdus pa'i yul dang sems dran pas bsdus pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1071: bag chags kyis bsdus pa gnyis rang gi rig pa
NK109(dze)002:1072: la ma spangs par rtsa ba dang yal ga'i tshul
NK109(dze)002:1075: shan dbye bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1079: phung po la sogs pa brten par byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1080: gcod pa yul dang shes pa gnas par byed pa
NK109(dze)002:1081: gnyis la ma spangs par rang grol du sbrul gyi
NK109(dze)002:1082: mdud pa'i tshul du rdzogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1083: rgyu 'bras shan dbye ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1085: sdig pa lus kyi sdig pa mi dge ba gsum dang /
NK109(dze)002:1088: de dag gi rnam smin ngan song gsum la sogs pa rnams /
NK109(dze)002:1089: dngos po'i 'dug tshul la ma spang par rang dag
NK109(dze)002:1090: tu 'o ma dang mar gyi tshul du rdzogs pa'o
NK109(dze)002:1092: dngos po shan dbye bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1094: gzhi thog ma ye gzhi dang /
NK109(dze)002:1095: bar gzhi lhun grub sna tshogs kyi gzhi dang /
NK109(dze)002:1096: gnas skabs lus kyi gzhi dang /
NK109(dze)002:1101: 'dzin pa snang ba'i dngos po gnyis ma spangs par
NK109(dze)002:1102: gnas dag tu gser dang ser po'i tshul du rdzogs
NK109(dze)002:1103: pa'o // rtog pa dang 'dzin pa shan dbye ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1105: yid la sogs pa nyon mongs bas bsdus pa'i rtog pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:1106: yid gnyis the tshom la sogs pa'i chos dang /
NK109(dze)002:1107: dngos po'i yul dngos por snang bas bsdus pa gnyis
NK109(dze)002:1108: ma spangs par ces dag tu dbang po dang yul
NK109(dze)002:1110: sgo lnga dang yul shan dbye ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1112: mig gis mthong bar byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1113: de bzhin du rna bas nyan par byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1114: snas snom par byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1115: lces myong bar byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1116: lus reg pas tshor bar byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1117: mig gis mthong pas gzugs sdug pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1118: mi sdug pa'i rnam par bcad pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1119: de bzhin rna ba la sogs pa'i gcod byed gnyis
NK109(dze)002:1120: ma spangs par rang bzhin du nyi ma dang 'od
NK109(dze)002:1122: shes rig dang stong pa shan dbye bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1125: log pa'i shes pa de ma yin la der 'dzin dang /
NK109(dze)002:1126: yang dag pa'i shes pa mtshan nyid gtan la 'bebs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1127: 'dzin pa zhes pa mthar thug dang bcas pa'i 'dzin pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1128: gzung ba'i yul tsam por 'dzin pa gnyis ma spang
NK109(dze)002:1129: par mthong dag tu bzhin me long gi tshul du
NK109(dze)002:1130: rdzogs pa'o // rig pa dang ma rig pa shan dbye bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1132: byed pa rig pa'i cho 'phrul sna tshogs par byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1133: 'jig pa ma rig pas yang dag pa'i lam 'jig
NK109(dze)002:1134: par byed par ni ma spangs par gzhi dag tu
NK109(dze)002:1135: / man shel dang 'od kyi tshul du rdzogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1136: rig pa nyid la phyi nang gi chos rdzogs par bstan pa ni bcu drug las /
NK109(dze)002:1137: chu bo bzhi'i rgyun bcad par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1138: kye ma zhes pa nges par sna gtad pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:1139: snang ba rang grol gyi nga la /
NK109(dze)002:1143: 'chi ba med pas 'gags pa phyi rol gyi yul
NK109(dze)002:1144: chos ni de nyid la spyod pa ma lus par
NK109(dze)002:1145: yongs su ljon shing lo 'dab rgyas pa ltar rdzogs
NK109(dze)002:1146: zhes pa'o // rig pa nyid la nyon mongs pa'i dri ma zad par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1147: snang ba rang grol gyi nga la phyi yul dang //
NK109(dze)002:1148: nang sems med pas rig pa nyid la nyon mongs
NK109(dze)002:1149: pa gang gis kyang ma bsgribs par zang thal bar
NK109(dze)002:1150: gsal bas chos ni de la spyod pa bzhin yongs
NK109(dze)002:1151: su rdzogs lugs ji ltar na nam mkha' dang nyi
NK109(dze)002:1153: lhag mthong skye bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1154: snang ba gyaranga grol nga la stong pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1155: dngos po las log pa rnams dang /
NK109(dze)002:1158: shes pas bsdus pa gnyis med pas /
NK109(dze)002:1159: snang ba rig pa'i ye shes lhag mthong du snang
NK109(dze)002:1160: ba'i chos de la spyod pa yongs su rdzogs lugs
NK109(dze)002:1162: ye shes kyi dngos po zag pa med pa rig pa'i snang ba bstan pa ni //
NK109(dze)002:1163: snang ba rang grol gyi nga la dmigs pa'i yul
NK109(dze)002:1164: 'di gcig pu yin zhes par gzung du med pas
NK109(dze)002:1165: / mthong tshad ye shes kyi snang ba zad pa med pa rig pa nyid la shar bas /
NK109(dze)002:1166: chos de la ni spyod pa yongs su rdzogs lugs me tog dang 'bras bu ltar rdzogs /
NK109(dze)002:1167: rang bzhin ngos bzung ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1168: snang ba rang grol gyi nga la /
NK109(dze)002:1170: khams dang skye mched kyis bsdus pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1171: sems byung tshor sna tshogs pa gnyis rang bzhin nyid la med pas /
NK109(dze)002:1172: gzhan la re ba med par /
NK109(dze)002:1175: de la spyod pa yongs su rdzogs lugs bzhin /
NK109(dze)002:1176: 'gags pa med pa rgya mtsho dang gza' skar ltar rdzogs /
NK109(dze)002:1177: bdag gzhan gyi 'khrul pa bcad par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1178: snang ba rang grol gyi nga la /
NK109(dze)002:1179: bdag las gud du 'dzin pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1181: sems las bsdus pa gnyis med pas rig pa nyid la chos lnga ste /
NK109(dze)002:1182: ye nas gnas pa'i don rig pas na rig pa /
NK109(dze)002:1183: rang gi de nyid de nyid kyis rig pas na rig pa /
NK109(dze)002:1184: gzhi 'dzin pa'i rig pa mi 'gyur bas rang rig pas rig pa /
NK109(dze)002:1185: lhag mthong gi rig pa lu gu rgyud nyid du rig pas rig pa /
NK109(dze)002:1186: snang ba sna tshogs pa'i don thams cad dus gcig
NK109(dze)002:1187: la rig pas na rig pa'i ches la yongs su
NK109(dze)002:1188: rdzogs pa ni / rang rig pa bdag gzhan mnyam par rig pas chu dang ri mo ltar rdzogs /
NK109(dze)002:1189: mi rtog pa ngos bzung bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1190: snang ba rang grol gyi nga la ye nas byed
NK109(dze)002:1191: rgyu med pas yul gzhan la mi 'jug cing shes
NK109(dze)002:1192: pa rang la gnas pa'i mi rtog pa'i bsam gtan
NK109(dze)002:1193: chen po / yongs su rdzogs lugs rang gnas cog
NK109(dze)002:1194: bzhag bzi pos lha khang du phyin pa ltar rdzogs
NK109(dze)002:1195: chen po / pa'o // sa'i nyes pa mngon sum
NK109(dze)002:1196: du spang zhing bsgrod pa med pa'i lam bstan pa
NK109(dze)002:1197: chen po / pa'o // ni / snang ba rang grol gyi nga la /
NK109(dze)002:1198: phyin par bya ba'i yul sa gcig bsgrod du med pas /
NK109(dze)002:1199: rang snang bsgrod pa med pa'i lam yul ni nam
NK109(dze)002:1200: mkha' la yongs su rdzogs lugs nam mkha' dang 'ja'
NK109(dze)002:1201: tshon ltar rdzogs / lta ba phyogs ris kyi mthong snang dag par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1202: snang ba rang grol gyi nga la /
NK109(dze)002:1204: ris theg pa rim pa dgu rang rang gi lta ba'i 'dod mi mthun pa med pas //
NK109(dze)002:1205: gsang ba theg pa thun mong ba rnams kyis mi
NK109(dze)002:1206: shes pa'i ye shes yongs su rdzogs lugs rig pa
NK109(dze)002:1207: mngon gsum gyi yul ltar rdzogs /
NK109(dze)002:1208: dag pa'i dbyings bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1209: snang ba rang grol gyi nga la /
NK109(dze)002:1210: dag pa ye shes kyi snang ba yon tan 'gags pa med par shar bas /
NK109(dze)002:1212: stong pa yangs shing gsal ba rig pa'i gnas yin pa gsum yongs su rdzogs lugs /
NK109(dze)002:1213: snang srid gzhir bzhengs gleng gzhi ltar rdzogs /
NK109(dze)002:1214: stong pa'i thig le bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1215: snang ba rang grol gyi nga la /
NK109(dze)002:1216: gcig gi mtha' dang dbus med pas /
NK109(dze)002:1217: gnyis su bsgrang bya med pas /
NK109(dze)002:1218: thig le nyag gcig mi 'gyur zhing brdal pa de la spyod pas /
NK109(dze)002:1219: chos rnams yongs su rdzogs lugs /
NK109(dze)002:1220: srid pa gsum ka dag pa gser g.ya' dang bral ba ltar rdzogs /
NK109(dze)002:1221: 'khor 'das gnyis med du bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1222: snang ba rang grol gyi nga la /
NK109(dze)002:1223: mun pa 'khor ba'i rnam par dang /
NK109(dze)002:1224: snang ba mya ngan las 'das pa gnyis med pas /
NK109(dze)002:1225: rig pa rdo rje'i lu gu rgyud mngon par snang ba la /
NK109(dze)002:1226: chos rnams ni de la spyod pa'i rdzogs lugs mngon
NK109(dze)002:1227: gsum du stong pa lam du khyer te bya dang
NK109(dze)002:1229: yul can stong pa ngos bzung bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1230: snang ba rang grol gyi nga la /
NK109(dze)002:1231: bdag yul du ma gcod pa'i mkhan po dang /
NK109(dze)002:1232: rtog pa de gnyis nges par 'dzin pa gnyis med pas /
NK109(dze)002:1233: stong pa nyid la spyod pas chos rnams ni yongs su rdzogs lugs dngos po dang /
NK109(dze)002:1234: dwangs ma nam mkha'i dkyil ltar rdzogs /
NK109(dze)002:1235: sgrib pa'i rtog pa zad de gsal ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1236: snang ba rang grol gyi nga la /
NK109(dze)002:1238: shes bya'i dri ma gnyis ye nas med pas /
NK109(dze)002:1239: gsal ba 'od lnga'i snang ba la spyod pas /
NK109(dze)002:1240: chos lnga yongs su rdzogs lugs rang snang rang byung nyi ma dang zer ltar rdzogs /
NK109(dze)002:1241: longs sku nyid ni snang ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1242: snang ba rang grol gyi nga la rnam par snang mdzad la sogs pa'i sku lnga rang snang bas /
NK109(dze)002:1243: zhing khams rnam par dag pa tshom bu snang ba la spyod pas /
NK109(dze)002:1244: chos nyid yongs su rdzogs lugs phra rags rang dag pa /
NK109(dze)002:1245: nam mkha' sprin dang bral ba ltar rdzogs /
NK109(dze)002:1246: bskyed rim gyi gol sa bcad par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1247: snang ba rang grol gyi nga la /
NK109(dze)002:1248: yi ge'i tshogs spro ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:1249: tshur bsdu ba'i rtsol ba med pas /
NK109(dze)002:1251: yi ge ltar mi dgos pas /
NK109(dze)002:1252: don rang bzhin rtsa gnas kyi yi ge rnams yongs
NK109(dze)002:1253: su rdzogs lugs 'od kyi gong bu kun tu bzang
NK109(dze)002:1254: po yab yum dang bcas pa /
NK109(dze)002:1255: nyung 'bru la mar ltar rdzogs te bskyed mii dgos pa'i lha rang chas pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1256: rig pa'i che ba bstan pa la gsum gyi dang po /
NK109(dze)002:1257: rig pa gcig pu'i ye shes bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1258: nga ni 'gran pa'i zla med kun las rgyal ba yin /
NK109(dze)002:1259: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:1260: nga ni 'khrul pa rang log gi nga zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)002:1261: ma rig pa'i la sogs pa'i zla med pas nyon mongs pa kun las rgyal ba ste /
NK109(dze)002:1262: rig pa'i ye shes phyogs med du shar ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:1263: 'khrul pa rang log pa'i nga la /
NK109(dze)002:1264: lus ngag gi bcos pa'i tshig med pa lta ba
NK109(dze)002:1265: kun las 'phags pa ste mngon sum du mthong ba
NK109(dze)002:1266: yin / 'khrul pa rang log pa'i nga ni mngon
NK109(dze)002:1267: gsum gyi ye shes de yid dpyod kyi btsal kyang
NK109(dze)002:1268: mi rnyed cing sus kyang mthong ba'i yul med pa
NK109(dze)002:1269: yin / ste / 'o na yang med pa ma
NK109(dze)002:1270: yin te 'khor 'das thams cad la khyab pa yin
NK109(dze)002:1271: yin / ste / / 'khrul pa rang log pa'i nga ni /
NK109(dze)002:1272: 'khor bar gnas pa ma yin te /
NK109(dze)002:1273: sa gcig la brten pa med kyang /
NK109(dze)002:1274: snang ba'i rkyen kun la brten pa yin pas rkyen gang gis kyang grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:1275: 'khrul pa rang log gi nga ni stong pa dngos ma yin te /
NK109(dze)002:1276: sems las 'das shing dri ma med pa'i rig pa'i sgron ma kun la mtshon du btub pa yin /
NK109(dze)002:1277: 'khrul pa rang log pa'i nga ni /
NK109(dze)002:1278: dran pa'i yid drug 'dus pa med kyang snang ba
NK109(dze)002:1279: kun la rang bzhin gyis 'jug par byed pa yin
NK109(dze)002:1280: no // re dogs kyi 'phrang bsal bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1281: 'khrul pa rang log pa'i nga ni /
NK109(dze)002:1282: 'khor ba la dogs pa med la /
NK109(dze)002:1283: 'das pa la re ba nyid med pas /
NK109(dze)002:1284: ji ltar dpyad kyang rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don las ma 'das pas /
NK109(dze)002:1285: kun la yangs te rnam grangs brgya stong gang ltar dpyad kyang me tog skye ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:1286: 'khrul pa rang log pa'i nga ni /
NK109(dze)002:1287: ngan song gsum du lhung gi dogs pa'i g.yang sa med cing //
NK109(dze)002:1288: 'od zer lnga'i bdag nyid du gnas shing /
NK109(dze)002:1289: kun gyi mig las 'phro ba yin /
NK109(dze)002:1290: 'khrul pa rang log pa'i nga ni ma rig pa
NK109(dze)002:1291: rkyen bzhi dang bcas pa'i 'khrul pa'i yul med kyang
NK109(dze)002:1292: / gdul bya so so'i snang ba chen por ye nas gnas pa yin /
NK109(dze)002:1293: 'khrul pa rang log pa'i nga ni dpyad pa'i rgyu ye nas yod ma myong yang /
NK109(dze)002:1294: dngos po gshis lam kun ltar spyod pa ma 'gags pa yin no //
NK109(dze)002:1295: dngos po gcig dang du ma las 'das par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1296: 'khrul pa rang log pa'i nga ni dngos po gshis
NK109(dze)002:1297: su gcig dang du ma bral bas phyin par bya
NK109(dze)002:1298: ba'i gnas sam / yul log na med kyang rig
NK109(dze)002:1299: pa nyid ye nas skyon kun las pha rol phyin
NK109(dze)002:1300: ba'i gnas sam / nas yod pa'o // 'khrul pa
NK109(dze)002:1301: rang log pa'i nga ni bya ba'i yul dang 'jug
NK109(dze)002:1302: ba'i gnas sam / nas yod pa'o // tu med / byed pa dngos po dang /
NK109(dze)002:1304: snang ba bzhi'am brgyad so sor snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:1305: rig pa'i sna nga tshul bstan pa la drug yod pa la /
NK109(dze)002:1306: dang po 'khrul pa'i sku gsung thugs ngos bzung bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1307: thams cad ni yod pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1312: sems ni 'byung ba ma rig pa'i gzhi yin la /
NK109(dze)002:1313: 'khrul pa ni rkyen bzhi'i dmigs pa ma dag pa las /
NK109(dze)002:1314: snang ba'i tshogs du ma byung bas /
NK109(dze)002:1315: 'khrul pa 'byung tshul gyi nga yi sems ni bsam pa ma 'gags pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1316: snang ba la sogs pa'i thams cad la gnas pa
NK109(dze)002:1317: 'khrul snang gi 'khrul pa khyab tshul gyi nga'i thugs
NK109(dze)002:1319: yod pa dang med pa la sogs pa thams cad
NK109(dze)002:1320: snang bar byed pa'i 'khrul pa'i snang ba khyab tshul
NK109(dze)002:1321: gyi nga yi sku rags pas du ma'o //
NK109(dze)002:1322: yod pa dang med pa thams cad la grags pa
NK109(dze)002:1323: 'khrul snang gi 'khrul pa khyab tshul gyii nga'i gsungs
NK109(dze)002:1325: de dag la nyams su blang bya dang sbyar na
NK109(dze)002:1326: mi rtog rlung gi bsam gtan la brten nas dran
NK109(dze)002:1327: bsam chos kyi sku la sbyar ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:1328: dngos po dmigs rten la bslab nas rags pa'i snang ba stong nyid du la bzla ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:1329: yi ge ba brda' sbyor la brten nas /
NK109(dze)002:1330: sgra tshig sngags kyi bzlas par bya ba'i gnad do //
NK109(dze)002:1331: rnam shes tshogs drug ngos bzung bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1332: mthong ba ni dbang pos gzugs ma 'gags par /
NK109(dze)002:1333: 'khrul pa khyab tshul gyi nga'i gzugs sdug pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1336: snang ba'i yul ma 'gags pa las sgra snyan pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1337: mi snyan pa ltar grags par shar /
NK109(dze)002:1339: snang ba'i yul 'khrul pa khyab tshul gyi nga'i dri zhim pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1340: mi zhim par tshor bar shar /
NK109(dze)002:1342: lce'i yul 'khrul ba khyab tshul gyi nga'i ro'i bye brag ltar bda' bar shar /
NK109(dze)002:1345: nga yi yid kyi rnam shes /
NK109(dze)002:1346: tshor ba bde sdug btang snyoms ltar mgyogs par shar ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:1347: de dag kyang nyams su blang bya dang /
NK109(dze)002:1349: sgo lnga'i rang zhen bzlog pa gzugs kyi dmigs rten la brten nas bslab pas /
NK109(dze)002:1350: dngos po snang ba 'gags pa'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)002:1351: sgra'i dmigs rten la brten nas bslab pas chos nyid
NK109(dze)002:1352: brjod pa med pa'i don rtogs pa'i man ngag dang
NK109(dze)002:1353: / dri'i dmigs rten la brten nas bslab pas rang
NK109(dze)002:1354: snang bde ba chen por 'char ba'i man ngag dang
NK109(dze)002:1355: / / ro'i dmigs rten la brten nas bslab pas
NK109(dze)002:1356: 'khrul snang nyams su myong bar rang 'char ba'i man
NK109(dze)002:1357: / / ngag dang / chos ni bla ma'i man
NK109(dze)002:1358: ngag de rnams la brten nas bslab pas 'khrul snang
NK109(dze)002:1359: rang log par 'gyur ba'i man ngag go /
NK109(dze)002:1360: de'i phyir na rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i yo
NK109(dze)002:1361: gis tshogs drug lhug pa rang yan du bzhag pas
NK109(dze)002:1363: nyon mongs pa rang grol du bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1364: phyi nyon mongs pa 'byung ba bzhi la mthar 'dzin pa'i shes pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1365: nang gi nyon mongs ba 'dod chags zhe sdang gti
NK109(dze)002:1366: mug nga rgyal phrag dog dug lnga la bdag tu
NK109(dze)002:1368: gsang ba'i nyon mongs pa sgo'i lnga'i yul zhen gyi
NK109(dze)002:1369: shes pa thams cad rdo rje'i sems dpa' rtogs pa
NK109(dze)002:1370: rang byung gi nga'i cho 'phrul lam /
NK109(dze)002:1373: sangs rgyas dang sems can gnyis //
NK109(dze)002:1374: rdo rje sems dpa' rtog pa rang byung gi nga
NK109(dze)002:1375: nyid la 'byung bas na dur sa yin ces pa'o
NK109(dze)002:1376: // de ltar kun byed pa'i mkhan po ni /
NK109(dze)002:1377: rtogs pa rang byung gi nga yin kyang /
NK109(dze)002:1378: kho'i ngo bo la g.yos pa med par snang bar
NK109(dze)002:1379: rang gsal du ye thog ma nas rdzogs pa chen
NK109(dze)002:1380: por bzhugs so // de ltar nga bdud du shar
NK109(dze)002:1381: ba'i rig pa nyid nyams su blang bya dang sbyar
NK109(dze)002:1382: por bzhugs so // na / nga'i dngos po ngos bzung ba'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)002:1383: nga yul dbyung ba'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)002:1384: nga brtson du bzung ba'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)002:1385: nga bsad pa'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)002:1386: nga gtong ba'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)002:1387: nga'i rtsa ba bcad cing dngos po spur ba'i man ngag dang /
NK109(dze)002:1388: nga rang sor bzhag pa'i gdams ngag dang bdun gyis /
NK109(dze)002:1389: nga bdag gi zhen yul bcad pa'i gnad do //
NK109(dze)002:1390: thog ma'i gzhi la 'khrul tshul bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1391: de ltar nga bdun gyii snang ba med pa'i dus na //
NK109(dze)002:1392: dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul ka dag pa'i ye shes rang snang bar bzhugs te /
NK109(dze)002:1393: ngo bo ye dag tu yod pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1394: rang bzhin rang dag tu yod pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1395: thugs rje gong ma gnyis kyi shugs dag tu yod pas /
NK109(dze)002:1396: ka nas dag pa'i gzhi yin la /
NK109(dze)002:1397: de yang ngo bo ye dag du yod pa'i gnad kyis /
NK109(dze)002:1398: 'khrul dang ma 'khrul gang du yang med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1399: rang bzhin rang dag tu yod pa'i gnad kyis /
NK109(dze)002:1400: ma rig pa rkyen bzhi dang bcas pas gos pa med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1401: thugs rje shugs dag gi gnad kyis /
NK109(dze)002:1402: 'char byed shes pa sga ma 'gags pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1403: de ltar gnas pa'i thog ma'i gzhi de las 'khrul
NK109(dze)002:1404: pa nyid ma grub par rang bzhin ye dag tu
NK109(dze)002:1405: yod kyang / gzhi dang gzhi'i shes pa'i khyad par las dus kyi tshe zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)002:1406: kyi ni 'brel pa'i tshig yin pas /
NK109(dze)002:1407: lhun grub byung khung yon tan gyi rtsal ma 'gags pa la /
NK109(dze)002:1408: ngo bo sku grub pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1409: rang bzhin 'od du grub pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1410: thugs rje zer du grub pa las /
NK109(dze)002:1411: yon tan skyon du gyur te /
NK109(dze)002:1412: rgyu bdag nyid gcig pa'i ma rig pa ngo bo'i rtsal du shar ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:1413: lhan skyes kyi ma rig pa /
NK109(dze)002:1414: rang bzhin gyi rtsal du shar ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:1415: kun du btags pa'i ma rig pa thugs rje'i rtsal du shar ba las /
NK109(dze)002:1416: rgyu'i rkyen ma rig pa gsum 'dus pa dang //
NK109(dze)002:1419: bdag po'i rkyen yul las 'khrul te /
NK109(dze)002:1420: de ma yin pa la der 'dzin gyi shes pa
NK109(dze)002:1421: thag pa la sbrul du bzung ba lta bu dang
NK109(dze)002:1422: / de la dag pa ngo bo dang /
NK109(dze)002:1424: thugs rje gsum gyi bzhugs tshul /
NK109(dze)002:1425: ma dag par 'khrul pas yul so sor shar ba la gcod pa byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1426: yul so so la myur du 'jug pas mgyogs pa zhes bya la /
