NK109(dze)002:1428: kun tu 'tshol byed kyi yid kyis yul dum bur
NK109(dze)002:1429: bcad de dkar po la sogs pa'i rnam pa so
NK109(dze)002:1430: sor bzung / gtan la 'bebs pa'i yid kyis de dag gtan la phab pas /
NK109(dze)002:1431: 'od rnams gong gi bas mi gsal ba /
NK109(dze)002:1432: mog ge ba lnga'i cha las /
NK109(dze)002:1435: de nas nges par 'jog pa'i yid kyis nges pa can du bcad pas /
NK109(dze)002:1437: drod gsher las skyes pa gnyis byung //
NK109(dze)002:1438: 'di dag gi tshe 'gro na yang phan tshun du 'gro /
NK109(dze)002:1439: 'dug na yang nam mkha' la 'dug pa las /
NK109(dze)002:1441: gos la sogs par yang mi dgos /
NK109(dze)002:1442: 'dod chags la sogs pa'i nyon mongs pa la yang /
NK109(dze)002:1443: dngos su spyod pa med de /
NK109(dze)002:1445: nyi zla la sogs pa yang med de rang 'od la 'dug go /
NK109(dze)002:1446: de nas yid kyi rnam par shes pas /
NK109(dze)002:1447: shes pa du ma 'dus pa'i tshogs su bcad pas /
NK109(dze)002:1448: 'dod chags la sogs pa yang bltas pas tshim pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1450: bcang ba rnams rim par 'byung nas nyon mongs par rags su song /
NK109(dze)002:1451: de tsa na sa chu me rlung gi 'byung ba'i snang ba shar nas /
NK109(dze)002:1452: zas kyang ma rmos pa'i 'bras sa lu dang /
NK109(dze)002:1455: khrus kyi rdzing bu la sogs pa'i 'dod pa'i yon tan dang /
NK109(dze)002:1456: 'jag skyil la sogs pa byung ste mngal las skyes pa byung ngo //
NK109(dze)002:1457: de nas nyon mongs pa can gyi yid kyis /
NK109(dze)002:1458: nga bdag tu yul so sor bcad pas de dag kyang nub nas /
NK109(dze)002:1459: tshe lo yang brgyad khri la thug 'dod chags kyang 'khyud pa la sogs pa byung /
NK109(dze)002:1460: gzugs kyang tha dad par smin nas /
NK109(dze)002:1461: zas su shing thog bzang po za zhing gos kyang ras bal dang shing shun gon ba /
NK109(dze)002:1462: gzugs dang bong tshod mang por byung ngo //
NK109(dze)002:1463: de nas 'gyu byed 'dzin pa'i yid rtog pa dang bcas pas sna tshogs su bcad pas bdag dang /
NK109(dze)002:1465: nga yi dang kho'i la sogs pa byung nas rmo sko'i las dang ri khyim dang /
NK109(dze)002:1466: las mi dge ba bcu spyad pas ngan song la sogs par snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:1467: yul tha dad par ma 'gags pas /
NK109(dze)002:1468: yid drug 'dus pa'i dran byed sna tshogs ma 'gags pa las /
NK109(dze)002:1469: dbang po tshogs drug tu yid drug smin nas so so'i yul tha dad pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1470: snang ba thams cad la yid drug gi rnam par
NK109(dze)002:1471: rtog pa'i tshogs lhug par shar nas de la 'jol
NK109(dze)002:1473: de yang 'di'i dus na gong gi nga badunapo'i snang bar snang ba yin no //
NK109(dze)002:1474: de ltar 'gro ba ris drug skye ba bzhis bsdus nas snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:1475: thog ma'i ka dag ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje
NK109(dze)002:1476: gsum gyi gnas tshul ngo ma shes pa las byung
NK109(dze)002:1477: ba'o // ye shes ma bu 'phrad pa'i rtags bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1478: de ltar gnas pa'i skyes bu de ni 'khrul zin
NK109(dze)002:1479: nas gong du skye ba bzhi las bskyed cing grub
NK109(dze)002:1480: pas / tha ma rgas pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1482: 'chi ba gsum las 'gro sa med pas /
NK109(dze)002:1483: de yang rdzus pa ni rlung gis 'byung bas skyed pas rlung du grub /
NK109(dze)002:1486: mngal chu'i 'byung ba bzhi las bskyed cing grub pas /
NK109(dze)002:1487: skyes bu rkyen gyis 'chi ba yin par tshe zadanasa tshe'i dus byed pa'i dus na /
NK109(dze)002:1488: 'byung ba bzhi po'i stobs so so la thim pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1489: sa sa la thim pas lus lci ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:1490: chu chu la thim pas kha chu dang sna chu 'bru ba /
NK109(dze)002:1491: me me la thim pas lus kyi mtha' nas drod 'chor zhing kha sna skam /
NK109(dze)002:1492: rlung rnam par shes pa la thim pas /
NK109(dze)002:1493: lus kyi stobs shor nas ldang mi nus pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1494: dbugs ngar ngar dang shang shang por 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)002:1495: rnam par shes pa nam mkha' la thim nas /
NK109(dze)002:1496: phyi nang gi dbugs chad de /
NK109(dze)002:1498: thim thim myogs myogs su gyur pa yin /
NK109(dze)002:1499: nam mkha' 'od gsal la thim pa'i dus su phyi nang gi dbugs kyi 'gyu byed chad nas /
NK109(dze)002:1501: rig pa rlung dang bcas nas chos nyid kyi bar ma dor 'gro ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:1502: thog ma med pa'i rlung gi srog 'dzin pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1506: snying rje med pa bskal pa las kyi rlung dang lngas /
NK109(dze)002:1507: rig pa'i ye shes bskyod nas chos nyid rnam par
NK109(dze)002:1508: dag pa'i pho brang la bkod par chos nyid kyi
NK109(dze)002:1509: klong du snang bar sngar gyi 'byung ba lnga'i snang
NK109(dze)002:1510: ba la rgya yis btab nas ye shes lnga yi
NK109(dze)002:1512: ye nas ngo bo ka dag pa'i rtsal du byung
NK109(dze)002:1513: ba'i rnam par snang mdzad kyi sku lnga la sogs
NK109(dze)002:1514: pa yab yum 'du 'bral med par snang bar 'gyur
NK109(dze)002:1515: / 'di'i dus su sngar bla mas bstan pa'i thabs
NK109(dze)002:1516: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i snang ba la ma
NK109(dze)002:1517: / zhen na // grol ba yin pas dran nas
NK109(dze)002:1518: snang ba lhug par mdzes pa las ma zhen par
NK109(dze)002:1520: de la chags pa med pa'i sku gong gi lnga po /
NK109(dze)002:1521: rang gi rig pa la phyi nang med par gsal ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:1522: de yang cir snang 'od du shar zhing /
NK109(dze)002:1523: de'i nang du sku lnga lnga so so'i tshom bur
NK109(dze)002:1524: shar bas yangs chen dag pa'i sku rang la mnga'
NK109(dze)002:1525: bas / thog ma'i ka dag gang gi ngo bor yang ma grub pa /
NK109(dze)002:1526: stong pa nyid chen po'i snang ba rang la shar nas /
NK109(dze)002:1527: lhun grub kyi skyon yon tan du grub pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1528: rig pa rang sa zin par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1529: de dag la yang rang snang du ngo shes pas sa lam bsgrod cing rtsol sgrub byar med par /
NK109(dze)002:1530: skad cig ma gsum la thog ma'i gzhi la rang log te /
NK109(dze)002:1531: phyin pa med pa'i gnas su pha rol ni /
NK109(dze)002:1532: lhun grub kyi snang ba las 'das te phyin pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1533: stong pa nyid chen po'i spyod yul rang la 'di'i dus na gsal bas /
NK109(dze)002:1534: rnam par rtog pa med pa'i sangs rgyas thig le nyag gcig gis rang rig pas rang mthong pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1535: 'di yang byas shing rtsol sgrub las byung ba ma yin te /
NK109(dze)002:1538: phung po lnga'i zhen pa'i thag pa yid drug gis
NK109(dze)002:1539: dran pa bcad pas ma rig pa gnyis la sogs
NK109(dze)002:1540: pa sangs nas sku dang ye shes su rgyas pas
NK109(dze)002:1541: // de las kyang sku rang gi rig pa nyag
NK109(dze)002:1542: gcig rdo rje lu gu rgyud gcig gis ka dag
NK109(dze)002:1543: // brgyan pa'o // de ltar ye nas yod pa'i
NK109(dze)002:1544: don 'di shes pas 'khor ba las theg pa thun
NK109(dze)002:1546: de las a ti khyad par 'phags pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1547: lta ba'i gnas lugs bstan pa la bcu gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)002:1548: shes rab kyis nyon mongs pa bcad par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1549: kye ma ni nges par bos pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:1550: bsad pa nyon mongs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1551: nga bdun po de bsad pas /
NK109(dze)002:1552: 'khor ba'i rgyud shes rab kyis bcad pa'i las de
NK109(dze)002:1553: la brten nas dga' ba skye bas na rang gi
NK109(dze)002:1554: snang ba chen po gsal ba yin no //
NK109(dze)002:1555: 'khor 'das gnyis med kyi lta ba nges par bzung ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1557: 'gro drug thams cad rang bcad cing bsgral na rang
NK109(dze)002:1558: gi rig pa'i snang ba las dang phrad pa yin
NK109(dze)002:1559: pas 'khor ba dang myang 'das gnyis su med pa'o
NK109(dze)002:1560: // rgya mtsho gting zab kyi gdam ngag ngos bzung bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1561: rgyu pha rol du phyin pa drug dang /
NK109(dze)002:1562: 'bras bu tshogs gnyis rtsad nas bcad na /
NK109(dze)002:1563: pha rol du phyin pa rgyu drug gi rtsal du /
NK109(dze)002:1564: sku gnyis su rang gi lus ngag yid gsum 'byongs ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:1565: snang ba kha sbyor gyi gdams ngag ngos bzung ba ston te /
NK109(dze)002:1566: 'di yi dus su dge ba'i las la sogs pa ci yang mi byed par rgyun thag bcad nas /
NK109(dze)002:1567: phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi bya ba btang nas /
NK109(dze)002:1568: sgron ma la bltas pas rang snang zin pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1569: ye shes rang yan gyi gdams ngag ngos bzung ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:1570: de ltar bya ba ci yang mi byed par gnas
NK109(dze)002:1571: pas phyi rol gyi snang ba rgya yis theb te
NK109(dze)002:1572: / rig pa lu gu rgyud mngon gsum mthong bas nye ste ye shes rang yan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1573: snang ba dbang sdud kyi man ngag ngos bzung ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:1574: lu gu rgyud rgyun 'dabs sbyor du mthong bas de la sems bzung mi dgos /
NK109(dze)002:1575: theg pa thun mong gi lta ba mi dgos /
NK109(dze)002:1576: sgom du med pa de nyid chos sku dngos yin pas so //
NK109(dze)002:1577: 'khor 'das rgya theg gi man ngag ngos bzung ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:1578: de ltar rig pa la snang ba nyams gong 'phel dang //
NK109(dze)002:1580: rang gi nyams lta ba'i rtsal gsum 'byongs pas na snang ba thams cad sku'i klong du 'gyur /
NK109(dze)002:1581: snang ba rang grol gyi gdams ngag ngos bzung ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:1582: de yang mig dang nam mkha' dang /
NK109(dze)002:1583: rig pa gsum la bral bar /
NK109(dze)002:1584: de gsum gyi bya byed g.yeng ba med pas chos nyid bde ba chen po'i sa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1585: ye shes gsum sbyor gyi gdam ngag gsum ni /
NK109(dze)002:1586: rnal 'byor pas grogs med par gcig pur 'dug la rig pa dal bar gnas pa las /
NK109(dze)002:1587: lus zang thal du mthong ba dang //
NK109(dze)002:1588: 'byung ba lnga la dbang bsgyur dang /
NK109(dze)002:1589: zas dang gos kyi 'du shes dang bral ba'i rtsal gsum lus la 'byung ngo //
NK109(dze)002:1590: ngo bo zang thal gyi man ngag ngos bzung ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:1591: snang ba ci ltar snang yang /
NK109(dze)002:1592: thad kar rig pa ye shes kyi grogs su shes na /
NK109(dze)002:1593: de nyid cog gi bzhag pas ngo bo zang thal chig rdzogs kyi nga zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:1594: tshogs drug lhug pa'i man ngag ngos bzung ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:1596: rgyun du gnas na de las gzhan ci zhig kyang bya mi dgos so //
NK109(dze)002:1597: de nga'i rang bzhin bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1598: de ltar sems can snang ba chen po de ni /
NK109(dze)002:1599: yang dag par gnas pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:1600: bla ma'i man ngag med pa la snang ba ma nus pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1601: gsang ba nyan thos la sogs pa la'o //
NK109(dze)002:1602: sngags rang gi ye shes kyis skal ldan skyobs cig /
NK109(dze)002:1603: dngos po rdo rje lu gu rgyud de nyid rang yin pa las gzhan med do //
NK109(dze)002:1605: gong du bstan pa'i don bcur byas nas bstan pa la bya /
NK109(dze)002:1606: yi ge med pa la sogs pa mtshan gyi skabs su bshad zin /
NK109(dze)002:1607: rjes su rgyud 'di'i gong du sgra thal 'gyur gyi rgyud bstan pas de'i rjes su gsungs pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1608: gleng gzhi ni thun mong dang /
NK109(dze)002:1610: le'u ni gzhung gi don nges par gcod cing ston pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1611: dang po ni gzhung 'di nyid kyi thog ma'i le'u bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1612: pad+ma kha 'byed las le'u dang po'i pad+ma kha dbye ba bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1613: &ath+ya t+ya&a&ah&a&a&a da ni le'u gnyis pa'i tshig gi don pad+ma kha dbye ba ltar bshad pas ston te /
NK109(dze)002:1614: 'di la bsdus pa'i don bdun du shes par bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:1615: don dang po dgongs pa las bskul te zhus pas
NK109(dze)002:1616: snang bar bstan pa la gnyis las zhu ba'i rang
NK109(dze)002:1618: de nas le'u dang po gsungs pa /
NK109(dze)002:1619: de nas rgyud kyi ston pa drug pa rdo rje
NK109(dze)002:1620: 'chang gis rig pa chos thams cad kyi rang bzhin
NK109(dze)002:1621: gang yang ma 'gags par gsal ba'i dgongs pa ni
NK109(dze)002:1622: rnam rtog gis mi byed par snyoms par ni gnyis
NK109(dze)002:1623: su med par bzhugs so ni /
NK109(dze)002:1625: zhes ni dus de tsam na med bzhin du nyid
NK109(dze)002:1626: la nyid sprul pa'i snang ba'i bdag pos ni yid
NK109(dze)002:1627: kyis 'di ston pa nyid dgongs pa la zhugs pa
NK109(dze)002:1628: de'i don ji lta bu zhig yin snyam nas the
NK109(dze)002:1629: tshom skyes pas / 'di skad du zhes zhus so ni ston pa la'o //
NK109(dze)002:1630: rgyu bstan pa ni kye ma zhes ston pa la
NK109(dze)002:1631: nges par bos na rig pa ni don mkhyen la
NK109(dze)002:1632: sngon du lu gu rgyud kyi sku rnam par dag
NK109(dze)002:1633: pa chen po las byung ba'i ston pa rdo rje
NK109(dze)002:1635: yang ni mnan pa'i tshig ste /
NK109(dze)002:1636: rig pa de nyid thog ma ye dag tu yod pa la /
NK109(dze)002:1637: da de'i don rtogs par byas pas yang dag par
NK109(dze)002:1638: rdzogs pa'i zhes 'khor 'das thams cad 'khor rtog pa
NK109(dze)002:1639: sangs pas snang ba rang 'phel du rgyas kyi rig
NK109(dze)002:1640: pa gzhi 'dzin pa dang lhag mthong gi dgongs pa
NK109(dze)002:1641: de gnyis dang mi 'bral ba'i bzhag pa chen po
NK109(dze)002:1642: de lus ngag gi gnad ji ltar bgyi bdag la
NK109(dze)002:1643: gsung du gsol // zhes ston pa la zhus so //
NK109(dze)002:1644: lan bka' stsal pa gsum kyis bstan pa las rig
NK109(dze)002:1645: pa'i ye shes dngos kyi gnas lugs bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)002:1646: / de rnams zhus ma thag pa'i /
NK109(dze)002:1647: de nas gnas lugs dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul
NK109(dze)002:1648: las rig pa'i rol pa snang thabs su ma shar
NK109(dze)002:1649: ba'i 'khor la bka' phyin ci ma log pa 'di
NK109(dze)002:1650: rtsal ba rna ba'i dbang po la /
NK109(dze)002:1651: rtsal lugs ji ltar rtsal na kye ma zhes bos
NK109(dze)002:1652: nas snang rgyud dngos po grub pa med kyang snang
NK109(dze)002:1653: ba ltar byung ba'i 'khor rnams nyon cig /
NK109(dze)002:1654: ces nyan par rna gtad cing bskul nas /
NK109(dze)002:1655: ngas dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul gyi sgrib pa phyi'i rdul dang rdul phran dang /
NK109(dze)002:1656: nang gi nyon mongs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1657: gsang ba'i tshig gi dbang po la skyon med pa'i
NK109(dze)002:1658: phyogs kyis rdo rje lu gu rgyud bltas pas ma
NK109(dze)002:1659: sgrib pa'i snang pa'i chos nyid bstan pa kun gyi
NK109(dze)002:1660: snying po khyed la bstan gyis /
NK109(dze)002:1661: shin tu lus ngag yid 'khrul pa'i snang ba la
NK109(dze)002:1662: ma yengs bar nyon cig ces nyan pa'i skyon bsal
NK109(dze)002:1663: nas rtsa ba'i dgongs pa chen po'i grangs ni zhes
NK109(dze)002:1664: pa rtsa ba thams cad bsdus pa'i dgongs pa sems
NK109(dze)002:1665: nyid rnal du 'bebs pa chen po gzhan gyis dpag
NK109(dze)002:1666: par dka' ba'i chos kyi rnam grangs ni ri bo
NK109(dze)002:1667: cog bzhag dang / rgya mtsho cog bzhag dang /
NK109(dze)002:1669: snang ba cer bzhag dang bzhis chos nyid kyi don gtan la 'bebs par 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)002:1670: rang bzhin gyi che ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1671: 'di nyid shes bya ma yin par nyams su blang bya dang sbyar na /
NK109(dze)002:1672: sngon du bla ma dag pa la slob ma dad
NK109(dze)002:1673: pa dang ldan pa gcig gis gdams pa zhus nas
NK109(dze)002:1675: 'khor ba las yid dbyung bas rang gi bla ma
NK109(dze)002:1676: la 'khor gsum yongs su dag par bya ba dang
NK109(dze)002:1677: / de yang rigs kyi bu zhes bya dang /
NK109(dze)002:1678: de nas 'jig rten gyi bya ba btang nas bsgrub dgos te /
NK109(dze)002:1679: de yang le'u dang po nas phyi nang bya ba
NK109(dze)002:1680: btang na snang ba rgya yis thebs zhes pa dang
NK109(dze)002:1681: / le'u 'di nas kyang phyi nang gi bya ba dang bral bar bya ste zhes pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1682: de nas 'jig rten 'di yis longs spyod spangs la snying po'i don la lta ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:1683: le'u drug pa nas phyi'i longs spyod la ma chags par zhes pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1684: de nas grol yul gyi rkyen dang bral bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK109(dze)002:1685: rang gi yul rkyen gyis mi gnod pa'i dgon par song la /
NK109(dze)002:1686: phyi nang gi 'brel pa bcad pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1687: 'di nyid las grong chen po las 'das te nags
NK109(dze)002:1688: kyi klong chen po'i dgon par gnas par gyis shig
NK109(dze)002:1689: ces pa dang / de lta bu'i dgon pa yul
NK109(dze)002:1690: rkyen gyis mi gnod pa'i gnas su grogs spangs te
NK109(dze)002:1691: rang gcig pur nyams su blang ba yang le'u drug
NK109(dze)002:1692: pa nas grong spangs la zhes pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1693: dang po las gcig pu las dal bar 'dug na rtsal gsum lus las 'byung zhes pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1694: de nas sngon du 'gro ba lus ngag gi spyod pa bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1696: kye sku yi snang ba ma 'gags pas /
NK109(dze)002:1697: gsung gi rol pa cir yang ston /
NK109(dze)002:1698: sems kyi rtog pa sna tshogs pa zhes pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1699: dang po las kyang thams cad 'khrul snang nga'i sku /
NK109(dze)002:1700: thams cad grags pa 'khrul snang nga'i gsung /
NK109(dze)002:1701: thams cad 'byung bzhi'i 'khrul snang nga'i sems zhes pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1702: de nas rnal du 'bebs pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1703: le'u gsum pa nas thugs kyi mdzad pa ci yang med /
NK109(dze)002:1704: drug pa las brda dang tha snyad yi ge'i tshogs spangs te ces pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1706: nga la spro zhing bsdu med pa zhes pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1707: de nas lus ngag gi gnad ni /
NK109(dze)002:1708: lus 'dug stangs gsum las ma g.yos pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1709: ngag smra ba bcad pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1710: yid rang gi de nyid dang mi 'bral bar ston pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1711: rang gi 'dug tshul gyi de bzhin nyid la gnas par bya ste zhes pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1712: lnga pa nas brjod pa thams cad ngang gis med ces pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1713: 'di nyid las spyod par spyad pa chen po de dang ma bral na zhes pas bstan to //
NK109(dze)002:1714: de nas dngos gzhi zag pa med pa'i ye shes de sgo gang la snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:1715: yul gang la gtad de nyams su blang ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:1716: 'di nyid las mig zur nyid las dbyings 'byung bas zhes pa dang //
NK109(dze)002:1718: mig ni nam mkha'i khams gsum brtag /
NK109(dze)002:1720: de yang nam mkha'i ngang las shes par bya zhes pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1721: gting dpag med pa'i rgya mtsho chen po nas /
NK109(dze)002:1722: nub pa med pa'i rgyal mtshan rtse mo ltos /
NK109(dze)002:1724: don gyi ngo bo mngon sum du 'char ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:1725: skye ba med pa'i mngon sum sangs rgyas kyis /
NK109(dze)002:1726: yul med rnam par dag pa'i snang ba mthong /
NK109(dze)002:1728: de ltar nyams su blangs pas nyams gong 'phel gyi snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:1729: rig pa'i sku ni lu gu rgyud sku dang bcas par snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:1731: de ltar snang ba rang 'phel nas rig pa tshad la phebs pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1732: dmigs pa'i yul ni rnam par dag pas zhes pa'o /
NK109(dze)002:1733: de las ma 'das chos nyid sgrub du med /
NK109(dze)002:1735: de nas chos nyid zad pa'i snang bar rang grol ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:1736: mtshan ma'i chos nyid ni brjod 'das dang /
NK109(dze)002:1737: blo'i bye brag brjod 'das zhing zhes pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1738: de ltar mthar phyin nas skye ba med pa la rang dbang thob pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1739: 'jug pa la rang dbang thob pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1740: des sprul pa chen po phyogs bcur mdzad nas zhes pas so //
NK109(dze)002:1741: de ltar snying po'i don de dkyus dang sbyar na
NK109(dze)002:1742: de yang 'di nyams su len pa'i skal ldan gyis
NK109(dze)002:1744: de yang snying po'i don la yang nas yang du
NK109(dze)002:1745: lta ba la brtson pa'i skal ldan dad pa dang
NK109(dze)002:1746: ldan pa'i rigs ni rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i
NK109(dze)002:1747: snod du rung ba yi ni 'di dang 'brel la
NK109(dze)002:1748: bu zhes sems las skyed pas /
NK109(dze)002:1749: phyi nang gi bya ba btang la bsgrub dgos te /
NK109(dze)002:1750: phyi'i bya ba las dang so nam dang bral bar bya ste /
NK109(dze)002:1751: nang gi bya ba smra brjod dang bral bar bya /
NK109(dze)002:1752: gsang ba sems 'dzin la sogs pa bral bar bya ste /
NK109(dze)002:1753: longs spyod spangs la dgon pa bsten pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1754: grong khyer chen po ni mi rigs bcu bdun nam bcu bzhi yod pa de las 'das te /
NK109(dze)002:1755: nags 'thug po yod pa'i klong dkyil du gzhan mi
NK109(dze)002:1756: rgyu ba'i bas mtha' dgon par gnas pa'i skal ldan
NK109(dze)002:1757: zhig gis lus ngag gnad gzir ba ni rang gi
NK109(dze)002:1758: 'dug tshul gyi ni seng ge lta bu dang /
NK109(dze)002:1760: drang srong lta bu'i de bzhin nyid la gnas par bya ste /
NK109(dze)002:1761: mig sprul sku'i gzigs stangs su rab tu gnas par byas la /
NK109(dze)002:1762: sgron ma de dang 'du 'bral med par nyin mtshan du btags /
NK109(dze)002:1763: de ltar btags pas mig gi zur nyid la dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma 'byung bas /
NK109(dze)002:1766: de'ang nam mkha' stong pa sprin dang bral ba nyid la gtad pas ngang la rnam par gsal lo //
NK109(dze)002:1767: stong pa chen po bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1768: nam mkha' la gsal ba'i dbyings de nyid ji lta
NK109(dze)002:1769: bur snang na gsal ba la ni 'od lnga'i cha
NK109(dze)002:1770: ma 'gags pa kha dog gnag pa chen po ste
NK109(dze)002:1772: rdzas su med pa la gnyen po ste yul la snang nus pa chen po /
NK109(dze)002:1773: snang ba la yid spyod kyis brtags par dka' bas na chen po /
NK109(dze)002:1774: gzung yul med pas stong pa la 'od du yod pas snang ba chen po /
NK109(dze)002:1775: ngo bo gcig yin pa la sems can dang sangs
NK109(dze)002:1776: rgyas gnyis ka la rgya ma chad pas chen po
NK109(dze)002:1777: / rig pa dang dbyings gnyis ltar snang ba la
NK109(dze)002:1778: 'khor 'das thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa chen po
NK109(dze)002:1779: / / mdzes la 'od lngas khyab ste byas pa ma yin pas brgyan med pa chen po /
NK109(dze)002:1780: des rang gi lus la gang zhing rgyal nas yod
NK109(dze)002:1781: kyang yid dpyod kyi dang btsal kyang ma rnyed pas
NK109(dze)002:1783: rang gi ngo bo smin pa la yo ga'i lus
NK109(dze)002:1784: rgyas ma rdzogs pas chen po'i skur sna tshogs pa
NK109(dze)002:1785: la snang ba dbugs med pas 'gro 'ong med pas
NK109(dze)002:1786: chen po'o // rig pa nyid kyis bzhag sa bstan pa la dang po 'dug stangs bstan pa ni //
NK109(dze)002:1788: zhes ngo mtshar ba'i tshig gis rangs ba brjod cing bos nas /
NK109(dze)002:1789: theg pa thun mong pa rnams la shin tu gsang
NK109(dze)002:1790: ba'i dgongs pa chen po bzhi yis man ngag dngos
NK109(dze)002:1791: gzhi nyams su blang dgos pas chen po //
NK109(dze)002:1792: rig pa'i ye shes su ma nor ba bstan pa /
NK109(dze)002:1793: lta ba mig nyid dang ma bral bar sbyar bas so //
NK109(dze)002:1794: dal ba bzhi po snang ba cer bzhag la sogs
NK109(dze)002:1795: pa 'di dang ma bral na rig pa la byan
NK109(dze)002:1797: snang ba lam khyer gyi gdams ngag bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1798: snang ba cer bzhag gis thabs bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1801: spyod pa dang sbyar ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:1804: rgyud ni mtshan gyi skabs su rin po che rgyal
NK109(dze)002:1805: mtshan gyis rgyud ces pa snang ba sna tshogs pa
NK109(dze)002:1806: rgyud kyi rang bzhin du bstan pas rang gi rig
NK109(dze)002:1808: snang ba sna tshogs pa shes pa chen po la
NK109(dze)002:1809: gcod byed med pa ni yid kyi zhen yul rang
NK109(dze)002:1810: 'gags pas snang ba rang bzhin gyi rgyud ces bya
NK109(dze)002:1811: / yul rang dag pa'i snang ba la rig pa
NK109(dze)002:1812: rang gi rgyud la gnas pa dang gnyis su ma
NK109(dze)002:1813: 'dres pa yongs su rdzogs pa'i tshul du med par
NK109(dze)002:1814: rang la gnas pa'i rgyud dag pa rgyal mtshan lta
NK109(dze)002:1815: bu'i rgyud kyi dgongs pa bar mtshams med par rgyud
NK109(dze)002:1816: ma chad pas rgyud de'i don gzhan gyis rtogs par
NK109(dze)002:1818: spyod pa dang ni sngon du 'gro ba'i lus ngag
NK109(dze)002:1819: yid kyi spyod pa bya ba'i rim pas lus ngag
NK109(dze)002:1820: yid kyi mngon zhen zlog pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1821: nyams mthar phyin gyi spyod pa rlung dang bsres bas
NK109(dze)002:1822: dbang po'i che chung gi rim pa gtan la dbab
NK109(dze)002:1823: pa'o // las dang pos bslab par bya ba'i spyod pas lus ngag srol du bzhugs pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1824: gzhi la sbyar ba ni 'di ltar snang ba cer
NK109(dze)002:1825: bzhag tu bzhag pas dngos po 'dug tshul dang dbyer
NK109(dze)002:1826: mi phyed pas gzhi thog ma ka dag yin la
NK109(dze)002:1827: rig pa dang mi 'bral bas gnas skabs kyi gazhi'o
NK109(dze)002:1828: // lus dang ni lus seng ge ltar 'dug pas 'khrul snang zil gyis mnan la /
NK109(dze)002:1829: glang po che ltar 'dug pas mtshan ma zil gyis mnan la /
NK109(dze)002:1830: drang srong ltar 'dug pas 'byung ba zil gyis mnan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1831: 'bras bu dang sbyar pa'i snang ba ni rang bzhin
NK109(dze)002:1832: rnam par dag pa'i snang ba bem po log nas
NK109(dze)002:1833: // rig pa'i rang gdangs ston pa ni bem po
NK109(dze)002:1834: med pa ni sa chu me rlung med par 'od
NK109(dze)002:1835: lnga'i rang snang chen po lnga shar ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:1836: 'khrul pa gdul bya'i snang ba ni 'gro ba rigs drug so so'i thad ka'i snang ba ste /
NK109(dze)002:1837: yang med pas rmi lam gyii rnam pa ltar kun rdzob tu byung bas /
NK109(dze)002:1838: don dam pa la de bzhin du kun rdzob la snang ba chen po ltar byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:1839: de yang thabs thugs rje chen pos gdul bya'i yul ni 'dra ba tha dad pa la /
NK109(dze)002:1840: 'dul byed sku de snyed du sprul nas don byed pa'o /
NK109(dze)002:1841: chos nyid yangs pa'i snang ba ni ye nas rang
NK109(dze)002:1842: bzhin ma bcos pa ste yangs pa ni mtha' dang
NK109(dze)002:1843: dbus med pa'i chos nyid brjod pa las 'das pa
NK109(dze)002:1844: la bdag gam bdag gis stong pa'am stong pa chen
NK109(dze)002:1845: po / de yang snang ba gsum 'di nyid la
NK109(dze)002:1846: thad ka grogs su shes pas snang ba thams cad
NK109(dze)002:1847: ye shes kyi ngo bor slongs pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1848: cer gyis bltas pas de yang dag pa'i rang bzhin
NK109(dze)002:1849: ji snyed pa thams cad la sto ba med cing
NK109(dze)002:1850: rang gi sgron ma'i de bzhin nyid dang bral bar
NK109(dze)002:1851: gnas te / snang ba de ce re snang yang
NK109(dze)002:1852: yid ma shor zhing don ma 'drus pa de ltar
NK109(dze)002:1853: gong gi shes pa chen po la gcod byed med
NK109(dze)002:1854: gnas te / par sbyar la / bzhag pa'i thabs
NK109(dze)002:1855: ji ltar bya ba ni bla ma las man ngag
NK109(dze)002:1856: zhus te phyi nang gi bya ba btang la dben
NK109(dze)002:1857: pa brten pa la sogs te lus ngag gi gnad
NK109(dze)002:1858: gnas te / par sbyar la / do // mdor
NK109(dze)002:1859: na sngon du 'gro ba'i man ngag bya ba'i rim
NK109(dze)002:1860: gnas te / par sbyar la / do // pa
NK109(dze)002:1861: rnams so // bsam gtan lam khyer gyi man ngag
NK109(dze)002:1862: gnas te / par sbyar la / do // pa
NK109(dze)002:1863: rnams so // bstan pa ni / rgya mtsho cog
NK109(dze)002:1864: bzhag gi dgongs pa bstan pa dang zhes pa ste
NK109(dze)002:1865: gnas te / par sbyar la / do // pa
NK109(dze)002:1866: rnams so // bstan pa ni / / 'di rgyud
NK109(dze)002:1867: dang sbyar na tshig dang yi ge dang brjod pa
NK109(dze)002:1868: tha snyad dang bral bar gnas pas yi ge med
NK109(dze)002:1869: pa'i rgyud ces pa sbyar ste /
NK109(dze)002:1870: tha snyad dang bral ba'i bsam pa de nyid brtan
NK109(dze)002:1871: cing mi 'gyur bas rtsa ba'i lung brjod bya las
NK109(dze)002:1872: 'das pas nges pa zad pa'i chen po'o //
NK109(dze)002:1873: sgom pa dang sbyar na rig pa mngon sum la goms par byed pa'i bsgom pa yin la /
NK109(dze)002:1874: de ltar rig pa gnyis la gtad pa tsam gyis
NK109(dze)002:1875: bsam pa gzhan du mi 'phro bas bsam gtan yin
NK109(dze)002:1876: la / de lta bu'i ngang las yengs pa med par gnas pas dgongs pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:1877: bar med pas dgongs pa chos nyid ma bcos pa /
NK109(dze)002:1878: stobs gzhan dbang du ma gyur bas chen po'o //
NK109(dze)002:1879: lam dang sbyar na phyi'i rgya mtsho las chu bran
NK109(dze)002:1880: thams cad 'dus pa ltar gsang sngags kyi lam sna
NK109(dze)002:1881: tshogs pa dgongs pa la 'dug pas lam /
NK109(dze)002:1882: bsgrod par ni nyan thos la sogs pas mi shes pas brtsol bsgrub che bas na'o //
NK109(dze)002:1883: dka' ba ni pha rol tu phyin pa la sogs
NK109(dze)002:1884: pa'i theg pa thun mong ba rnams yun ring por
NK109(dze)002:1885: sbyong dgos te / skal pa sum cu rtsa gnyis /
NK109(dze)002:1886: nyan thos grangs med pa gsum dang /
NK109(dze)002:1887: ma h+aa lam rim gyis bsgrod dgos pas na dka' ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:1890: rjes 'jug gnyis lam 'di mngon sum du khyer ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:1891: a ti phyogs gzhan la sogs te theg pa thun mong ba rnams kyis mi shes pas chen po'o //
NK109(dze)002:1892: ngag ni su dang yang ma smras pas brjod du med pa'i khong du chud par byed pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:1893: de yang dang po bslab par bya ba'i rim pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1894: gnyis pa bstan par bya ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:1896: ngag tshad la phebs pa'i man ngag go /'bras bu
NK109(dze)002:1897: dang sbyar na rgya mtsho ni chos nyid kyi rgya
NK109(dze)002:1898: mtsho rnam par rtog pa'i g.yo 'gul gang gis kyang
NK109(dze)002:1899: mi bskyod pa'o // brda rtags dbang po'i sgo'i rgya
NK109(dze)002:1900: mtsho ni mig gi de kho na nyid ma bcos
NK109(dze)002:1901: pa las mig gi rnam par shes pa yul du
NK109(dze)002:1903: mig gi rang bzhin chu'i ngo bor snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:1904: de rgya mtsho ni rgya mtsho rlung gi ma bskyod
NK109(dze)002:1905: pa dang 'dra bar yo ga'i lus ngag yid rkyen
NK109(dze)002:1906: dbang du mi 'gro bar gnas pa nyid la bya'o
NK109(dze)002:1907: // chos bzhag pa gzhan gang gi phyogs su yang mi lta zhing dgongs pa las mi 'da' bar /
NK109(dze)002:1908: gsal la ma yengs par snang ba la /
NK109(dze)002:1909: kun tu khyab pa chen po /
NK109(dze)002:1910: yangs pa'i dbyings kyi snang ba dang ma bral bas /
NK109(dze)002:1911: mdzes pa'i rig pa dang 'du 'bral med par gnas pa la bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:1912: dgongs pa ni dbyings kyi sgron ma la mig zur gyis blta bar bya ste //
NK109(dze)002:1913: dbyings kyi nang du rig pa nyid tshud pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1914: ye shes lam khyer gyi gdam ngag bstan pa la /
NK109(dze)002:1915: rig pa cog bzhag gi man ngag bstan pa dang zhes pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:1916: rgyud dang sbyar na mtshan gyi skabs su rgyal ba'i
NK109(dze)002:1917: gdung rgyud lta ba nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam par
NK109(dze)002:1919: rig pa'i ngo bo nyid thams cad kyi rje btsun
NK109(dze)002:1920: du 'gyur zhing de nyid mi 'gyur ba la bya
NK109(dze)002:1921: ste / mi 'gyur pa ni mig gi de kho
NK109(dze)002:1922: na nyid ma bcos par rang snang bas dgongs pa
NK109(dze)002:1924: gzer ni yul nam mkha' dang mig gi dbang po dang /
NK109(dze)002:1925: rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud dang gsum mi
NK109(dze)002:1926: 'bral bar gzer thebs pas yi ge ni rgyal po'i
NK109(dze)002:1927: yig tshang dang 'dra bar smos mi dgos par yon
NK109(dze)002:1928: tan rang rdzogs su yod pas chen po'o //
NK109(dze)002:1929: lta ba dang sbyar ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:1930: chos nyid lta ba cir snang rang byung gi ye shes su shes shing mthong ba ste /
NK109(dze)002:1931: lta ba rang byung gi mig gi de bzhin nyid rang gi lta zhing rang las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:1932: 'gro sa ni gnas skabs nyams len gyi dus na
NK109(dze)002:1933: nam mkha' sprin dang bral ba mthar thug 'dug tshul
NK109(dze)002:1934: gyi dus na chos nyid ka dag go /'dir bdag
NK109(dze)002:1935: gi rig pas sngon chad ma mthong ma phyin pas
NK109(dze)002:1936: chen po'o // chos can lta ba'i lta ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:1937: chos can lta ba'i yul sna tshogs pa de nyid
NK109(dze)002:1938: rig pa lhag mthong du ma mthong bas dka' ba
NK109(dze)002:1939: yin la me long gi de nyid rtogs na chos
NK109(dze)002:1940: nyid lta ba'i lta bar snang bas na'o //
NK109(dze)002:1941: chen po ni de'i don mthong dka' bas na'o //
NK109(dze)002:1942: yid dang sbyar na brtag par dka' ba ni yid
NK109(dze)002:1943: kyi rnam par shes pa'i yul sna tshogs par snang
NK109(dze)002:1944: zhing de nyid dbang po la brten nas gcod par
NK109(dze)002:1945: byed pas de'i mtshan nyid shes pa'am tshad la 'bebs
NK109(dze)002:1946: par dka' bas mchong ni gcig tu mi gnas pa'o
NK109(dze)002:1947: // chen po ni bla ma'i man ngag dang ldan
NK109(dze)002:1948: pas brtags pas ye shes kyi grogs su 'gro ba'o
NK109(dze)002:1949: // // 'bras bur sbyar na gzhi 'dzin pa'i rig
NK109(dze)002:1950: pa mtshan nyid gang du yang ma grub pa dang
NK109(dze)002:1951: // // / lhag mthong gi rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyi sku la bya ste /
NK109(dze)002:1952: de'i ngang du bzung ste bya byed dang bral bar bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:1953: cog bzhag ni dbyings kyi sgron mar de nyid thabs kyis bzung bar bya ste /
NK109(dze)002:1954: don mig mi 'gul bas yid ma 'gyus pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1955: man ngag gi bya byed rig pa'i man ngag bsgrub thabs dang sngags la brten pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1956: slab thabs bcos pa'i man ngag ji ltar bya'i go rim la brten pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1957: rim 'jug dbang gi man ngag gi rang gi sngar mthong gi lag len la brten pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1958: 'jig rten mthong sbyor gyi man ngag gi rim pa la brten nas /
NK109(dze)002:1959: mthar thug gnad kyi man ngag rang gi lus ngag la brten pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:1960: snying tig mngon sum gyi man ngag bla ma drin
NK109(dze)002:1961: can la brten pa ste de yang man ngag gi
NK109(dze)002:1962: bzhag thabs la thug go /'bras bu lam khyer gyi
NK109(dze)002:1963: man ngag ngos bzung bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:1964: ri bo cog bzhag gi lta ba bstan pa dang zhes pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:1965: de yang rgyud dang sbyar na nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam par bstan pa'i rgyud chen po ste /
NK109(dze)002:1969: chad pa'i mtha' bzhi ma spangs par mnyam rgyu chos
NK109(dze)002:1970: nyid nam mkha' mnyam pa rig pa yin pas de
NK109(dze)002:1971: nyid rang la rang chas su ye nas 'du 'bral
NK109(dze)002:1972: med par gnas pas rgyud ces bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:1973: 'bras bu dang sbyar na ldog bcas thun mong gi 'bras bu /
NK109(dze)002:1974: a nu man chad theg pa brgyad kyi 'bras bu yin la /
NK109(dze)002:1975: mthar thug tshad phebs kyi 'bras bu ni /
NK109(dze)002:1976: gnas par dka' ba ni chos nyid thams cad zad pas so //
NK109(dze)002:1977: yul ni 'dzin pa dang rig pa rang gdangs kyi
NK109(dze)002:1978: snang ba yul can du ma las 'das pas mngon
NK109(dze)002:1979: gsum 'byongs pa'i yul la chen po de las gong
NK109(dze)002:1981: sems dang sbyar na phyin par dka' ba'i sems kyi
NK109(dze)002:1982: rtog tshogs dang bsam pa du ma rnams lam ye
NK109(dze)002:1983: shes kyi rgyan du shar bas 'gyur ba med pa'i
NK109(dze)002:1984: sa sems kyi cig pa'i rang bzhin la nyon mongs
NK109(dze)002:1985: pa ka nas dag pas chen po'o //
NK109(dze)002:1987: man ngag yod pa la tshegs med pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1988: theg pa thun mong ba rnams kyis mi rtogs pas
NK109(dze)002:1989: de'i don dpag par dka' bas chen po ni thabs
NK109(dze)002:1990: che bas skad cig la shes pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:1991: khyab pa med pa'i ye gdangs ni sems kyi byung
NK109(dze)002:1992: tshor kyi dngos po 'dug tshul la ma khyab pas
NK109(dze)002:1993: so // ye gdangs ni rig pa'i ye nas gdangs lnga'i mtshan nyid du gnas pas chen po'o //
NK109(dze)002:1994: 'bras bu dang sbyar na rig pa'i gnad gzir ba
NK109(dze)002:1995: las rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i 'bras bu mthar
NK109(dze)002:1996: phyin pa ni / ri bo ni /
NK109(dze)002:1997: rig pa nyid mi 'gyur te thog ma nas 'pho
NK109(dze)002:1998: 'gyur med kyang 'gro ba thams cad la yongs su
NK109(dze)002:1999: brdal khyab tu gnas pa'i don de chen po'o //
NK109(dze)002:2000: phra ba ni rtogs par dka' ba yin la /
NK109(dze)002:2001: yongs su gzung bar dka' ba ni rig pa rang
NK109(dze)002:2002: snang gi 'bras bu de theg pa gzhan gyis mi
NK109(dze)002:2003: zin pas so // de lta bu'i don de ri
NK109(dze)002:2004: bo dang 'dra ba mi 'gyur la dbang mtho ba
NK109(dze)002:2005: zin pas so // nyid do // de ltar gzung
NK109(dze)002:2006: bar dka' ba de nyid ji ltar bzhag na che
NK109(dze)002:2008: snang ba'i 'brel sna tshogs par snang yang bla ma'i
NK109(dze)002:2009: man ngag med na sus kyang mthong ba med pa
NK109(dze)002:2010: ste / de nyid yid dpyod kyis mi rnyed pas chen po yin la /
NK109(dze)002:2011: de yang mig gi bya byed med par nam mkha'i ngang la ma yengs par bzhag ste /
NK109(dze)002:2012: ma bcos par rang gis lta bar bya /
NK109(dze)002:2013: rang gsal tsam du bzhag par bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:2014: lta ba ni rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud
NK109(dze)002:2015: la bltas pas bzlum pa la ni thig le dang
NK109(dze)002:2016: thig le'i phyed sku la sogs pa mthong ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:2017: dbyibs ni rdzas su grub pa med pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2018: de ltar rig pa'i ngo bo de nyid ye shes kyi rtsal gyi 'khyud pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2019: de nyid 'gro 'ong ltar snang yang las kyi rlung
NK109(dze)002:2020: las grub pa'i dbugs phyi nang du 'gyur ba med
NK109(dze)002:2021: pas / skye shi las 'das pas chen po yin pas na //
NK109(dze)002:2022: de yang dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma dang
NK109(dze)002:2023: ma bral bas mig gi lta ba ma yengs pas
NK109(dze)002:2024: lta bas rig pa tshad la phebs pa'i 'bras bu
NK109(dze)002:2025: nyid yin no // de la yang thugs rje rtsal
NK109(dze)002:2026: gyi 'char lugs ltar na 'di nyid rgyur mi ldog
NK109(dze)002:2027: pa bse shing gi 'bras bu lta bu thig le
NK109(dze)002:2028: ni don dam spros pa med pa /
NK109(dze)002:2029: nyag ni zab pa'am rtogs par dka' la gcig ni
NK109(dze)002:2030: du ma dang tha snyad las 'das pa de ye
NK109(dze)002:2031: shes gnyis kyi bdag nyid shar bas dngos po'i gnas
NK109(dze)002:2032: lugs kyi thog tu rdzogs pas chen po'o //
NK109(dze)002:2033: de yang chos thams cad zad pas snang ba ci
NK109(dze)002:2034: yi ngo bor yang ma grub pas na gang gi
NK109(dze)002:2035: phyogs su ni dngos po dang /
NK109(dze)002:2036: stong par bltas kyang de nyid ma grub pa med pa nyid yin pas /
NK109(dze)002:2037: rgyal po gdan sa zin te mi 'gyur /
NK109(dze)002:2038: blon po btson du zin te mi 'gyur /
NK109(dze)002:2039: dmangs cham la phab ste mi 'gyur /
NK109(dze)002:2040: rig pa rang sa zin te mi 'gyur pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2041: de'i phyir na rang bzhin rnam dag gi 'bras bu zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:2042: snang srid gzhi bzhag gi lta ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:2043: dbyings rig 'du 'bral med par bltas pas sangs rgyas
NK109(dze)002:2044: kyi bden pa'i rig pa lu gu rgyud dang ma
NK109(dze)002:2045: bral bar dus thams cad du gnas pas dbang po
NK109(dze)002:2046: rab bar do med par 'byung ba rang dengs su
NK109(dze)002:2048: 'bring bar do med par skad cig ma gsum la sangs rgyas ba dang //
NK109(dze)002:2049: tha ma bar do med par rang bzhin sprul pa
NK109(dze)002:2050: sku'i zhing khams su dbugs phyung nas sangs rgyas ba'o
NK109(dze)002:2051: // de'i phyir na snang srid gzhi bzhengs pas 'khor
NK109(dze)002:2052: ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa gnyis 'dres pa
NK109(dze)002:2053: // dang / gzhir bzhag pas chos nyid rnal du phebs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2054: khams gsum yongs su grol bas zag bcas rang 'gags pa dang //
NK109(dze)002:2055: srid gsum ka nas dag pa'i chos rnams rang zad pa'i snang ba shar ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:2056: des na grong khyer rgyun gcod kyi lta ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:2057: mthong snang rang dag pa'i dgongs pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2058: bar ma do de ni rang bzhin gnas pa'i bar ma do de bem po'i snang ba rang dag /
NK109(dze)002:2059: shi ka ma'i bar do med de skye shi gnyis kyi mtha' rang bcad /
NK109(dze)002:2060: chos nyid kyi bar ma do med de sku gsum 'di nyid la lam du byas zin /
NK109(dze)002:2061: srid pa'i bar do med de rig pa nyid 'khrul
NK109(dze)002:2062: gzhi dang bral bas skad cig ma la snang ba
NK109(dze)002:2064: rig pa tshad la phebs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2065: chos nyid rang zad pa'i snang ba la spyod pas
NK109(dze)002:2066: bar do bzhi sangs rang bzhin 'dug tshul du rgyas
NK109(dze)002:2067: pas / nyon mongs pa gnas bsgyur bas 'khor ba btsal du ma rnyed pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2068: rgyas btab pas chos can chos nyid 'dres pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2069: gnas dag pas snang ba rnams rang sar dengs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2070: rang grol bas gnyan po gzhan la rag ma lus pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2071: de'i phyir na nyin mtshan kha sbyor gyi sgom pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:2072: spyod pa rab bzhag pas spyod pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2073: sngon du 'khor 'das ru shan 'byed pa'i spyod pa
NK109(dze)002:2074: byas pas des skye ba la rang dbang thob ste
NK109(dze)002:2075: sprul pa sku'i yon tan rdzogs pas 'pho ba chen
NK109(dze)002:2076: po'i skur bzhengs nas thugs rje'i go ma 'gags pas
NK109(dze)002:2077: / rang bzhin gyi thugs rjes sprul pa lta bu'i
NK109(dze)002:2078: rig pa la dbang thob pas chen po ste phyogs
NK109(dze)002:2079: bcur gang zag sum stong mya ngan las 'das bar
NK109(dze)002:2080: / byed do // de yang ji ltar byed na
NK109(dze)002:2081: 'di ltar gang la rig pa bcug pa bdag dang
NK109(dze)002:2083: de'i phyir na spyod pa la rgyun du byed pa'i
NK109(dze)002:2084: rnal 'byor gyis 'khrul snang zhing khams su spyod pa
NK109(dze)002:2085: dang / sgom pa la rgyun du byed pas 'gyu byed rang sar dag pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2086: lta ba la rgyun du byed pa'i 'byung ba rang zad pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2087: 'bras bu la rgyun du byed pas ngan song dong sprugs pas na /
NK109(dze)002:2088: snang ba dbang sgyur gyi spyod pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:2089: ri bo cog bzhag gi lta ba bstan pa la
NK109(dze)002:2090: bzhis bstan pa'i dang po bzhi'i dgos pa brjod pa
NK109(dze)002:2091: bstan pa ni / e ma ho /
NK109(dze)002:2092: sangs rgyas chen po yi mdzad spyod ni zhes pa la sogs pa yis bstan no //
NK109(dze)002:2094: zhes ngo mtshar du brjod cing bos nas /
NK109(dze)002:2095: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi mdzad spyod ni sngon 'byung
NK109(dze)002:2096: cog bzhag bzhi po de la bstan pa da ltar
NK109(dze)002:2097: yang de nyid las g.yos pa med do //
NK109(dze)002:2098: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas nyid kyi snang ba ni
NK109(dze)002:2099: bzhi po de las med par rang rdo rje sems
NK109(dze)002:2100: dpa' yis sngon byung du yang bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2101: rtog pa gsal bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2102: a +aa ri bo cog bzhag lta ba gsang ba nyid /
NK109(dze)002:2103: ces pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:2104: a de ni skye med kyi lta ba +aa ni 'gags pa med pa'i lta ba //
NK109(dze)002:2105: skye med kyi rol pa sna tshogs su shar ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:2106: ri bo lta bu mi 'gyur ba'i lta ba rtsol
NK109(dze)002:2107: med du cog gis bzhag pa'i theg pa thun mong
NK109(dze)002:2108: pas ma rtogs pa de nyid la lta ba gsang
NK109(dze)002:2109: ba nyid do // de lta bu'i don de la
NK109(dze)002:2110: gzhi la the tshom yod pa ma yin pas 'di
NK109(dze)002:2111: nyid la yang 'gyu ba ngang gis med do //
NK109(dze)002:2112: gzhan dbang ma grub pa'i ye shes bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2113: don gyi ngo bo nyid la zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:2114: don gyi ngo bo lu gu rgyud de nyid la /
NK109(dze)002:2115: sngar sangs rgyas sgam pos byas pa ma yin phyis
NK109(dze)002:2116: sems can sgrin pos byed pa'i mkhan po ga la
NK109(dze)002:2118: de nyid 'bad rtsol las 'das pas gzhan gyi dbang
NK109(dze)002:2119: du ma gyur pas bcos pa ma yin 'di la
NK109(dze)002:2120: 'chos pa'i mkhan po'am bdag por grub pa med do
NK109(dze)002:2121: / yid dpyod kyi lta ba ma yin pas blta byed 'dzin 'dzin pa'i chos dang bral ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:2122: rig pa 'di nyid theg pa thun mong bas mthong ba ma yin te /
NK109(dze)002:2123: bla ma'i man ngag dang ldan pa la mthong byed mig la rnam par 'od thig ler gsal lo //
NK109(dze)002:2124: de nyid snang ba sna tshogs su snang bar byed pa ma yin te /
NK109(dze)002:2125: stong pa zang thal du yod pa snang ba'i phyogs theg pa rim pa dgu'i 'dod pa dang bral /
NK109(dze)002:2126: de lta bu'i rig pa la skye 'bri yod pa
NK109(dze)002:2127: ma yin te snang ba la thogs pa med par
NK109(dze)002:2129: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i don rtsol ba med
NK109(dze)002:2130: par cog bzhag tu bzhag pa nyid la bskyod du
NK109(dze)002:2131: med de bsgrub pa'i chos dang bral /
NK109(dze)002:2132: gcig las 'das pas du ma yin la /
NK109(dze)002:2133: du ma'i chos dang bral bas gcig pu yang ma yin /
NK109(dze)002:2134: phyi nang med par zang thal bar yod de /
NK109(dze)002:2135: ma rtogs pa'i dus na phyi dang nang du yang gsal la /
NK109(dze)002:2136: de nyid rang grol pas phyi nang med par zang thal bas gzhan dbang ma grub pa nyid do //
NK109(dze)002:2137: de lta bu'i don de la mig gi de kho
NK109(dze)002:2138: na nyid blta byed ma 'gags pas dngos med yin
NK109(dze)002:2140: rang gsal du yod pas chad pa gnyis las 'das /
NK109(dze)002:2141: de nas mngon sum du bltar yod pas rang rig
NK109(dze)002:2142: khyab che bas gzhan dbang du ma gyur pa'i ye
NK109(dze)002:2143: shes nyid do // kun brtags kyi gzhi dgag par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2144: de la lta ba med pa'i zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:2146: de lta mngon sum du gyi don la mngon par
NK109(dze)002:2147: zhen na ltung byed yin pas de la lta ba
NK109(dze)002:2148: rang bzhin med pas zhes pa'i mtha' dang bral bar
NK109(dze)002:2150: dngos po la blta ba zhes grub pa med pas
NK109(dze)002:2151: rnal 'byor bas kyang zhen pa mthar thug gis bcas
NK109(dze)002:2153: de ltar zhen pa med par lta ba de nyid
NK109(dze)002:2154: lta ba'i don las mi 'da' ba yin pas rig
NK109(dze)002:2155: pa byad kyi zhen pa mthar thug dang bcas pa'i
NK109(dze)002:2157: de dngos po rang snang du yod pa ma yin
NK109(dze)002:2158: pa de nyid rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i lta
NK109(dze)002:2159: ba yin pas rnal 'byor pa de'i ngang du ma
NK109(dze)002:2160: bcos pas gzhan du ma yengs par gnas par bya'o
NK109(dze)002:2161: // rgya mtsho cog bzhag la gsum gyis bstan pa'i dang po gol sa dgag par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2162: e +ae rgya mtsho cog bzhag gi dgongs pa ni zhes pa la sogs pas bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2163: e ni rig pa skye ba med pa la lam
NK109(dze)002:2164: skye med du rtogs pas +ae 'gags pa med pa'i
NK109(dze)002:2166: snang ba 'gags med tshad du phyin pa las 'bras
NK109(dze)002:2167: bu skye med kyi don khong du chud pas a
NK109(dze)002:2168: de nyid sngon du lam sbyangs pa las byung bas
NK109(dze)002:2169: e zhes bya'o // rgya mtsho ni mig bya byed dang bral bar cog gis bzhag pa la bya /
NK109(dze)002:2170: dgongs pa thun mtshams med par dus rgyun du gnas pa ni bsam gtan dang /
NK109(dze)002:2172: ting nge 'dzin dang gzhi'i ka dag yin no //
NK109(dze)002:2173: snang ba ma yin pa ni mig gzhan du yengs
NK109(dze)002:2174: pa yin snang bar byed ba mig gis snang ba'i
NK109(dze)002:2175: yul bcad pa yin te rang sor bzhag par bya
NK109(dze)002:2176: / mig ni de kho na nyid 'od lnga'i gsal bar byas pas stong pa yang ma yin /
NK109(dze)002:2177: ye nas stong ma myong pas stong par yod pa ma yin /
NK109(dze)002:2178: gsal pa ma yin pa dbang po sgo lnga'i rnam shes tha dad par gsal ma yin te /
NK109(dze)002:2179: rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i snang ba rang gsal ba chen po'i yul du ye nas med pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2180: bying ba ni rang bzhin gyis bying ba gnyid lta bu ni ma yin /
NK109(dze)002:2181: bar chod gyis bying ba shes pa rmugs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2182: 'byung bas bying ba lus myogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2183: nyon mongs pas bying ba nyams thog tu mi phebs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2184: phyin ci log gi bying ba dgongs pa'i gol sar gyur pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2185: snyoms las kyis bying ba bsam gtan le lo'i dbang du gyur pa ma yin /
NK109(dze)002:2186: rgod pa ni yid kyis dgod pa 'gyu byed sna tshogs dang /
NK109(dze)002:2187: sems kyis rgod pa dran bsam sna tshogs dang /
NK109(dze)002:2188: bar chod kyis rgod pa yid sems g.yeng ba sna tshogs dang /
NK109(dze)002:2189: 'du ba'i 'byung bas rgod pa lus tsha grang gis 'khrugs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2190: phyin ci log gis rgod pa sems mi dge ba sna tshogs slong ba /
NK109(dze)002:2191: rang bzhin sna tshogs pas rgod pa bya ba ma
NK109(dze)002:2192: yin pa'i bsam pa sna tshogs pa dang drug ngang
NK109(dze)002:2194: de ltar bsgom pa'i gol sa bcu gnyis med pas rig pa ma g.yos pas rang gsal /
NK109(dze)002:2195: de nyid ma g.yos pas lus mi g.yo /
NK109(dze)002:2196: lus sems bya byed dang bral bas yid sems g.yo bar mi 'gyur te rang bzhag tu gnas pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2197: ma bskyod pa ni mig gi phyed btsum med par
NK109(dze)002:2198: har por lta ba rig pa nyid rlung gis ma
NK109(dze)002:2199: bskyod pa cog bzhag du gnas so //
NK109(dze)002:2200: de gnyis rlung dang bral bas dbang po dang nyon mongs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2201: yul rtog gi spyod pa kun las 'das pa yin te 'gyu byed med pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2202: byas bas ma byung ba ni ched du rtsol ba
NK109(dze)002:2203: dang bcas pas shes pa gud du mi bcad par
NK109(dze)002:2204: bzhag pa nam mkha' thabs sla ba'i man ngag chen
NK109(dze)002:2206: de ltar rang bzhag chen po'i dgongs pa las sa gcig du bsdad pas /
NK109(dze)002:2208: yul stong pa la rig pa stong pa gtad pas bsdu mi dgos /
NK109(dze)002:2209: de nyid cog bzhag gcig gi ngang zhes bya /
NK109(dze)002:2210: de ltar gnas pa'i dus na nyon mongs pa gnas mi srid pas gol ba ma yin /
NK109(dze)002:2211: dran rtog ji ltar shes kyang don de nyid las 'da' ba'i sa med do //
NK109(dze)002:2212: ye shes kyi snang ba ngos bzung bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2213: gsang ba ye shes rgya mtsho lta bu la zhes pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:2214: gsang ba gzhan gyis mi shes pa'i ye shes kyi
NK109(dze)002:2215: snang ba rgya mtsho lta bu rgya che la gting
NK109(dze)002:2216: zab cing g.yo 'gul dang bral ba nyid la /
NK109(dze)002:2217: rig pa ye nas gnas pa'i don bcos pa med
NK109(dze)002:2218: pas rgyun dbang po'i sgo ma bkag pas 'byams pa
NK109(dze)002:2220: gting dpag dka' ba ni lus 'byung ba las grub
NK109(dze)002:2221: pa phung po lnga la sogs pa dpag tu med
NK109(dze)002:2222: pa tshogs pas rgya mtsho dang 'dra nas /
NK109(dze)002:2223: ye shes 'byung ba mig rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo
NK109(dze)002:2224: lta bu ni sgron mas thams cad du nub pa
NK109(dze)002:2226: zhes rdo rje 'chang gis gdams pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2227: 'khrul rtog gi the tshom gcod par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2228: stong pa'i sems med ma bcos chen po'i sku /
NK109(dze)002:2230: sems stong par 'dug kyang sna tshogs su 'gyur pa
NK109(dze)002:2231: de med pas rig pa nyid ma bcos pa chen
NK109(dze)002:2232: po'i sku gsum du shar ba la bya //
NK109(dze)002:2233: de nyid sus kyang byas pa med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2234: byed pa yid kyi rnam shes kun las rgyal /
NK109(dze)002:2235: ye nas ma bcos par rang byung cog bzhag nyid ni mig dang sgron ma nam mkha' gsum yin /
NK109(dze)002:2236: de gsum 'khrul snang gis ma bsgyur rang gi blo yis ma bcos pa nyid bsam gtan yin /
NK109(dze)002:2237: chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i nam mkha' la gnas
NK109(dze)002:2238: na sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa nyid du rdo rje
NK109(dze)002:2239: 'chang gis bstan / chos kyi sku'i ye shes la
NK109(dze)002:2240: bsam pa kun rab tu spang ste ye nas sems
NK109(dze)002:2241: yod ma myong yid kyi 'gyu byed med na sgom
NK109(dze)002:2242: 'chang gis bstan / pa yang yin / dgongs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2245: grub pa'i dmigs pa'i phyogs rang gi 'dod pa mi 'dzin na /
NK109(dze)002:2246: dper na rgya mtsho'i gting du gza' dang skar ma
NK109(dze)002:2247: shar ba bzhin du 'dzin byed gsal cha med de
NK109(dze)002:2249: zhen yul du ma bcad pas 'dzin pa med par
NK109(dze)002:2250: rang sar bzhag pa ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i dgongs
NK109(dze)002:2251: pa'i 'dug tshul de bzhin no zhes pa dus thams
NK109(dze)002:2252: cad du bzhugs pa yin pas rnal 'byor pas kyang
NK109(dze)002:2254: rig pa cog bzhag gi man ngag la lnga yis bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)002:2255: nyams su blang ba'i thabs bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2256: o +ao rig pa cog bzhag gis man ngag nyid ces pa la sogs te /
NK109(dze)002:2257: o ni skye ba med pa'i dbyings nam mkha'i yin la /
NK109(dze)002:2258: +ao ni nam mkha' la skye med kyi dbyings rnam
NK109(dze)002:2259: par dag pa'i sgron ma bzhag pas snang ba 'gag
NK109(dze)002:2260: med du shar bas de nyid la rig pa cog
NK109(dze)002:2261: gis bzhag pa'i man ngag nyid yin /
NK109(dze)002:2262: de ltar bzhag pa 'di ni gsang sngags kyi thabs
NK109(dze)002:2263: rnams kyi mthar thug pa ni bla ma la rag
NK109(dze)002:2264: lus pa yin / de dbyings rnam par dag pa nyid las 'od du 'char /
NK109(dze)002:2265: de la rig pa'i ngo bo lu gu rgyud lta bu 'byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:2266: de yang ji ltar 'byung na phra ba shes rab kyi cha dang /
NK109(dze)002:2267: 'khyud pa ye shes dang 'od kyi cha dang /
NK109(dze)002:2268: 'gyu ba rlung dang sku yi cha gsum du 'byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:2269: nyams su blang ba'i rgyu bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2270: mig ni nam mkha' khams gsum la brtags ces pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:2271: de yang mig ni chu bur gyi mig yul 'dzin pa dang bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2272: sha'i mig gis 'byung ba lnga'i rang bzhin gling nyi shu /
NK109(dze)002:2273: ri rab dang bcas pas rdzas lkog tu gyur pa rnams gcod cing shes pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2274: shes rab kyi mig gis chos dang chos ma yin pa rnam par 'byed cing gcod pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2275: ye shes kyi mig gis 'khor 'das kyi gnas lugs
NK109(dze)002:2276: phyin ci ma log par mkhyen pa'i thams cad mkhyen
NK109(dze)002:2277: pa'i mig yin te don gyi sangs rgyas kyi mig
NK109(dze)002:2278: go / mig gi rnam par shes pa ni gsum
NK109(dze)002:2279: 'dus pa las gcod pa de 'gags pa la don
NK109(dze)002:2281: mig gi 'dus te reg pa ni shes pa dang
NK109(dze)002:2282: dbang po dang yul gsum 'dus pa las reg pa
NK109(dze)002:2284: mig gi 'dus te reg pa'i rkyen gyis tshor ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:2285: 'dus pa'i yul gzung bya la nye bar len pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2287: thos pa dang gsum 'dus pa las bde bar tshor
NK109(dze)002:2288: ba dang sdug pa dang btang snyoms gsum gyis gzugs
NK109(dze)002:2289: la zhen pas 'khrul pa rang 'khor du gcod pa
NK109(dze)002:2290: dang / tshogs pa dang g.yo zhing chags pas nyams su myong ba phyin ci log dang /
NK109(dze)002:2291: kun rdzob kyi rnam par gcod pa'o /
NK109(dze)002:2292: de ltar mig rang gi ngo bo dang /
NK109(dze)002:2294: reg pa dang tshor ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:2295: bzhi ni phye ba dang btsums pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2296: mthong ba dang gcod pa bzhir byung ste /
NK109(dze)002:2297: de bzhi spangs la nam mkha'i khams su sprin ser
NK109(dze)002:2298: bu med par brtags ces pa ste bltas pas nyams
NK109(dze)002:2299: gong du 'phel ba'i snang ba sangs rgyas sku ni
NK109(dze)002:2301: de nyid la brtan pa thob nas dgongs pa ni
NK109(dze)002:2302: lta ba ma yengs pa drod lus ngag la rtags
NK109(dze)002:2303: 'ga' 'byung / de nas rig pa'i sku rdo rje
NK109(dze)002:2304: lu gu rgyud kyi sku tshigs rnams su sku re
NK109(dze)002:2305: 'ga' 'byung / re snang ba'o // nyams su longs pa'i tshad bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2306: snang ba chig chod dgongs pa ni zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:2307: de ltar nyams gong 'phel gyi snang ba rdzogs pas
NK109(dze)002:2308: snang ba 'di nyid chig chod du zag pa med
NK109(dze)002:2309: pas yo ga ba'i dgongs pa yin no //
NK109(dze)002:2310: rig pa nyid kyi bzhag sa btsal ba las byung ngo //
NK109(dze)002:2311: de'i phyir gsang ba ni nyan thos dang so so'i skye bo la sogs pa lags pa /
NK109(dze)002:2312: gsang ba chen po sngags phyi nang rnams kyis 'di'i don mi shes pas so //
NK109(dze)002:2313: de ltar gsang zhing nyams su blangs pa las nyams
NK109(dze)002:2314: gong 'phel gyi snang ba'i stobs la brten nas rig
NK109(dze)002:2315: pa tshad la phebs nas chos nyid zad pa'i sa
NK109(dze)002:2316: ste / snang ba de dag zad pa'i pha rol
NK109(dze)002:2317: na chos rnams zad pa ste 'khor ba las sgrol
NK109(dze)002:2318: ste / ba zhes bya'o // gong gi snang ba'i
NK109(dze)002:2319: dus na yang zhen pa mthar thug dang bcas pa'i
NK109(dze)002:2320: chags pas ma bcings par rang snang du bzhag go
NK109(dze)002:2321: ste / ba zhes bya'o // / rig pa lta ba de dngos bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2322: de las gsang sngags nyid kyi sku zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te //
NK109(dze)002:2323: de yang gong 'phel gyi dus na rig pa'i tshigs
NK109(dze)002:2324: las skur snang ba de las gsang sngags phyi nang
NK109(dze)002:2325: rnams su bstan pa'i rigs lnga nyid kyi sku yab
NK109(dze)002:2326: lnga yum lnga ste zung bcu me rlung kun la
NK109(dze)002:2327: khyab pa'i 'byung ba ni rig pa lu gu rgyud
NK109(dze)002:2328: nyid mngon sum du lam du byas pa las byung
NK109(dze)002:2329: ba ste / de nyid la brtags pas sku sna
NK109(dze)002:2330: tshogs pa yang 'char bar rdo rje 'chang gis bshad
NK109(dze)002:2331: ba ste / do // sna tshogs kyi rgyud dang ye shes bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2332: rig pa'i snang ba thabs mkhas pas zhes pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:2333: gong gi nyams su len pa las bar chad nas
NK109(dze)002:2334: 'byung ba rang dengs la ma song na rig pa'i
NK109(dze)002:2335: snang ba chos nyid kyi bar ma do la thabs
NK109(dze)002:2336: lngar bstan pas bla ma mkhas pas 'di nyid du
NK109(dze)002:2337: gsang sngags kyi lam sna tshogs su snang bas /
NK109(dze)002:2338: sangs rgyas ni ming rnam par snang mdzad la sogs sna tshogs 'char bar nges pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2339: snang ba'i rkyen sa dang chu dang me dang rlung dang nam mkha' lnga 'od lngar gsal ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:2341: rdul phran kyi dri ma dang rags pa ri rab
NK109(dze)002:2342: dang gling bzhi rnams kyi dri ma gnyis med de
NK109(dze)002:2343: / de nyid med pas rig pa'i ye shes lnga sku lnga'i 'od klong du thim pas /
NK109(dze)002:2344: 'gags pa med pa'i 'od dkar po dang //
NK109(dze)002:2348: mthing ka lnga yul bar ma do la dngos su
NK109(dze)002:2349: snang ba nyid ni gzugs sku 'od kyi zhal phyag
NK109(dze)002:2350: gi rnam par snang bas bsam pa dang bcas pas
NK109(dze)002:2351: don gnyis la thogs pa med par bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:2352: nga'i 'dzin pa nyid rang log pa'i rig pa'i rang snang du shar bas /
NK109(dze)002:2353: rig pa'i ye shes khyab brdal bas zhes bya ste /
NK109(dze)002:2354: snang ba chen po'i rang bzhin rnam par dag pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:2355: sa rdo mi snang gsal ba 'od dang sku dang
NK109(dze)002:2356: thig le rab tu rgya che bar snang ba ni
NK109(dze)002:2357: gong du 'khrul pa'i rnam par rtog pa'i blo ni
NK109(dze)002:2358: bsam gyis mi khyab pas 'gags pa las byung bas
NK109(dze)002:2359: / blo'i bye brag du ma rnams brjod pa las 'das shing /
NK109(dze)002:2360: chos kyi sku la bsam pa'i sems med pas /
NK109(dze)002:2361: ye shes lnga 'dus pa'i sku gcig ni kun tu
NK109(dze)002:2362: rtsal ma 'gags par snang ba du ma ston pa
NK109(dze)002:2363: / de yang gsal ba'i ye shes lnga 'dus pa rang gi rig pa yin pas /
NK109(dze)002:2364: de la chags pa med pa'i rig pa rang snang bar shes pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2365: sngar gyi bla ma'i gsung la brten pas dkyil rig pa 'khor 'od rgya chen po la spyod pa /
NK109(dze)002:2366: gong du cog bzhag bzhi nyid du bzhag pas thams cad de'i ngang du chub pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:2368: rig pa'i ye shes lnga sku lnga lnga ltar snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:2369: gsang ba'i ye shes lnga sku lnga'i klong nas mkhyen pa ma 'gags par gsal bas /
NK109(dze)002:2370: rig pa'i gsal ba'i cha 'od lnga phyogs bcur zer
NK109(dze)002:2371: gyi tshul du 'phro ba ni ye shes bzhi sbyor
NK109(dze)002:2372: gyi snang ba'o // de la brtan pa thob nas thig mi 'gyur zhing lam drang ba /
NK109(dze)002:2373: le rang bzhin snang par brdal ba /
NK109(dze)002:2374: nyag sku sna tshogs su snang ba gcig ni de
NK109(dze)002:2375: dag rang gi rig par 'dus pas bar do'i snang
NK109(dze)002:2377: chos kyi sku thig le nyag gcig tu ka dag
NK109(dze)002:2378: chen por rang rdzogs pas gong gi sku dang ye
NK109(dze)002:2379: shes snang ba du ma med par rig pas chos
NK109(dze)002:2380: nyid zad pa'i snang ba ye nas stong pa ci
NK109(dze)002:2381: yi ngo bor yang ma grub la /
NK109(dze)002:2382: brjod pa gang gis kyang thog tu mi babs zhing
NK109(dze)002:2383: ston par dka' ba'i gnas su sangs rgya ba ni
NK109(dze)002:2384: / sngon du rig pa cog bzhag sku ni /
NK109(dze)002:2385: skye shi med pa'i dbyings gcig tu 'dril ba las na ste /
NK109(dze)002:2386: de ltar gnas pa ni snang ba sna tshogs kyi rgyu ye shes las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:2387: don bdun pa snang ba cer bzhag gi thabs rgyas
NK109(dze)002:2388: par bshad pa la gsum gyis bstan pa'i dang po
NK109(dze)002:2389: / chen po lnga ngos bzung bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2390: u +au snang ba gcer bzhag thabs chen ni /
NK109(dze)002:2391: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:2392: u ni skye ba med pa'i rig pa las /
NK109(dze)002:2393: mdzad pa med pa'i thugs rje rang snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:2394: +au ni skye med kyi shes rab las 'gag med kyi thugs rje phyogs med du shar ba ste /
NK109(dze)002:2395: snang ba ce re bzhag pas thabs gtad pa'i 'ben dang 'brel pas /
NK109(dze)002:2397: dngos po 'dug tshul gyi snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:2398: ye shes phyogs dag gi snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:2399: gdul bya tha dad kyi snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:2400: rang bzhin ltar snang gi snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:2401: 'gro drug 'khrul pa'i snang ba rnams rang gi rig pa la 'dus pas /
NK109(dze)002:2406: rlung dang nam mkha' lnga'i sgra la bslabs pas mchog
NK109(dze)002:2407: tu sangs rgyas thob pas de nyid la spyod pa
NK109(dze)002:2408: yang dag pa'i lam ltar snang bas /
NK109(dze)002:2409: rags pa'i 'byung ba lnga rang log pas chen po /
NK109(dze)002:2410: zhi ba dkar po dang rgyas pa ser po dang /
NK109(dze)002:2411: dbang gzhi 'dzin pa dmar po dang /
NK109(dze)002:2412: bya rtsal du bral ba'i ljang gu dang /
NK109(dze)002:2413: mi 'gyur ba'i mthing ga lnga nyid chos gzhi ma'i snang bar gsal pas /
NK109(dze)002:2414: de nyid la lus ngag gi gnad kyis ma yengs
NK109(dze)002:2415: pa'i ngang du zhen pa'i 'dzin pa med pa ni
NK109(dze)002:2416: chen po ste / rang sar zhog ces ston pas gdams pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2417: gsang sngags chen po'i mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i ye shes chen po ni /
NK109(dze)002:2418: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes dang /
NK109(dze)002:2422: bya ba grub pa dang lnga'o //
NK109(dze)002:2423: 'od chen po lnga yis gzhan du ma bskyod pas dbyings rnam dag pa'i sgron mar zhog /
NK109(dze)002:2424: de ltar bzhag pas rdo rje mi 'gyur ba sems dpa'/
NK109(dze)002:2425: bdag don dang gzhan don la sems dpa'i snang ba sku dang ye shes su cog bzhag ni /
NK109(dze)002:2426: chos kyi sku las byung ba'i snang ba thams cad
NK109(dze)002:2427: rig pa dang rig pas bsdus pa thams cad ston
NK109(dze)002:2428: pa yin no // ye shes dag pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2429: gnyis kyi snang ba cer re /
NK109(dze)002:2430: dbang po'i sgo la snang bas /
NK109(dze)002:2431: gsang ba'i bzhag thabs ni mig dang /
NK109(dze)002:2432: rig pa nam mkha' gsum cer cer bzhag pas thabs
NK109(dze)002:2433: yin pas ngang phyogs gang du'ang ma lhung ba las
NK109(dze)002:2434: / sku lnga'i snang bas 'byung ba lnga ma spangs par rang dag pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2435: rtsol bas spangs pa ma yin pa rang rang gis
NK109(dze)002:2436: ma bcos par don sgron ma la zhog ces pa'o
NK109(dze)002:2437: // chos nyid rnam par dag pa nam mkha'i klong
NK109(dze)002:2438: las cer mthong du snang bas de thabs chen por
NK109(dze)002:2439: // rtags pas / rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po
NK109(dze)002:2440: rtsol sgrub dang bral ba la sgom rgyu med pas
NK109(dze)002:2441: rkyen dmigs pa rang sar dag ste ma bcos nyid
NK109(dze)002:2442: // rtags pas / do // lta sgom spyod pa'i rang bzhin bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2443: lta ba'i 'dus dbyings kyi sgron ma yin /
NK109(dze)002:2444: zhes pa la sogs pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:2445: lta ba ni yang dag pa'i 'du ba'i sa dbyings
NK109(dze)002:2446: rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma la lta ba ma
NK109(dze)002:2447: yengs na yin / bsgom pa de nyid las ma
NK109(dze)002:2448: g.yos pas bskyal sa rig pa lu gu rgyud kyi
NK109(dze)002:2449: sku yin par rdo rje 'chang gis bstan /
NK109(dze)002:2450: spyod pa'i spyad pa chen po ni de nyid rang
NK109(dze)002:2451: ma bral na lta sgom spyod pa rnam gsum gyi
NK109(dze)002:2452: ngo bo nyid yin par rdo rje sems dpas gsungs
NK109(dze)002:2453: so // de nyid kyi gdams ngag bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2454: sangs pa rags pa'i 'byung ba lnga sku dang ye
NK109(dze)002:2455: shes su rgyas pas de la byar med pa rdzogs
NK109(dze)002:2456: pa chen po'i klong yin pas /
NK109(dze)002:2457: de las ma 'das par gnas na chos nyid logs na bsgrub tu med do //
NK109(dze)002:2458: de'i phyir na de dang ma bral bar gnas pas gsang sngags rnams kyi lta ba'i gdeng rnyed pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2460: yi ge a li dang ka li'i tshogs rig pa la med /
NK109(dze)002:2461: rgyud sangs rgyas nas da lta'i yi ge man chad du bring chags pa /
NK109(dze)002:2462: gsang ba nyan thos la sogs pa la /
NK109(dze)002:2463: chen po skal ldan la snang ba las /
NK109(dze)002:2464: dgongs pa bar med pas sems rtse gcig tu gnas pa /
NK109(dze)002:2466: gzhi'i dngos po'i 'dug tshul la bya /
NK109(dze)002:2467: le'u ni gzhung gi dum bu nges par gcod pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2468: gnyis pa grangs kyi gnas bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2469: da ni le'u gsum pa ma 'khrul pa'i sangs rgyas
NK109(dze)002:2470: la ma byas pa'i chos bstan pa la spyi don
NK109(dze)002:2471: drug gis bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)002:2472: snang ba gsum gyi mtshan nyid bstan pa la nang
NK109(dze)002:2473: gses kyi don bdun du byas pa la dang po
NK109(dze)002:2474: 'gyur ba med pa'i ye shes bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2475: de nas yang rig pa mi 'gyur ba'i klong chos
NK109(dze)002:2476: nyid kyis brgyan pa'i pho brang nas zhes pa la
NK109(dze)002:2478: de nas le'u gnyis pa bstan pa de nas /
NK109(dze)002:2479: yang ni zhes gsum pa bshad pas /
NK109(dze)002:2480: rig pa mi 'gyur ba ston pa'i gnas kyis tshul klong chos kyi dbyings /
NK109(dze)002:2482: kyi 'od dang ye shes kyis brgyan pa'i pho brang
NK109(dze)002:2483: 'og min kyi gnas nas ni de lta bu nas
NK109(dze)002:2484: rig pa de nyid ston pa byung ste dus thams
NK109(dze)002:2485: cad du 'gyur ma myong ba'i ye shes gnyis 'dus
NK109(dze)002:2486: pa'i sku gsum gcig tu gyur pas chen po ste
NK109(dze)002:2487: / 'di zhes le'u gsum pa skad tshig dang yi
NK109(dze)002:2488: ge zhes bcad nas smras pa snang thabs kyi 'khor
NK109(dze)002:2489: / la smras so // don gnyis pa rang bzhin gyi snang ba ngos bzung bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2490: e ma zhes pas bstan te /
NK109(dze)002:2492: zhes ngo mtshar dang bcas pas bos nas /
NK109(dze)002:2493: rang bzhin ni ma bcos pa /
NK109(dze)002:2494: kyi snang ba yul du yod pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:2495: de nyid rnam par dag pa'i yul 'od dang 'od
NK109(dze)002:2496: khyim du gnas gnas pa 'di ni 'od lnga gsal
NK109(dze)002:2497: ba ma 'dres par 'tsher ba zer sna tshogs pa
NK109(dze)002:2498: / sku lnga'i pho brang dbyings te dkyil 'khor du
NK109(dze)002:2499: byung ba de nyid ye nas mi 'gyur bar gnas
NK109(dze)002:2500: / pa'o // gdul bya'i snang ba nges par gzung
NK109(dze)002:2501: bar bstan pa ni 'khrul pa rgyu rkyen dang bcas
NK109(dze)002:2502: pa gcig tu mi gnas pa la bya /
NK109(dze)002:2503: gdul bya 'gro ba rigs drug gi snang ba 'di
NK109(dze)002:2504: ni rags pa dngos po rdzas su yod pa dang
NK109(dze)002:2505: / mtha' med dang gzugs yas pas rdul dang yi ger snang ba la /
NK109(dze)002:2506: de'i 'dul byed sku dang mdzad pa med pa'i thugs
NK109(dze)002:2507: rje rigs mi 'dra ba sna tshogs par sprul nas
NK109(dze)002:2508: don byed pa'o / ye ji bzhin pa'i snang ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2509: chos nyid ye nas ma bcos pa yangs pa dbyings
NK109(dze)002:2510: bsam gyis mi khyab pa'i snang ba rang bzhin kyi
NK109(dze)002:2511: 'od gsal ba gdangs sku dang ye shes kyi cha
NK109(dze)002:2512: / ye shes med pa'i ni mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i
NK109(dze)002:2513: ye shes su phye ba med pas ngo bo ka
NK109(dze)002:2514: dag tu gcig pa las lhun grub kyi rtsal du
NK109(dze)002:2515: / mar 'char ba'o // chas 'jug snang ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2516: gsal ba ni gab pa'i don thal la ngo sprod
NK109(dze)002:2517: pas dad pa can dpe la brten nas snang ba'i
NK109(dze)002:2518: 'od snang ba chen po bar ma do la 'di
NK109(dze)002:2519: ltar snang ba yin zhes pa /
NK109(dze)002:2520: de ji ltar snang zhe na sku lnga'i tshom bu'i
NK109(dze)002:2521: snang ba sna tshogs pa lha dang lha mo nyid
NK109(dze)002:2522: du snang ba de las gsung rang byung gi yi
NK109(dze)002:2523: ge drug ljags kyi dbang po las spros nas gzhan
NK109(dze)002:2524: don ma 'gags ste mos pas spyod pa'i sa la
NK109(dze)002:2526: dag pa stong pa nyid kyi snang ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2527: gzhi ka dag las lhun grub kyi rol pa sna
NK109(dze)002:2528: tshogs su shar ba nyid las sangs rgyas kyi sku'i
NK109(dze)002:2529: 'od kha dog nyi shu rtsa lnga la sogs te
NK109(dze)002:2530: bsam gyis mi khyab par shar ba las /
NK109(dze)002:2531: thig le nyid 'od la 'du ba dang 'phro ba
NK109(dze)002:2532: rab tu zer nyi ma ltar rab tu 'phro zhing
NK109(dze)002:2533: 'bar ba'o // shes rab nyams snang gi snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:2534: gsang sngags a ti chen po'i mdzad pa ni man
NK109(dze)002:2535: ngag dang thabs ma lus par lhag ma med cing
NK109(dze)002:2536: / so sor dbang po'i bye brag du ma las 'phro ba dang gtun te /
NK109(dze)002:2537: ye thog ma nas spros bcas /
NK109(dze)002:2540: rab tu spros med gzhi'i don du gzhag thabs bzhir bsdus nas /
NK109(dze)002:2541: de nyid dang mi 'bral bar blang dor med par bstan no //
NK109(dze)002:2542: don gnyis pa 'khrul pa rang snang gi ye shes
NK109(dze)002:2543: bstan pa la don gnyis kyi dang po skye ba
NK109(dze)002:2544: med pa'i lam bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2545: e ma ho zhes pas ngo mtshar dang bcas pas
NK109(dze)002:2546: bos nas gsang sngags a ti yo ga la thabs
NK109(dze)002:2547: gsang ba de skal ldan la sngags pa de nyid
NK109(dze)002:2548: kyis sems gnas par bya ste /
NK109(dze)002:2549: gzhi gnas kyi ye shes nyid las mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i ye shes chen por 'gyur ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:2550: chos nyid mi snang ba dkyil rig pa 'khor snang ba yin te /
NK109(dze)002:2551: rig pa la skye ba med pa de nyid dbang
NK109(dze)002:2552: po'i mig gis mngon sum du phra rags kyi dri
NK109(dze)002:2553: ma sangs nas 'od dang thig ler rgyas pas /
NK109(dze)002:2554: yul rags pa med de rnam pa sgo lnga'i yul
NK109(dze)002:2555: du dag pa'i snang ba 'od dang zer mthong ba'o
NK109(dze)002:2556: // 'gags med kyi thugs rje bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2557: sku sprul pa'i sku las ye shes rang la rang
NK109(dze)002:2558: chas yod pa de nyid mngon sum du bstan pas
NK109(dze)002:2559: ngang ma bcos pa la rnam par rtog pa rang
NK109(dze)002:2561: chos nyid stong pa nyid spros pa dang bral ba
NK109(dze)002:2562: las ye shes lnga'i 'od thugs rje sprul pa'i skur
NK109(dze)002:2563: 'bar mngon du gdul bya la bstan pas mun pa
NK109(dze)002:2564: 'khor ba ma yin pas snang ba mya ngan las
NK109(dze)002:2566: don gsum pa rig pa'i de bzhin nyid ma spangs
NK109(dze)002:2567: la yongs su rdzogs par bstan pa la gsum gyis
NK109(dze)002:2568: bstan pa'i dang po de'i don zhus par bstan pa
NK109(dze)002:2569: ni / de nas mi snang ba'i snang ba chen
NK109(dze)002:2570: pos ni 'khrul pa rang snang ye shes bstan pa'i
NK109(dze)002:2571: de nas mi snang ba 'khrul pa med pa'i rig
NK109(dze)002:2572: pa nyid snang ba chen pos ni 'khrul pa nyid
NK109(dze)002:2573: la rmi lam kyi rnam par snang la /
NK109(dze)002:2574: rig pa gzhi 'dzin pa'i rig pa dang lhag mthong
NK109(dze)002:2575: sku ni sku gsum gcig du gnas shing dril pa
NK109(dze)002:2576: rgyun 'dabs su / 'brel ma chad par skye bas
NK109(dze)002:2577: lu gu rgyud du snang la dbang po'i yul las
NK109(dze)002:2578: rgyun 'dabs su / / nyid ma bcos pa la 'di ni tshig sgra skad du zhus so //
NK109(dze)002:2579: kye zhes bos nas gsang ba lus med pa la
NK109(dze)002:2580: mi snang bas rig pa lu gu rgyud 'od lnga
NK109(dze)002:2582: bdag ni yid kyi rnam shes rtog pa dang bcas
NK109(dze)002:2583: pas cag /'gyu ba dang 'dzin pa rnams dang bcas
NK109(dze)002:2584: pa la gsal ba'i rang gdangs kyi snang ba bstan
NK109(dze)002:2586: de nas lan du rig pa'i rgyu bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2587: de nas ni zhus ma thag pa nas rig pa
NK109(dze)002:2588: mkha' la khyab ste dbyings gcig tu dril ba'i yul
NK109(dze)002:2589: chen po nas 'di skad ces yid kyi rnam shes
NK109(dze)002:2590: 'khor dang bcas pa la gsungs so //
NK109(dze)002:2591: kye ma zhes bos nas snang ba dbang po'i yul
NK109(dze)002:2592: 'khor dang bcas pa rnams rab tu nyon cig ces
NK109(dze)002:2594: da dngos po'i 'dug tshul ye nas dag pa la
NK109(dze)002:2595: rig pa mngon sum du mthong zhing rtogs pas yang
NK109(dze)002:2596: dag pa'i rig pa'i chos nyid las 'khrul pa ye
NK109(dze)002:2599: rig pa rdo rje'i mi 'gyur ba lu gu rgyud las rgyun bstan pa nyid /
NK109(dze)002:2600: ngo bo ka dag la 'khrul pa med pas sngar
NK109(dze)002:2601: da ltar gang zag gi lus la gnas pa med
NK109(dze)002:2602: pa'i sngon du yang 'khrul ma myong pas /
NK109(dze)002:2603: da lta rig pa'i ngo bo la 'khrul pa med do //
NK109(dze)002:2604: de ltar med pa'i don khong du chud pas phyis 'khrul mi srid pas /
NK109(dze)002:2605: gtan tshigs rig pa ma 'khrul par zhes pa de'i
NK109(dze)002:2606: phyir ma 'khrul pa'i rig pa la ma rig pa
NK109(dze)002:2607: sangs te sku dang ye shes su rgyas so //
NK109(dze)002:2608: dbyings kyi rgyu bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2609: dbyings ni phyi'i nam mkha' dang /
NK109(dze)002:2610: nang gi dbyings 'od dang kha dog /
NK109(dze)002:2611: gsang ba'i dbyings sgron ma las nyon mongs pa'i dri ma dag pas /
NK109(dze)002:2612: yang dag don gyi sgron ma de nyid kyang /
NK109(dze)002:2613: rtag pa'i ye shes ltar sngar lus la ma brten pa'i dus na sus kyang ma byas pas /
NK109(dze)002:2614: da ltar rtsol ba dang bcas nas mi byed par rang sar bzhag pas /
NK109(dze)002:2615: phyis mi phyed pa ni mngal gyi grong khyer du
NK109(dze)002:2616: mi 'jug pas 'khor bar gnas par mi 'gyur ro
NK109(dze)002:2617: // gtan tshigs yul can du ma'i rtog pa chod
NK109(dze)002:2618: pa de'i phyir ma byas pa'i chos ni rang bzhin
NK109(dze)002:2619: rdzogs pa chen po'i rtsol bsgrub dang bral ba zhes
NK109(dze)002:2620: // bya'o // de yang nyams su blang bya dang
NK109(dze)002:2621: sbyar na lus ma bcos par dal bar gnas pas
NK109(dze)002:2622: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub thob pas chen
NK109(dze)002:2623: // bya'o // po'o // ngag gi ma slad par
NK109(dze)002:2624: 'khrul pa'i gtan rgyud dang bral bar gnas pas brjod
NK109(dze)002:2625: du med pa'i gzhi rnyed pas chen po'o //
NK109(dze)002:2626: yid kyi dran bsam bcad nas sgron ma gtad nas
NK109(dze)002:2627: gang du yang ma skyur bas snang ba'i 'phel dang
NK109(dze)002:2629: chen po gsum ni lus sprul sku la dbang thob /
NK109(dze)002:2631: yid chos sku la dbang thob pas bdag nyid gcig
NK109(dze)002:2632: pu zla dang bral bas snang ba'i grogs dang ldan
NK109(dze)002:2633: pa ni / ma 'khrul pa ni rig pa la
NK109(dze)002:2634: gdos bcas kyi dri mas sangs pas rig pa nyid
NK109(dze)002:2635: gcer bu gling par rgyas pa de sus kyang ma
NK109(dze)002:2636: byas par rang gis rang mthong pa las byung bas
NK109(dze)002:2637: chos las 'das pas bsgrub tu med par bstan pa
NK109(dze)002:2638: pa ni / zhes bya'o // rig pa'i dbyings la
NK109(dze)002:2639: bzang ngan med par bstan pa la bzhis bstan pa'i
NK109(dze)002:2640: pa ni / zhes bya'o // dang po / rig pa'i rang sa bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2641: rig pa lhag mthong rdo rje ni mi 'gyur lu
NK109(dze)002:2642: gu rgyud kyi sku snang ba'i cha nas bzhag pa'i
NK109(dze)002:2643: nyid ni // sngar lus la ma brten pa'i dus
NK109(dze)002:2644: na 'khor ba zhes bya bar grub pa med pas
NK109(dze)002:2646: mya ngan las 'das pa yang nyams su myong pa
NK109(dze)002:2647: med pas de lta bu'i nyams khong du chud pa'i
NK109(dze)002:2648: skal ldan la rig pa nyid da lta dang 'khor
NK109(dze)002:2649: ba'i nyes skyon med pas gnas gcig tu 'khor ba
NK109(dze)002:2651: phyis mngal gyi grong khyer du mi 'jug pas lus nyid du 'khor ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:2652: lus la rig pa gnas pa ma yin no //
NK109(dze)002:2653: dbyings kyi rang sa bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2654: dbyings rgya che zhing mtha' dbus med pa rnam pa
NK109(dze)002:2655: yul du 'dzin pa dag pa'i sgron ma snang ba
NK109(dze)002:2656: nyid ni / lus la ma brten pa'i dus dang da lta gnyis la khyad par med pas ni /
NK109(dze)002:2657: sngar sems rnam par rtog pas slad pa can de
NK109(dze)002:2658: dang ldan pa de nyid dang bral ba 'pho 'gyur
NK109(dze)002:2659: med par gnas pa'i de la sems kyi myong byed
NK109(dze)002:2660: med pas / da 'khor ba ye sangs rgyas pas
NK109(dze)002:2661: sems can dang sangs rgyas gnyis med du khong du
NK109(dze)002:2663: dngos po gshis la srid par 'char byed ma 'gags pa'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)002:2664: phyis kyang rig pa dang dbyings gnyis su med par 'dres pa nyid las 'bral bar mi 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)002:2665: gtan tshigs rig pa'i ngo bo dbyings la khyab pa de'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)002:2666: snang ba ni ming du med pa las snang ba'i ming du mar shar ba'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)002:2667: rig pa'i ngo bo bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2668: rig pa lu gu rgyud kyi sku snang cha nas bzhag pa de nyid /
NK109(dze)002:2669: ye nas bud+d+ha tha mar bzhugs pas 'khor ba nyid
NK109(dze)002:2670: grub pa med pas sangs rgyas kyang ma grub pas
NK109(dze)002:2671: sngar lus la brten pa'i dus nas sangs rgyas ma
NK109(dze)002:2672: myong bas / da sangs rgyas rgyu med pas sangs rgyas mi srid de /
NK109(dze)002:2673: de'i gnad kyis phyis lus bor ba'i dus na yang sangs rgyas par mi 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)002:2674: dbyings kyi ngo bo bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2675: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma de nyid ni /
NK109(dze)002:2676: dngos po 'dug tshul la sems can grub pa med
NK109(dze)002:2677: pas sngar lus la ma brten pa'i dus na sems
NK109(dze)002:2678: can ming du med pas gnas pa zhes ma myong
NK109(dze)002:2679: bas / da lta bas de'i don la mi gnas
NK109(dze)002:2680: par shes na srid pa'i 'khor lo la 'jug mi
NK109(dze)002:2681: bas / srid pa / de'i stobs kyis sems can
NK109(dze)002:2682: gyi lus la brten cing gnas par mi 'gyur ro
NK109(dze)002:2683: bas / srid pa / // gtan tshigs dbyings rig
NK109(dze)002:2684: ye sangs rgyas par bzhugs pa de'i phyir na lung
NK109(dze)002:2687: byin gyis rlabs pa gsum ye nas bud+d+ha la bstan
NK109(dze)002:2688: du med kyang bla ma'i gdams ngag la brten nas
NK109(dze)002:2689: mtshon du med pas snying po'i rang gnad ces bya'o
NK109(dze)002:2690: // rig pa rang rdzogs su bstan pa la gzhi
NK109(dze)002:2691: bstan pa'i dang po 'khor 'das gnyis su med par
NK109(dze)002:2692: bsre ba'i man ngag dran par bya ba bstan pa
NK109(dze)002:2694: zhes ngo mtshar ba dang bcas pas snang ba'i tshogs
NK109(dze)002:2695: la bos nas rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud
NK109(dze)002:2696: la rgyu 'bras sangs rang ngo rgyas pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2697: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma sems can gyi lam rten du bzhugs pa gnyis ni /
NK109(dze)002:2698: sngar lus la ma brten pa'i dus na 'du 'bral
NK109(dze)002:2699: med par gnas pas rgyab tha dad du gyes pa
NK109(dze)002:2700: med pas 'khor 'das gnyis su nyams su ma myong
NK109(dze)002:2701: pas / da lta yang 'du 'bral med par dus
NK109(dze)002:2702: thams cad du gnyis med du gyes pa med pa
NK109(dze)002:2703: ni srid pa'i yul la rtog bcas su 'phro mi
NK109(dze)002:2704: pas / srid pas / phyis lus dang bral ba'i
NK109(dze)002:2705: dus na yang dbyings rig gnyis rgyu gyes par mi
NK109(dze)002:2706: pas / srid pas / 'gyur ro // gtan tshigs
NK109(dze)002:2707: dbyings rig gnyis kyi ngo bo la 'khor 'das gnyis
NK109(dze)002:2708: su med par 'dres pas de'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)002:2709: lung gsum la 'khrul pa rgyu rkyen mtshungs pa gsum dbyings dang rig pa la med pa la /
NK109(dze)002:2710: bla ma'i gdams ngag gis bstan pas 'khrul pa dang
NK109(dze)002:2711: ma 'khrul par bstan la phab pas 'khrul pa 'byung
NK109(dze)002:2713: 'khor 'das ngo sprad pa'i gdams ngag dran par bya bar bstan par ni /
NK109(dze)002:2714: sems can kyis 'khor ba la spyod cing yang nas
NK109(dze)002:2715: yang du 'khor te de na gnas kyang 'khor ba'i
NK109(dze)002:2716: mtshan nyid sngar ma mthong pas bla ma'i gdams ngag
NK109(dze)002:2717: med pa dang / rang la skal pa dang dad
NK109(dze)002:2718: pa med pa rnams kyis da yang 'khor ba'i mtshan
NK109(dze)002:2719: nyid mi mthong pas 'khor ba la byings kyang skal
NK109(dze)002:2720: med rnams kyis mthong bar mi 'gyur /
NK109(dze)002:2721: gtan tshigs 'das pa la 'khor ba ma grub par gnas te /
NK109(dze)002:2722: de'i rtsal chos nyid la rtogs pa'i rang bzhin du
NK109(dze)002:2723: med kyang skal pa med pa'i gang zag gis dus
NK109(dze)002:2724: gnyis su rtogs ma myong pa de'i phyir na 'khor
NK109(dze)002:2725: ba la yun ring bar gnas pa zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:2726: de ltar 'khor ba'i snang ba de las ye shes
NK109(dze)002:2727: rang grol gyi gdams ngag dran par bya ba ni
NK109(dze)002:2728: / yang ni mnan pa ste dag pa rtogs pa
NK109(dze)002:2729: sngon du skur pa'i sangs rgyas kyis rig pa rdo
