NK109(dze)002:2730: rje lu gu rgyud kyi sku nyid yinaranga pas gzhan
NK109(dze)002:2731: nas rtogs bya'i yul med par sngar 'das pa'i dus
NK109(dze)002:2733: da yang gzhan du mi rtog pas /
NK109(dze)002:2734: ma 'ongs pa'i dus phyis kyang gzhan 'byung du rtogs par mi 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)002:2735: gtan tshigs 'khor ba nyid rang grol ba de'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)002:2736: sangs rgyas la rnam par rtog pa ye nas med
NK109(dze)002:2737: ma myong ste yul tha dad du med pa yin
NK109(dze)002:2738: kyang sems can kyi snang tshul la rnam par rtog
NK109(dze)002:2739: pa du ma byung bas dbyings rig rang grol du
NK109(dze)002:2740: rtogs pa la gzhan 'byung gi chos med pa zhes
NK109(dze)002:2741: bya'o // rig pa spyi blugs kyi man ngag dran par bya ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2742: rig pa nyid la 'byung ba bzhi'i dri ma rang
NK109(dze)002:2743: sangs nas mkhyen pa'i ye shes su rgyas pa dbyings
NK109(dze)002:2744: bsam gyis mi khyab par shar ba sems yin la
NK109(dze)002:2745: / de nyid sku dang ye shes kyi gnas su
NK109(dze)002:2746: gyur pas can zhes bya ba gnyis dus chen po
NK109(dze)002:2747: bral ba med par ye nas bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2748: des na rig pa rang gi gnas lugs nyid la
NK109(dze)002:2749: 'khrul pa med kyang snang ba thabs yul can la
NK109(dze)002:2750: 'khrul ltar byung bas de nyid 'khrul gzhi rtsad bcad
NK109(dze)002:2751: pas ye shes rang lugs su log pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2752: gtan tshigs sangs rgyas dang sems can gzhi las ma
NK109(dze)002:2753: g.yos pa de'i phyir na ngo bo la gcig par
NK109(dze)002:2755: rig pa'i mkha' dbyings bstan pa la gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)002:2756: zhen pa'i blos sangs par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2757: e ma ho zhes snang ba la ngo mtshar bos
NK109(dze)002:2758: nas dgongs gcig ni thig le nyag gcig gi don
NK109(dze)002:2759: la gnas pa ste mkha' rig pa klong dbyings te
NK109(dze)002:2760: dbyings rig gnyis su med pa de nyid /
NK109(dze)002:2761: gsang sngags kyi lta ba rdo rje 'dus ma byas pa /
NK109(dze)002:2762: sems pa don gnyis byed pa rig pa shes shing rang rig tu yod pa /
NK109(dze)002:2763: sku sku gsum gcig tu dril ba lu gu rgyud de /
NK109(dze)002:2764: rang bzhin stong pa'i ngos nas rtag pa ma yin /
NK109(dze)002:2765: snying po gsal ba'i cha nas chad pa'i lta ba nyid yongs kyis med pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2766: 'o na de stong pa phyang chad pa ma yin
NK109(dze)002:2767: te 'od lnga 'gags pa med par snang bas stong
NK109(dze)002:2768: pa ma yin / 'od de mtshan ma zhen yul
NK109(dze)002:2769: dang bcas par med pas gsal ba ngang gis med
NK109(dze)002:2770: de gting yangs su gnas pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2771: stong pa dang gsal ba gnyis rgyu mthun pa ma
NK109(dze)002:2772: yin te stong pa yul yin la gsal ba gdangs
NK109(dze)002:2773: yin pas de gnyis ka'i snang ba rang sar rig
NK109(dze)002:2775: de gnyis ka 'byung ba phyis kyi tshul ma yin
NK109(dze)002:2776: par rig pa las byung ba'i tshul du ma spangs
NK109(dze)002:2777: la yongs su dgag sgrub med par rdzogs pas /
NK109(dze)002:2778: de la skyed pa'i rim pa'i tshul du rim pas ma yin te /
NK109(dze)002:2779: snang ba cig char du rang snang rang gi tshul
NK109(dze)002:2780: las 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa gnyis
NK109(dze)002:2781: su snang ba ltar stong pa dang gsal ba rang
NK109(dze)002:2782: rgyud du bzung bas gol te snang ngo //
NK109(dze)002:2783: 'khrul pa'i yul spang bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2784: de lta bu'i chos nyid stong gsal rig pa'i snying
NK109(dze)002:2785: po la ming dang yi ge dang tha snyad kyi
NK109(dze)002:2786: tshogs de dag thams cad ye nas yang dag pa
NK109(dze)002:2787: nyid du bral ba de nyid ni /
NK109(dze)002:2788: yul gang la snang na dag pa sprin dang bral
NK109(dze)002:2789: ba'i nam mkha' la ngos gzung med par zang thal
NK109(dze)002:2790: du snang ba ni rtag chad du kun las 'das
NK109(dze)002:2791: pa'i don de / skye ba med par ye nam
NK109(dze)002:2792: mkha' dang gnyis su med par gnas pa a'i snang
NK109(dze)002:2793: ba 'od lnga yang ye nas skye med las ngos
NK109(dze)002:2794: 'di dang 'di la yod pa dang med pa las
NK109(dze)002:2795: 'das pas 'di lta bur gzung du med /
NK109(dze)002:2796: gnyis su med pa'i yang dag pa'i ye shes nam mkha' la gsal ba de nyid la /
NK109(dze)002:2797: lu gu rgyud la 'gro 'ong yod pas bya byed
NK109(dze)002:2798: ma 'gags pa ye shes kyi rlung gis bskyod pa
NK109(dze)002:2799: ste de la dmigs pa yongs su dag pas rnam
NK109(dze)002:2800: par rtog pa'i bdag gis gos pa med pa ni
NK109(dze)002:2801: / dper na de nyid rang bzhin med pa de
NK109(dze)002:2802: me long nang gi gzugs brnyan dang ltar snang yul
NK109(dze)002:2803: du nam mkha' la snang ste gzung yul zhen pa'i
NK109(dze)002:2805: de yang ma 'gags par zang thal bas ngo bo
NK109(dze)002:2806: la 'gags pa med par snang ba de nyid kun
NK109(dze)002:2807: gyi snying por ye nas gnas pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2808: de lta bu ni theg pa thun mong pa las
NK109(dze)002:2809: gsang ba 'di nyid kyi gnas lugs de nyid dang
NK109(dze)002:2810: 'du 'bral med par de bzhin nyid du gnas pa
NK109(dze)002:2811: yin no // sku gsung thugs kyi snang ba bstan
NK109(dze)002:2812: pa las don gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang po sku
NK109(dze)002:2813: gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2814: kye rig pa nyid rang don mthar phyin pas kye gzhan don la thogs med du byed pas /
NK109(dze)002:2815: gdul bya'i yul mi 'dra ba tha dad pa la /
NK109(dze)002:2816: 'dul byed kyi sku mi 'dra ba tha dad par sprul nas /
NK109(dze)002:2817: snang ba thub pa drug la sogs par snang ba ma 'gags pas /
NK109(dze)002:2818: de'i gsung so so dang mthun par rol pas /
NK109(dze)002:2819: cir yang rigs drug so so mthun par ston pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:2820: de ltar sna tshogs pa'i snang ba ston kyang rig
NK109(dze)002:2821: pa'i ngo bo la bud+d+ha dang sems can la khyad
NK109(dze)002:2823: thugs kyis mdzad cing ci'i ngo bor yang med pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2824: rig pas 'khrul pa'i bya byed gcad par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2825: rig pa'i bya ba dang byed pa ma 'gags par snang bas /
NK109(dze)002:2826: sems kyi bsam pa du mar shar te yul so
NK109(dze)002:2827: sor bcad pas rnam par rtog pa sna tshogs par
NK109(dze)002:2828: byung bas sems can gyis rig pa nyid ngo ma
NK109(dze)002:2829: shes pas na sems dang rig pa 'dres shing mtshungs
NK109(dze)002:2830: pa'o // zhes rig pa'i ngo bo la yi ger
NK109(dze)002:2831: bris pa dang 'bri ba'i mkhan po dang 'bri bar
NK109(dze)002:2832: byed pa med pa'i rgyud 'brel ba lu gu rgyud
NK109(dze)002:2833: gsang ba chen po las tshig tu 'phros pa /
NK109(dze)002:2834: ma 'khrul rig pa nyid la ye nas 'khrul ma myong bas /
NK109(dze)002:2835: de la lus kyang byas pa med pa'i chos a
NK109(dze)002:2836: ti yo ga bstan pa'i le'u gzhung gi dum bu
NK109(dze)002:2838: gsum pa ni gnyis pa bshad pa'i 'og ma bstan pa grangs kyi gnas gzhan bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2840: le'u bzhi pa pad+ma kha 'byed pa bstan par bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:2841: don dam snang ba'i le'u 'di la bsdus pa'i don bzhi'i bstan pa las /
NK109(dze)002:2842: don dang po rig pa'i ngo bo bstan pa la /
NK109(dze)002:2843: nang gses kyi don gnyis kyis dang po rol pa'i don zhus par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2844: le'u gsum pa bstan pa'i de nas yang tshig 'di skad du /
NK109(dze)002:2845: rgyu ma rig pa'i bya ba med pa'i rig pa ye nas ka dag pas /
NK109(dze)002:2846: lung byed pa med pa'i lhun grub kyi snang ba
NK109(dze)002:2847: shar ba kun tu de ni yon tan sna tshogs
NK109(dze)002:2849: ngan pa med pas bzang po /
NK109(dze)002:2850: skyon las 'das pas bka' phyin ci ma log pa //
NK109(dze)002:2851: rna ba'i dbang por rtsal ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:2852: snang ngo de ltar shar ba yi /
NK109(dze)002:2853: de'i tshe thabs sla ba'i man ngag las byung ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:2854: sna tshogs par ston pas 'gags pa med pa'i gnad
NK109(dze)002:2855: bsdus pas rang snang rna ba'i dbang pos bcad pas
NK109(dze)002:2856: mnyan pa'o // don gsum pa mthar phyin pas kye
NK109(dze)002:2857: kye snang ba'i sgyu 'phrul pa nyid kyang dmigs pa
NK109(dze)002:2858: dang bral ba'i ye shes chen po dang ye nas
NK109(dze)002:2859: ldan pa yin par sems can kyis ma rtogs pas
NK109(dze)002:2860: rol pa'i don du byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:2861: rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyi sku'i rol pa bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:2862: rdo rig pa mi 'gyur ba las rje ye shes
NK109(dze)002:2863: thams cad kyi 'byung gnas lu gu rgyud rgyun 'dabs
NK109(dze)002:2864: sbyor du skye ba sku gsum gcig du dril ba
NK109(dze)002:2865: ni grangs med pa'i snang ba chen po ni /
NK109(dze)002:2866: sku gsum dang bzhi dang lnga dang sku gcig pa
NK109(dze)002:2867: dang thig le rang bzhin gyi thig le kun khyab
NK109(dze)002:2869: kun tu bzang po'i thig le yon tan thams cad du shar te /
NK109(dze)002:2871: chos nyid spros pa med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2872: don dam pa'i thig le yul thams cad las 'das pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2873: kun rdzob kyi thig le rgyu dang rkyen gyis rnam par snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:2874: thig le'i phyed sku ni phyed ces phyed kyi don
NK109(dze)002:2875: dam pa'i rgyu byung bas sku phyed pa'i sgron ma
NK109(dze)002:2876: bzhi yin la / rkyen nyams su len pa rgyun
NK109(dze)002:2877: ma chad pa las 'bras bu sku rnams su smin
NK109(dze)002:2878: bzhi yin la / la / phyed kun rdzob kyi
NK109(dze)002:2879: thig le rgyu 'byung ba 'dus pa ma'i thig les
NK109(dze)002:2880: bzhi yin la / la / lus skyed la /
NK109(dze)002:2881: rkyen skye ba bzhis 'byung ba las gzugs sku tha
NK109(dze)002:2883: pha'i rgyu byang chub kyi sems kyi snyigs ma 'dus pas dran bsam du ma skyed la /
NK109(dze)002:2884: rkyen skye ba bzhis bsdus pa'i sems can tha dad par smin bas na phyed sku ste /
NK109(dze)002:2886: kun rdzob kyi lus su smin pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2887: nyams len gyis dus 'od kyi thig le'i dbus su
NK109(dze)002:2888: sku lte ba yan chod du snang ba re re
NK109(dze)002:2889: 'char bas na thig le'i phyed sku dang zhes pa'o
NK109(dze)002:2890: // ye shes dang gzhi gnas kyi ye shes gsum /
NK109(dze)002:2891: ye shes dang ni mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i ye shes lnga las /
NK109(dze)002:2892: gzugs sku ni 'od dang kha dog tu snang bas sku /
NK109(dze)002:2893: 'od dang dkar po dri ma dag pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:2894: yon tan rdzogs pa'i ser po dang /
NK109(dze)002:2895: ma chags dag pa'i dmar po dang /
NK109(dze)002:2896: bya rtsol bral ba'i ljang gu dang /
NK109(dze)002:2898: 'od kyi 'ja' gur ni gyen bsgreng du snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:2902: mu khyud du snang ba la bya /
NK109(dze)002:2903: de'i ngo bo la dbugs 'gag pa dang bcas pa
NK109(dze)002:2904: med pas srog med pa'i sku zang thal dang bcas
NK109(dze)002:2905: pa'o // 'gyu ba ye shes kyi rlung la brten
NK109(dze)002:2906: pas sems kyi bsam pa med pa'i gnad kyis snang
NK109(dze)002:2907: ba'i 'od de thig le dang sku sna tshogs par
NK109(dze)002:2908: snang ba dang ye nas 'du 'bral med par gnas
NK109(dze)002:2909: pa'o // ba'o // don gnyis la dbyings kyi sgron
NK109(dze)002:2910: ma'i ngo bo bapastana la gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang
NK109(dze)002:2911: pa'o // ba'o // po / dbyings dngos bstan pa ni dbyings ni rig pa'i gnas la bya /
NK109(dze)002:2912: rnam pa 'byung ba bzhi dag pas sgron ma ye shes kyi snang ba rang gsal ba la bya //
NK109(dze)002:2913: 'di'i ngo bo la lta ba ni dgongs pa ste rnam pa rtog pa rgyu mi srid do //
NK109(dze)002:2914: khyab pa med pa ni bem po la med la
NK109(dze)002:2915: rang mdangs mthing ga las 'od lnga'i snang ba 'gyur
NK109(dze)002:2916: ma bcas pas te rig pa nyid dang /
NK109(dze)002:2917: yul sgo lnga'i gzugs la sogs pa med pa'i gsal
NK109(dze)002:2918: ba yi ge'i na ro lta bu'i cha 'od lnga
NK109(dze)002:2919: dang bcas pa / sus kyang ma byas par rang 'byung ba'i 'od kyi ra ba dang bcas pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2920: dbyings kyi snang ba bstan pa ni skyes bu rtsol
NK109(dze)002:2921: bas ma bris pa'i 'od kyi mu khyud zlum por
NK109(dze)002:2923: dbang po so sos ma bcad pa'i yul 'od dang zer du bcas pa /
NK109(dze)002:2924: ye nas rang byung du mthing ga la sogs pa'i
NK109(dze)002:2925: snang ba spel zhing ri mo mkhan lta bu'i ma
NK109(dze)002:2926: bkod par snang ba rang rdzogs pas 'od dang 'od
NK109(dze)002:2928: don gsum pa 'du 'bral med pa'i ye shes bstan
NK109(dze)002:2929: pa la gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang po de nyid
NK109(dze)002:2931: de yang zhes pa dbyings dang rig pa gnyis 'du 'bral med par gnas te /
NK109(dze)002:2932: gang gis kyang ma dmigs te yul dang yul can
NK109(dze)002:2933: du ma bcad pa'i snang ba gang gis kyang ngo
NK109(dze)002:2934: bor ma grub pa chen po ste /
NK109(dze)002:2935: de la dri ma ma rig pa gsum dang rkyen bzhi dang /
NK109(dze)002:2937: sgrib pa gnyis kyi phyogs med pa la rang gis
NK109(dze)002:2938: ngo bor rang snang du bzhugs pa ni sus kyang
NK109(dze)002:2940: mtshan ma zil gyis mnan par bya ba'i gdams ngag dran pa bya ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:2941: dbyings dang rig pa de'i ngo bo la rgyu ma
NK109(dze)002:2942: rig pa sangs pas dmigs pa yul gyi rkyen la
NK109(dze)002:2943: sogs pa bzhi dag /'khrul pa'i dus na yul sna
NK109(dze)002:2944: tshogs ma 'gags par shar yang de nyid rang grol
NK109(dze)002:2945: bas / rang gi ngo bo rdo rje lu gu rgyud dang bcas pa nyid /
NK109(dze)002:2946: gzugs la sogs pa'i yul drug las 'das pas /
NK109(dze)002:2947: sa sra ba med par brtan pa chen po 'od ser po dang /
NK109(dze)002:2948: chu gsher ba med pa'i 'od dkar po chen po dang /
NK109(dze)002:2949: me tsha ba med pa'i sreg pa chen po dmar po dang /
NK109(dze)002:2950: rlung g.yo ba med pa'i bskyod pa ljang gu chen po'o //
NK109(dze)002:2951: nam mkha' khyab pa med pa'i gdangs can mthing ga
NK109(dze)002:2952: chen po lnga chos nyid rang zad pa'i dbyings su
NK109(dze)002:2953: rang dag pas / snang ba'i ngo bo gang du yang grub rgyu med pas /
NK109(dze)002:2954: de nyid la 'jigs pa med pas phyis kyang mi
NK109(dze)002:2955: 'jigs pa de la rkyen gyis mi shigs pas yul
NK109(dze)002:2957: ngo mtshar zad pa mtshan nyid shes pas che ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:2958: de la theg pa rim pa dgu'i grub pa'i matha'i phyogs gang du yang mi 'dzin pas /
NK109(dze)002:2959: thog ma rang gi rig pa lta byed ma 'gags pa las byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:2960: dbyings rig gnyis su med pa'i lta ba bstan pa
NK109(dze)002:2961: la gnyis kyi dang po sku ngo bo bstan pa
NK109(dze)002:2962: ni / kye ma zhes nges pa kho nar snang ba la bos nas /
NK109(dze)002:2963: nyams gong du 'phel ba'i snang ba las ye shes
NK109(dze)002:2964: dang 'od kyi sku bsam gyis mi khyab byung ba
NK109(dze)002:2965: de dag ni / sngon du du ma'i tha snyad
NK109(dze)002:2966: thams cad ma spangs bas rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen
NK109(dze)002:2967: po bya rtsol las 'das pa nyid kyi klong du
NK109(dze)002:2968: ye nas ma bcos par chub pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2969: sangs rgyas kyi sku ni gzugs ma spangs pa yongs
NK109(dze)002:2970: su rdzogs pas rnam par snang mdzad kyi sku dang
NK109(dze)002:2971: / rnam shes ma spangs pa yongs su rdzogs pas rdo rje mi bskyod pa'i sku dang /
NK109(dze)002:2972: tshor ba ma spangs pa yongs su rdzogs pas rin po che 'byung ldan kyi sku dang /
NK109(dze)002:2973: 'du shes ma spangs la yongs su rdzogs pas snang ba mtha' yas kyi sku dang /
NK109(dze)002:2974: 'du byed ma spangs la yongs su rdzogs pas don
NK109(dze)002:2975: yod grub pa'i sku dang lnga po 'di dag rtsol
NK109(dze)002:2976: ba med par ye nas skyed mi dgos par gnas
NK109(dze)002:2978: rab tu mang bar 'phro ba ni sems dpa' dang
NK109(dze)002:2979: sems ma dang so so'i rigs kyi tshom bu nas
NK109(dze)002:2981: de yang gang las 'phros na rig pa las so //
NK109(dze)002:2982: ci'i phyir 'phro na rang gi rtsal rdzogs pa dang cho 'phrul bstan pa'i phyir /
NK109(dze)002:2983: 'phros pa la dgos pa ci yod na chos sku
NK109(dze)002:2984: khyab bdal chen po las longs sku mtshan dang dpe
NK109(dze)002:2985: byad du byung / de las sprul sku gang 'dul
NK109(dze)002:2986: ba'i gzugs su sprul nas don byed pas dgos pa
NK109(dze)002:2987: byad du byung / yod / ji ltar 'phros na rigs lnga'i gtso bo dang /
NK109(dze)002:2989: gang du 'phro na gnas nyams len gyi dus la nam ka dag pa la 'phro la /
NK109(dze)002:2990: rang bzhin lam snang gi dus na chos nyid kyi
NK109(dze)002:2991: bar ma do la 'og min gyi gnas zhes bya
NK109(dze)002:2992: bar 'phros pas / nam ka la chu bur gyi mig gis tshugs pa med par snang la /
NK109(dze)002:2993: bar do la shes rab kyi mig gis tshugs pa med par snang bas /
NK109(dze)002:2994: de la nyon mongs pa gang gis kyang mi tshugs pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:2995: de ltar sna tshogs su snang yang ngo bo rig
NK109(dze)002:2996: pa chos kyi sku las g.yos pa med bzhin du
NK109(dze)002:2997: / longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku mtshan dang dpe byad
NK109(dze)002:2998: sna tshogs par ston pa ni dper na nyi ma
NK109(dze)002:3000: de ltar longs sku 'khor ba las 'das nas kyang /
NK109(dze)002:3001: gdul bya sems can rnams mya ngan las 'das par
NK109(dze)002:3002: mtshon pa'i phyir sprul pa'i sku gdul byed thub pa
NK109(dze)002:3003: chen po rnams su sprul nas gzhan don rdzogs par
NK109(dze)002:3004: byed pa'o // rang bzhin bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3005: chos dag pa sku mi 'gyur ba de nyid snang
NK109(dze)002:3006: ba la ngos bzung nas gang la 'dzin pa'i shes
NK109(dze)002:3007: pa ma bzhugs pa de las gzhan du 'phro ba
NK109(dze)002:3008: med par gnas pa de las ma g.yos pa de
NK109(dze)002:3009: nyid do // de ltar byung tshor kun du snang
NK109(dze)002:3010: yang nyon mongs pa gzhan gyis rang gi rig pa
NK109(dze)002:3011: nyid zil gyis mi non pa nyid ni chos sku'i
NK109(dze)002:3012: rang bzhin te dper na gzu bo'i blo can gyis
NK109(dze)002:3013: lha khang du phyin pa lta bu'o //
NK109(dze)002:3014: de kho na rig pa g.yos pa med pas sku
NK109(dze)002:3015: ste gas la ba rang shes su gsal ba la
NK109(dze)002:3016: cha nyon mongs pa'i phyogs su ma lhung /
NK109(dze)002:3017: yod pa dang med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3018: snang ba dang stong pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3019: chos dang chos ma yin pa'i phyogs su ma lhung bas snyoms pa chen po ste /
NK109(dze)002:3020: de yi ngo bo mi 'gyur bas rdo rje lta
NK109(dze)002:3021: bu'i sku'i snang ba chos kyi dbyings kyi rang bzhin
NK109(dze)002:3022: rgya che tshad med pa nyams su blangs pa'i tshe
NK109(dze)002:3023: skal ldan gyis mthong bar 'gyur ro //
NK109(dze)002:3024: de ltar thams cad rig pa chos kyi sku'i rang bzhin du shar yang /
NK109(dze)002:3025: ngo bo 'khor 'das 'dzin pa'i snga dbyings dang rig
NK109(dze)002:3026: pa gnyis la byed pa nyid las rab tu 'das
NK109(dze)002:3027: pa ni // ngang dang rang bzhin dang /
NK109(dze)002:3028: bdag nyid chen po gsum du rang bzhin du bzhugs /
NK109(dze)002:3029: dper na mar me dang mar me'i rkyen nang 'od bzhin no //
NK109(dze)002:3030: zhes ni don dam pa'i rig pa chos kyi sku
NK109(dze)002:3031: las rtags bkod pa'i yi ge a li dang ka
NK109(dze)002:3032: li'i tshogs med pa la rgyud gsang ba chen po
NK109(dze)002:3033: las / le'u mtshan don gyi don dam pa rang gi rig pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3034: brjod pa'i don dam pa de nyid gtan la 'bebs pa'i tshig dang yi ge 'di dag dang /
NK109(dze)002:3035: thob pa don dam pa ni de nyid la brten nas rig pa mngon sum du rtogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3036: de ltar rig pa don yin pa la dam pa
NK109(dze)002:3037: bla ma'i man ngag gis gdams pas snang ba ye
NK109(dze)002:3038: ji bzhin pa'i snang ba 'di nyid la gtan la
NK109(dze)002:3039: phebs pa'o // de yang snang ba ni gsum ste
NK109(dze)002:3040: da so so med pa ye ji bzhin snang ba
NK109(dze)002:3041: chos thams cad zad pa la bya /
NK109(dze)002:3042: rig pa rang snang gi snang ba nyams gong du 'phel ba rnams la bya /
NK109(dze)002:3043: chos nyid la ma bkod pa'i snang ba da so so 'dug tshul la bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:3044: le'u ni gzhung gi dum bu nges par gcod par
NK109(dze)002:3045: byed pa bzhi ba ni gsum pa bstan pa'i 'og
NK109(dze)002:3046: tu grangs kyi gnas gzhan no //
NK109(dze)002:3047: da ni le'u lnga pa pad+ma kha 'byed pa ston te /
NK109(dze)002:3048: le'u lnga pa rdzogs pa chen po tshig gis gol
NK109(dze)002:3049: bar bstan pa 'di la bsdus pa'i don bzhi'i bstan
NK109(dze)002:3050: pa'i dang po // rig pa'i ye shes bya rtsol
NK109(dze)002:3051: dang bral bar bstan pa la nang gses kyi don
NK109(dze)002:3052: pa'i dang po // gnyis las / dang po stong pa'i ye shes bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3053: le'u bzhi pa bshad pa'i de nas yang lnga pa ston te /
NK109(dze)002:3054: rdo rje 'chang chen po rig pa rang byung ba
NK109(dze)002:3055: nyid yul sgo lnga'i zhen pa tha dad du 'dzin
NK109(dze)002:3056: pa med pa'i chos nyid kyi klong nyon mongs pa
NK109(dze)002:3057: rang bzhin gyis dag pa las /
NK109(dze)002:3058: snang ba ni rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i snang
NK109(dze)002:3059: ba mtshan ma'i spros pa thams cad nye bar zhi
NK109(dze)002:3060: ba dang / yang dag bkod pa'i snang ba ye
NK109(dze)002:3061: shes rnams kyi 'byung gnas las ni snang ba gsum
NK109(dze)002:3062: du byung ste de bzhin gshegs pa'i snang ba mkhyen
NK109(dze)002:3063: pa ma 'gags pa gzigs snang du mar byung ba
NK109(dze)002:3064: ba dang / dang / da dngos po med pas snang ba stong pa kun la khyab pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3065: rig pa rang snang gi snang ba dbyings su shar ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:3066: chos nyid ma bkod pa'i snang ba ni dri ma gang gis kyang ma gos pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3067: ye shes phyogs dag pa'i snang ba sku dang ye
NK109(dze)002:3068: shes dang thig le dang 'od sna tshogs par snang
NK109(dze)002:3069: ba dang / 'gro drug 'khrul pa'i snang ba yul
NK109(dze)002:3070: gcig la tha dad par mthong ba ni chu la
NK109(dze)002:3071: rigs drug so so mthong lugs la sogs pa phung
NK109(dze)002:3072: po bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang bcas te thabs
NK109(dze)002:3073: ni dmigs rten la bslab pa'i rim pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3074: dmigs rten yin pa de la bslab pa'i rim pas
NK109(dze)002:3075: rig pa'i ye shes rang gis nyams la stobs skyed
NK109(dze)002:3076: ba med pas / shes rab rnam par dag pa nyams su myong ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:3077: de nyid la rdo rje 'chang bka' 'di chos kyi skus bsdus pa'i don du bka' rtsal ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:3078: dper na 'o ma las mar bsdus pa ltar brgyad
NK109(dze)002:3079: khri bzhi stong nang gi rig par bsdus nas dbang
NK109(dze)002:3081: longs skus gnyen po'i don du bka' rtsal te /
NK109(dze)002:3082: dper na tsha ba'i nad la ga bur gyis gnyen por 'gyur la /
NK109(dze)002:3083: grang ba can gyi dug tu 'gyur ba dang 'dra bar /
NK109(dze)002:3084: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po tshig du bstan pas /
NK109(dze)002:3085: gal te grang ba can dang mtshungs pas na /
NK109(dze)002:3086: tshig dang yi ge dang brjod pa las 'das pa'i don shes par bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:3087: tsha ba'i nad kyi gnyen por 'gyur ba bzhin du
NK109(dze)002:3088: nyon mongs pa brgyad khri bzhi stong gi gnyen por
NK109(dze)002:3089: chos kyi sgo yang de tsam gcig bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3090: blo rim dang sbyar nas sprul pa'i sku'i dbye ba
NK109(dze)002:3091: la dgongs te bka' rtsal ba ni dper na skas
NK109(dze)002:3092: kyi rim pa ltar theg pa rim pa dgu so
NK109(dze)002:3093: so'i blo'i rim pa dang sbyar nas gong 'og rim
NK109(dze)002:3094: par phye nas bka' rtsal pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3095: mi mnyam pa ni rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po
NK109(dze)002:3096: la lta ba gang dang yang mi mnyam pa ste
NK109(dze)002:3097: / chos nyid ma bcos pa nyid bskyed pas mkha'/
NK109(dze)002:3098: dbyings sku dang ye shes 'byung bas klong ngo rang
NK109(dze)002:3099: la dri ma rnams dag pas rab du dbang pos
NK109(dze)002:3100: mnyam pa nyams su myong ba'o /
NK109(dze)002:3101: kye zhes rang la bos pa'i tshul du snang ba 'di ni gong gi snang ba rnams te /
NK109(dze)002:3102: mtshon pa ye shes kyi tshul la yi ge med
NK109(dze)002:3103: pas brdas brtags pa'i ming gis rang bzhin rdzogs pa
NK109(dze)002:3104: chen po'i don la reg par mi nus pas /
NK109(dze)002:3105: ma h+aa yo gas skyed pa'i yi ge rnams a ti'i don las gol ba yin /
NK109(dze)002:3106: de yang rig pa'i ye shes de tshig gis gtan
NK109(dze)002:3107: la mi phebs pa ni tshig bdag nyid kyis bdag
NK109(dze)002:3108: nyid rtogs na gang zag gi rgyud la phan brtags
NK109(dze)002:3110: tshig de shes pa tsam gyis chog na nus pa
NK109(dze)002:3111: brda 'phrad pa tsam la tshig de bslabs te des
NK109(dze)002:3112: shes pas de yang grol bar 'gyur bas 'bad rtsol
NK109(dze)002:3113: mi dgos par grol bar rigs dper na sa bon
NK109(dze)002:3114: ma btabs pa la'ang 'bras bu 'byung dgos /
NK109(dze)002:3115: tshig de bcangs pas grol na byol song la sogs pa'i mgul du btags kyang grol bar 'gyur /
NK109(dze)002:3116: de ma yin par tshig gis don rtogs nas grol na /
NK109(dze)002:3117: don de ji ltar rtogs te yid dpyod las med pas na /
NK109(dze)002:3118: rang gi rgyud la nyams su myong ba med pas na /
NK109(dze)002:3119: dper na mig nad can la dung ser por mthong
NK109(dze)002:3120: ste de la dkar po'i yon tan du ma tshig
NK109(dze)002:3121: du brjod kyang / ser po'i zhen pa ldog du mi btub pa dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)002:3122: de'i ser po'i zhen pa ldog pa la ni sman
NK109(dze)002:3123: pa mkhas pas mig nad can de dmig thur gyis
NK109(dze)002:3124: phebs // dkar por bshad mi dgos pas ser po'i zhen pa rang log pa dang 'dra bar /
NK109(dze)002:3125: bla ma'i man ngag gis nyams su myong brgyud la
NK109(dze)002:3126: skyes pas tshig la brten mi dgos par grol ba
NK109(dze)002:3127: yin no // 'o na tshig de bshad pas grol ba yin na ni /
NK109(dze)002:3128: dper na tsha ba'i ro ma myong bar tsha ba gtan la 'bebs pa dang 'dra bar /
NK109(dze)002:3129: tshig gis thog tu mi phebs so //
NK109(dze)002:3130: gal te nyams su myong rgyu med na tha mal pa dang khyad par ci yang med do //
NK109(dze)002:3131: de'i phyir na tshig la dpyod na rdzogs pa'i don las gol ces pas na /
NK109(dze)002:3132: tshig gis b+hu mi d+ha bas rig pa tshig thams cad las ye nas 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3133: de ltar tshig med pa'i phyir da so so'i 'dug
NK109(dze)002:3134: tshul de nyid brjod pa gang gis kyang gtan la
NK109(dze)002:3135: mi phebs pas na brjod pa thams cad las ngang
NK109(dze)002:3136: gis 'das so // de ltar brjod du med pa'i
NK109(dze)002:3137: a ti'i gnas lugs de la rim pa dgu yi
NK109(dze)002:3138: grub pa'i matha'i blta ba'i lam gzhung rnams kyis kyang
NK109(dze)002:3140: sna tshogs pa'i skad mi 'dra ba'i mtshon ba ngang gis med pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3141: de'i phyir na dngos po'i 'dug tshul nyid la sgo
NK109(dze)002:3142: lnga'i yul tha dad par 'dzin pa med pas tshig
NK109(dze)002:3143: gis gtan la mi phebs te /
NK109(dze)002:3144: tshig gi rjes su 'brang ba'i rnal 'byor pa ni theg pa thun mong par gol bar bstan la /
NK109(dze)002:3145: 'di ltar rang gi rig pa dngos po /
NK109(dze)002:3146: 'dug tshul la sems med pas skyes pa'i rim pa
NK109(dze)002:3147: yul tha dad du slong ba'i spro bsdu mi dgos
NK109(dze)002:3148: / de'i sku skyed pa'i yi ge spro bsdu mang
NK109(dze)002:3149: po mi dgos pas yi ge med pa'i gtan tshigs
NK109(dze)002:3150: dang so so 'dug tshul la yi ge yod pa'am
NK109(dze)002:3154: yi ge bas ye shes tsam du yang don la grub pa med pa'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)002:3155: rgyud lung gi tshig las 'das par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3156: rgyud kyi tshig 'di dag shes bya tsam du byas te /
NK109(dze)002:3157: rang gi mtshon pa'i ye shes mngon sum du bstan ba'i bag tsam yang med de /
NK109(dze)002:3158: la la gnas skabs yul la dgongs nas gsung /
NK109(dze)002:3159: la la ma 'ong pa'i sems can 'jug pa'i phyir gsung /
NK109(dze)002:3160: la la drang don 'dren par gsung /
NK109(dze)002:3161: la la gzhi'i yon tan brjod /
NK109(dze)002:3168: de dag gi grangs dang che ba brjod pa'i tshig phal cher yin pa las /
NK109(dze)002:3169: mngon gsum rang gnad la dbab par bstan pa nyung pas rgyud med pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3170: 'di nyid gtan tshigs kyis mi phebs pas /
NK109(dze)002:3172: mngon gsum rang gnad la dbab pa'i man ngag ni
NK109(dze)002:3173: med bcos ma rtogs pa 'jug pa'i man ngag gis
NK109(dze)002:3174: b+hu mi d+ha bas na man ngag thams cad kyang
NK109(dze)002:3175: med pa'o // de ci'i phyir na tshig la brten pas na /
NK109(dze)002:3176: rig pa nyid tshig thams cad bral ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:3177: des na tshig 'dzin cing brjod pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3178: thos pa dang bral rnams gol bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3179: sems sde las mchog tu gsang ba'i chos nyid ni /
NK109(dze)002:3180: rna dbang gzhan las thos mi 'gyur /
NK109(dze)002:3181: de bzhin lce'i dbang pos kyang /
NK109(dze)002:3182: 'di la brjod du rdul tsam med ces pas na brjod pa thams cad kyis stong pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3183: de yang rang gi rig pa'i ye shes nyid /
NK109(dze)002:3184: shes rab kyi spyod yul ma yin pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3185: de nyid tshig gis gtan la mi phebs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3186: 'di la sdig pas gos pa med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3187: da ge bas zab du med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3188: dbang po la rno rtul med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3189: sku gsum ye shes lnga 'bras bu ma yin te lam yin pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3190: 'khrul pa lam ye shes kyi grogs su 'gyur ba
NK109(dze)002:3191: dang bdun gyis theg pa thun mong ba las khyad
NK109(dze)002:3193: don gnyis pa rig pa nyid yi ges gtan la
NK109(dze)002:3194: mi phebs par bstan pa la gsum gyis bstan pa'i
NK109(dze)002:3195: dang po / yi ge 'bru gsum gyis 'khrul pa spangs pa bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3197: zhes snang ba'i bdag po la ngo mtshar dang bcas pa'i tshig gis bos nas /
NK109(dze)002:3198: rig pa'i ye shes la chos med pas rang snang ba yang chos las grol te /
NK109(dze)002:3199: tshig med pa'i phyir chos su snang ba ka dag ste med pas /
NK109(dze)002:3200: ngad so so gshis kyi 'dug tshul ma bltas btags
NK109(dze)002:3201: pa'i yi ge yod pa ma yin pas tshig med
NK109(dze)002:3202: de / tshig ni yi ge la brten pa'i phyir ro //
NK109(dze)002:3203: rig pa dngos po'i 'dug tshul ye nas gnas pa'i
NK109(dze)002:3204: nga nyid la skye ba nyid med pas zhes pa
NK109(dze)002:3205: ste / skye med mtshon pa'i yi ge a yin
NK109(dze)002:3206: te glo bur du skye med gtan la dbab mi
NK109(dze)002:3207: dgos pas yi ge a ni ye nas skye med
NK109(dze)002:3209: de yang rang rig pa'i ye shes dang so so'i
NK109(dze)002:3210: gnas lugs la ye nas 'gags med rang shar bas
NK109(dze)002:3211: / da dgag pa'i gnas grub pa med pas /
NK109(dze)002:3212: 'gag med mtshon pa'i yi ge yin pas na ye
NK109(dze)002:3213: nas 'gag med du snang bas de nyid mtshon mi
NK109(dze)002:3214: dgos pas sku gsum du bzhugs pas na ngang gis
NK109(dze)002:3215: med pa'o // nga rig pa dngos po'i 'dug tshul
NK109(dze)002:3216: rang bzhin ma bcos pa thugs kyi dgongs pa de
NK109(dze)002:3217: ye nas 'du 'bral gnyis med par gnas pas /
NK109(dze)002:3218: de mtshon pa'i yi ge h'u yin te /
NK109(dze)002:3219: h'u gis mtshon mi dgos pas ye nas zad pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3220: de'i phyir na 'gags pa med pa'i thugs rje rang
NK109(dze)002:3221: shar bas gdul bya so so'i sems can la 'dul
NK109(dze)002:3222: byed kyi sku'i snang ba so sor sna tshogs par
NK109(dze)002:3224: ming 'di zhes bya ba 'dug tshul la ma grub
NK109(dze)002:3225: pas yi ges btags pa'i ming rnams ngo bo la
NK109(dze)002:3227: de yang gsang sngags phyi nang gnyis yi ge la
NK109(dze)002:3228: brten cing de nyid kyi mtshan nyid rab tu gsal
NK109(dze)002:3230: a ti'i rnal 'byor bas yi ge la brten na gsang sngags phyi nang du gol ba yin pas /
NK109(dze)002:3231: a ti la yi ge'i dngos po ye nyid nas ga la srid de yod pa ma yin no //
NK109(dze)002:3232: rdzogs pa chen po sangs rgyas nyag gcig du ma
NK109(dze)002:3233: las 'das shing spros pa gang gis kyang ma spros
NK109(dze)002:3234: pas / rang gi 'dug tshul thig le nyag gcig tu rab tu gnas pas /
NK109(dze)002:3235: phyir snang ba'i dus na yang rig pa rdo rje
NK109(dze)002:3236: lu gu rgyud du nyag gcig du snang ba yin
NK109(dze)002:3237: no // de'i phyir na mtshan ma blos btags pa'i
NK109(dze)002:3238: yi ges lha yi sku kha dog dkar dmar du
NK109(dze)002:3240: ye nas rang bzhin gyi 'od kha dog lnga ye
NK109(dze)002:3241: nas blos btags shing bsgyur mi dgos par yod pa'i
NK109(dze)002:3242: don ma shes pas a ti las gol ba ni
NK109(dze)002:3243: / a ti la mtshan ma'i yi ge gang yang med do //
NK109(dze)002:3244: rig pa nyid la lhan cig byed pa'i rgyu med
NK109(dze)002:3245: do ye nas rgyus ma skyed par rang snang bas
NK109(dze)002:3246: / de la da skyed mi dgos te ye nas
NK109(dze)002:3247: rang rdzogs su yod pas skyed pa'i sa bon kyi
NK109(dze)002:3248: yi ge ga la yod de /
NK109(dze)002:3249: de ltar ma shes pas ma h+aa man chad kyi sngags kyi phyi nang rnams gol ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:3250: rig pa nyid la ye shes dang sku lnga rang chas su rdzogs pas ye nas bzhugs pas /
NK109(dze)002:3251: sngags phyi nang gi yi ge la brten ba'i rdzogs
NK109(dze)002:3252: pa'i rim pa yi ge a la sogs pa la
NK109(dze)002:3253: rten pa ni gol bas a ti la yang yod
NK109(dze)002:3255: rang gi rig pa thig le nyag cig kun pas ye nas gnas pa yin te /
NK109(dze)002:3256: sngags phyi nang gi yi ge mang po spros nas
NK109(dze)002:3257: 'phags pa mchod pa dang sems can gyi don byed
NK109(dze)002:3258: pa la sogs pa spros pa'i yi ge ni a
NK109(dze)002:3259: ti gnas lugs la ming yang med do //
NK109(dze)002:3260: rig pa la nga so so'i 'dug tshul la 'di
NK109(dze)002:3261: ltar snang ba yod thos snang grags thams cad ye
NK109(dze)002:3262: nas ma 'dres la yongs su rdzogs par gnas la
NK109(dze)002:3263: / sngags phyi nang gi bsdus pas yi ge bsdus
NK109(dze)002:3264: pa rnams gol pa yin pas a ti'i gnas lugs
NK109(dze)002:3266: rig pa'i sku la dngos po mtshan ma rang snang gi sku dang /
NK109(dze)002:3267: grags pa zhen 'dzin gyi gsung dang /
NK109(dze)002:3268: rtog pa 'dus pa'i thugs kyi dngos po med pas /
NK109(dze)002:3270: gsung gi yi ge a dang thugs kyi h'u gsum med pa ma yin te /
NK109(dze)002:3271: dngos po'i mtha' thams cad bcad par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3276: mthing kha lngas brgyan pa'i rig pa la sngags phyi
NK109(dze)002:3277: nang gi yi ge spros pa'i kha dog nyid du
NK109(dze)002:3278: ye nas med pas na yi ge spro bsdus kha
NK109(dze)002:3279: dog yod pa rnams a ti'i gnas lugs la gol
NK109(dze)002:3280: lo // a ti'i gnas lugs la kha dog yod pa min no //
NK109(dze)002:3281: zlum pa thig le'i cha dang 'khril ba rlung gi
NK109(dze)002:3282: cha dang lu gu rgyud 'brel ba'i cha dang gsum
NK109(dze)002:3283: de nyid ye nas gnas pa'i 'dug tshul la /
NK109(dze)002:3284: gru bzhi la sogs pa'i dbyibs su snang bar med pa'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)002:3285: yi ges mtshon pa'i zhi rgyas dbang drag gi dbyibs su 'dod pa'i sngags rnams gol bas /
NK109(dze)002:3286: a ti gnas lugs la 'dod pa med do //
NK109(dze)002:3287: rig pa dngos ni lu gu rgyud dbang po'i yul du bstan du yod la /
NK109(dze)002:3288: de rdzas su grub pa med pas dngos po med pas /
NK109(dze)002:3289: nyan thos kyi chos kyi bdag dang gang zag gi
NK109(dze)002:3290: bdag tu 'dod pa chos nyid mnyam pa'i don las
NK109(dze)002:3291: gol ba dang / mu stegs kyi bdag chos nyid phyogs la logs pa'i don gyis gol bas na /
NK109(dze)002:3292: a ti gnas lugs la bdag ni chos kyi 'khor
NK109(dze)002:3293: los kyi phyogs gcig tsam la yang 'dod pa ma
NK109(dze)002:3294: yin no // rig pa'i sku zhes lus la brten pa'i dus na ste /
NK109(dze)002:3295: 'di la yul dang shes pa gnyis su med pa'i phyir na /
NK109(dze)002:3296: sems tsam pa'i rnam pa dang shes par 'dod pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3297: gzung ba'i yul dang zhen pa'i shes par gol ba na /
NK109(dze)002:3298: a ti gnas lugs la yi ge bzung ba'i yul dang /
NK109(dze)002:3300: rig pa gcig dang gnyis zhes ye nas med pas
NK109(dze)002:3301: dbu ma ba'i gcig du bral la sogs pa'i gtan
NK109(dze)002:3302: tshigs kyis bsgrub dgos pas de ltar bsgrub pa'i dbu
NK109(dze)002:3303: ma pa'i chos nyid brjod du med pa las gol
NK109(dze)002:3304: bas dang / a ti gnas lugs la tha snyad med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3305: sa dang lam gcig gnas gnyis su 'dren pa'i pha
NK109(dze)002:3306: rol du phyin pas thig le nyag gcig tu ma
NK109(dze)002:3308: a ti'i gnas lugs yi ge'i sa bcu dang lam lnga dang rig pa nyid la mi 'dod pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3309: rig pa nyid kyi snang ba la thams cad rdzogs pa de nyid rang yin pas rdzogs la /
NK109(dze)002:3310: byang sems kyi rgyu bsod nams kyi tshogs gnyis su 'dod pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3311: a ti'i rtsol sgrub dang bral ba'i don ma rtogs gol te /
NK109(dze)002:3312: a ti gnas lugs la yi ges brtags ba'i rgyu
NK109(dze)002:3313: bsod nams dang 'bras bu ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis
NK109(dze)002:3314: su nga rig pa rang byung nyid la mi 'dod
NK109(dze)002:3315: do // rang gi rig pa nyid la yi ges
NK109(dze)002:3316: bstan pa'i dpes mtshon du ye nas dngos po med
NK109(dze)002:3317: do // pas / gsang skor la sogs pa'i dpe'i ngo sprod la sogs pa 'dod pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3318: rig pa mngon gsum gyis don la mthong bas gol
NK109(dze)002:3319: bas yi ges brtags pa'i dpes nga rig pa nyid
NK109(dze)002:3320: mi mthong ngo // rig pa nyid kyi ye nas dri ma med par zang thal bar bzhugs pas /
NK109(dze)002:3321: byang sems kyi shes bya'i sgrib pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3322: nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa gnyis kyi don ma sgrib
NK109(dze)002:3323: pa'i 'dod pas 'di gnyis sel bar 'dod pas ye
NK109(dze)002:3324: shes zang thal dri med rang dag tu ma rtogs
NK109(dze)002:3325: pas gol te / a ti gnas lugs la yi
NK109(dze)002:3326: ges btags pa'i dri ma gnyis kyis nga rig pa
NK109(dze)002:3327: la ye nas ma sgrib par zang thal du rdzogs
NK109(dze)002:3328: pas gol te / pa'o // rang rig pa nyid
NK109(dze)002:3329: ye nas dge bcu dang sdig pa bcu med pas
NK109(dze)002:3330: pas gol te / pa'o // / theg pa thun
NK109(dze)002:3331: mong pa rnams kyi yi ges btags pa'i dge ba
NK109(dze)002:3332: bcus thar ba thob par 'dod la sdig pa bcus
NK109(dze)002:3333: thar pa'i gegs su 'dod pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3334: dngos po 'dug tshul ma rtogs pas gol pas na /
NK109(dze)002:3335: a ti gnas lugs la bcu phrag gnyis las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3336: rdzogs pa chen po tshig las gol bas rgyu bstan pa la gnyis kyi bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)002:3337: yi ge rgyun thad kyi gdams ngag dran par bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3338: e ma ho zhes rang las ngo mtshar skyes nas /
NK109(dze)002:3339: de ltar yi ge med pa'i chos nyid dag pa tshig las 'das pa la /
NK109(dze)002:3340: yi ge'i rgyu the tshom yin la rtsal snang ba
NK109(dze)002:3341: dang tshig tu brjod pa gnyis su yi ges brtags
NK109(dze)002:3342: pas yod pa ma yin te /
NK109(dze)002:3343: yi ge'i rgyu the tshom dang lta ba sna tshogs pa rab tu ston pas /
NK109(dze)002:3344: yi ge nyid la dngos po gshis kyi don gang
NK109(dze)002:3345: yang med pas yi ges brtags pa rnams brda tsam
NK109(dze)002:3346: mi tshig tsam yin pas don la med par bstan
NK109(dze)002:3347: pa'o // nga ni rig pa'i ye shes yi ges
NK109(dze)002:3348: brtags pa'i chos la ye nas ma bstan pas rang
NK109(dze)002:3349: 'byung du kun la khyab cing kun la rang shar
NK109(dze)002:3350: pa'o // bas / yi ges brtags cing tha snyad
NK109(dze)002:3351: mang po don yin zer yang mgo 'khor zhing nga
NK109(dze)002:3352: rig pa'i sku la mngon gsum du snang bas ma
NK109(dze)002:3353: 'thad ba'i tshig gis slar sgrol bas mi mthong ba'o
NK109(dze)002:3354: pa'o // bas / // thog ma'i gzhi sus kyang
NK109(dze)002:3355: ma bcos shing ma bslad pa'i ka dag tshig gi
NK109(dze)002:3356: sgro skur dang bral ba'i rang 'byung ba'i ye shes
NK109(dze)002:3357: de nyid la yi ge'i rgyu the tshom dang lta
NK109(dze)002:3358: pa'o // bas / // ba med la / yi
NK109(dze)002:3359: ge'i rkyen theg pa sna tshogs pa gnyis rang gi
NK109(dze)002:3360: zhe 'dod gnyis la ma ltos par rang byung bas
NK109(dze)002:3362: yi ge brtags pa'i lhan gcig byed pa'i rgyu dang
NK109(dze)002:3364: / nye bar len pa'i rkyen gnyis rig pa nyid
NK109(dze)002:3366: / mi 'dod do // rig pa nyid la bsam
NK109(dze)002:3367: pa med pa'i chos kyi sku bsam pa med pa
NK109(dze)002:3369: / mi 'dod do // dang / de nyid la
NK109(dze)002:3370: tshig med yi ge med pa'i longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK109(dze)002:3371: sku brjod pa med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3372: de nyid la yi ges brtags pa'i yul tha dad
NK109(dze)002:3373: pa med pa'i sprul pa'i sku zhen pa med pa
NK109(dze)002:3374: gsum rig pa rang la rdzogs pas /
NK109(dze)002:3375: yi ges brtags pa'i sku gsum dang ye shes lnga
NK109(dze)002:3376: la sogs pa'i tshogs la nga rig pa nyid ltos
NK109(dze)002:3377: pa mi cha'o // dngos po 'dug tshul la ye
NK109(dze)002:3378: ge med pa'i gnad kyi rgyun du grub pa med
NK109(dze)002:3379: pa mi cha'o // pa dang / lung dang man
NK109(dze)002:3380: ngag du grub pa med pa'i de gsum yang yi
NK109(dze)002:3381: ge'i tshogs la brten pas na /
NK109(dze)002:3382: rgyud dang lung gi tshogs mang por la dran par
NK109(dze)002:3383: gtad pa'i 'ben mi rnyed pas rig pa'i ye shes
NK109(dze)002:3384: la bsgrib pa'o // ston pa rgyun zad gyi man ngag bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3385: thog ma ye ji bzhin pa'i sangs rgyas 'gro ba
NK109(dze)002:3386: rnams kyi mgon por byung ba ma rig pa'i dri
NK109(dze)002:3387: ma med pa nyid rgyu bdag nyid gcig pa'i ma
NK109(dze)002:3390: kun tu brtags pa gsum gyi 'gran pa'i zla med
NK109(dze)002:3391: par ye nas rang sangs ye rdzogs chen por rgyas
NK109(dze)002:3392: pas / 'di'i dus na yi ge la ma brten /
NK109(dze)002:3393: yi ge yis don la ma brten par sangs rgyas pas //
NK109(dze)002:3394: da lta yi ge'i don stong nyid du mtshon pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3396: spros pa med pa dang gnyis med du brtags pa'i
NK109(dze)002:3397: don rnams la nga rig pa nyid mi gnas so
NK109(dze)002:3398: // gzhan las log pa'i rang las byung ba'i rig pa'i rgyal po gzhan zil gyis gnon pa nyid /
NK109(dze)002:3399: yi ges sgros btags pa'i tshig so so'i 'dod pa du ma la don du 'dzin pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:3401: tshig zab mos nyams kyi gong chod nas nyams su
NK109(dze)002:3402: myong ba skye bar byed pa la tshig dang yi
NK109(dze)002:3404: dper na ga bur gyis grang ba can la btang na dug du 'gyur ba dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)002:3405: de yang tshig mang po shes pa'i gtad yal ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:3406: dper na btsan dug ngo ma shes pa'i skyes bus sngags med par zos pa dang 'dra ste /
NK109(dze)002:3407: phyin ci log du gol ba'i 'gyur ba yin no /
NK109(dze)002:3408: dang po byung ba chos nyid ka dag chen po la /
NK109(dze)002:3409: tshig med pa'i phyir tshig la brten nas byang ba chos sku dang chu ba pa longs sku dang /
NK109(dze)002:3410: sems dpa' sprul pa'i sku mi rnyed pas /
NK109(dze)002:3411: tshig kyang yi ge las byung bas na yi ge'i
NK109(dze)002:3412: mtshan nyid du 'dod pa nga rig pa nyid la
NK109(dze)002:3414: bar du 'gro ba lhun grub yon tan gyi 'char
NK109(dze)002:3415: tshul re dgos par 'gyur ba med pa'i lam yin
NK109(dze)002:3416: pas / yi ges brtags pa'i spong len yang dag pa med pas /
NK109(dze)002:3417: a ti'i gnas lugs la spong len du grub pa med do //
NK109(dze)002:3418: rig pa thig le nyag gcig spros pa'i mtha' brgyad
NK109(dze)002:3419: dang bral ba la snang ba'i grangs 'di ltar bcad
NK109(dze)002:3421: ka kha ga g+ha nga la sogs pa'i a li
NK109(dze)002:3422: dang ka li bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su grub pa
NK109(dze)002:3423: med de a ti don dam pa'i gnas lugs nyid
NK109(dze)002:3424: la yod pa ma yin no //
NK109(dze)002:3425: rig pa'i ye shes kyi snang ba mthong bar bstan
NK109(dze)002:3426: pa la gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang po rig pa
NK109(dze)002:3427: ngos 'dzin gyi gdams ngag bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3428: rnam par snang mdzad la sogs pa'i 'od lnga rang
NK109(dze)002:3429: byung bas dkyil rang gi rig pa dang 'khor sku
NK109(dze)002:3430: dang ye shes su snang nas /
NK109(dze)002:3431: brtags pa'i tha snyad dang bcas pa'i yi ge gcig kyang chos nyid bar do la med kyang /
NK109(dze)002:3432: nga chos nyid bcos pa med pa'i snang ba rang dag pa la //
NK109(dze)002:3433: gsal 'gyur tshig dang bcas pa'i yi ge'i ngang ngam shugs kyi med pas /
NK109(dze)002:3434: a ti'i gnas lugs la tha snyad dang bral ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:3435: theg pa thun mong ba la rang bzhin gyis gsang
NK109(dze)002:3436: ba'i rig pa sku dang ye shes kyi byung khungs
NK109(dze)002:3437: lhun stug pa'i bdag nyid la 'khor 'das ma spangs
NK109(dze)002:3438: par rdzogs pa la yi ge ming du brtags pa'i
NK109(dze)002:3439: tshig gcig kyang med pa'i phyir /
NK109(dze)002:3440: a ti brjod pa gang gis kyang thog tu mi phebs pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3441: a ti ngos 'dzin gyis gdams ngag bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3442: gsang ba ni thun mong du gsang ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3443: khyad par du nyan thos la gsang dang /
NK109(dze)002:3444: mchog tu a ti gzhan phyogs la gsang ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:3445: de yi don rang la sngags te rig pa'i ye shes mngon sum du bskul bar byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3446: a skye ba med pa la ti 'gyur ba med pa'i snang ba la /
NK109(dze)002:3447: mtshan ma sgros brtags pa'i yi ge med pa'i a
NK109(dze)002:3448: ti gnas lugs la ming dang ming can du 'dzin
NK109(dze)002:3449: pa'i shes pa'i yi ge yod pa ma yin no
NK109(dze)002:3450: // a ti yo ga rang la rdzogs pa de
NK109(dze)002:3451: nyid ye nas byas shing bcas pa ma yin par
NK109(dze)002:3452: // rdzogs pas / 'khrul pa'i brdas brtags pa'i yi ge med pas rang snang du rdzogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3453: rang rig tu gsal ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3454: rang byung du byung ba dang //
NK109(dze)002:3455: rang shar du khyab pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3456: rang dag tu gnas pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3457: rang grol du yangs pa'i phyir na a ti yo ga phyogs gang du yang lhung ba med par /
NK109(dze)002:3458: rgya gar yang chad pa med do //
NK109(dze)002:3459: zhes yi ges btags pa'i tshig dang brjod pa dang
NK109(dze)002:3460: du len theg pa thun mong pa rnams la yang
NK109(dze)002:3461: dag pa'i chos nyid med pas bla ma brgyud pa'i
NK109(dze)002:3462: man ngag dang bral pa'i rang gi gsang ba chen
NK109(dze)002:3465: gzhi rdzogs pa chen po thams cad kyi ngo bor rdzogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3466: lam rdzogs pa chen po sku dang ye shes su rang rdzogs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3467: 'bras bu rdzogs pa chen po 'khor 'das gnyis rang grol du rdzogs pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3468: chen po ni 'di nyid thabs sla bas chen po
NK109(dze)002:3469: yin te tshig gsum du bsdus nas bstan du yod
NK109(dze)002:3470: pa dang // thabs myur ste lus ma bor bar zag bcas rang zad la bud+d+h+aa ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3471: thabs mang pas chen po yin te /
NK109(dze)002:3472: snang ba gang la gtad pa thams cad dngos po
NK109(dze)002:3473: gnas lugs kyi nyams su myong ba 'char ba dang
NK109(dze)002:3474: // thabs che ba yin te 'di las man ngag thabs che ba gzhan med pas na chen po'o //
NK109(dze)002:3475: tshig las gol bar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3476: nyan thos rnams tshig la nyan pa dang thos pa
NK109(dze)002:3477: rjes su 'dzin pas chos nyid brjod du med pa
NK109(dze)002:3479: rang rgyal rten 'brel lugs 'byung dang lugs ldog tshig la brten cing bsgoms pas /
NK109(dze)002:3480: rang snang bcos pa med pa'i dgongs pa las gol ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3481: sems tsam tshig la brten pa'i sems nyid don dam
NK109(dze)002:3482: du 'dod pas rig pa bsam pa las 'das pa
NK109(dze)002:3484: dbu ma ba don dam kun rdzob tshig gis phye nas /
NK109(dze)002:3485: rang bzhin med pa don dam du 'dod pa rig pa mngon gsum gyi lam las gol ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3486: pha rol du phyin pa spyi'i tshig la brten pas
NK109(dze)002:3487: sa lam don dam du 'dod pas rtogs ba cig
NK109(dze)002:3489: kri ya ba rang gi yi dam gyi lha tshogs
NK109(dze)002:3490: kyi sngags dang phyag rgya don dam du 'dod pas
NK109(dze)002:3491: rang byung ye shes las gol ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3492: yo ga ba tshig la brten pa'i byang chub lnga dang /
NK109(dze)002:3493: bskyed pa'i lha gcig dang tha mi dad du 'dod pas /
NK109(dze)002:3494: rang snang cer grol las gol /
NK109(dze)002:3495: ma h+aa yo ga brten pa lha dang rten gzhal yas khang tshig la brten nas /
NK109(dze)002:3496: yang dag pa'i kun rdzob la phyi snod gzhal yas khang du 'dod pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3497: nang bcud brten pa lha dang lha mo'i dkyil 'khor du 'dod pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3498: tshogs drug lhug ba snang ba rang grol kyi dgongs pa las gol ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3499: a nu ba tshig la brten pa'i dbyings dang ye shes don dam 'a dod pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3500: a ti 'bras bu thig le nyag gcig lam du
NK109(dze)002:3501: byas te ma spangs yongs su rdzogs pa'i don las
NK109(dze)002:3502: gol ba dang / gzhan yang a tir khas blangs tshig gi 'jal byed du 'dod pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3503: lta ba gzhi la lus nas gol ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3504: sgom yon tan gyi 'char tshul la lus nas gol ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3505: nyams myong yig thog du lus nas gol ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3506: spyod pa gnas lugs la lus nas gol ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3507: thams cad sems yin du lus nas gol ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3508: snang ba rtsal dang rol pa nyid don dam par 'dod pas gol ba rnams te /
NK109(dze)002:3509: 'di dag kyang nyams su myong ba med pas yid
NK109(dze)002:3510: spyod kyi lta sgom 'dzin pas gol ba yin no
NK109(dze)002:3511: // 'di ltar tshig gi 'di 'dod pa rnams dang bral bas spro bsdu med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3512: rig pa nyid shes rab kyis spyod yul ma yin
NK109(dze)002:3513: par dbang po'i mngon gsum du gtan la phabs pa
NK109(dze)002:3515: gnad rnam pa gsum gyis skye ba med pa'i chos nyid dang lhan gcig tu gnas pas /
NK109(dze)002:3516: thos bsam sgom gsum bya mi dgos bas dbang po la rno rtul med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3517: nyams myong nyid rang snang la phebs pas the tshom gyi mtha' chod pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3518: tshogs dang sdig pa'i las kyi phan gnod dang bral
NK109(dze)002:3519: bar da lta nyams myong la sbyar du yod pas
NK109(dze)002:3520: las dge sdig las 'das pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3521: 'di ltar snang ba rang thog tu grol bas gnyen
NK109(dze)002:3522: po gzhan la re ba che ba med pa dang
NK109(dze)002:3523: / brjod du med pa'i don rang gi ngag la brten nas nyams su myong du yod pas /
NK109(dze)002:3524: tshig dang brjod pa la 'das pa rnams kyis a
NK109(dze)002:3525: ti yo ga phyin ci ma log pa rnams gol
NK109(dze)002:3527: gol sa gang gi yang phyogs su ma lhung pas
NK109(dze)002:3528: gzhan tshig dang yi ges brtags pa rnams yang dag
NK109(dze)002:3529: du 'dod pa de rnams gol bar bstan pa ni
NK109(dze)002:3531: le'u ni gzhung gi don nges par gcod pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3532: lnga pa bzhi'i 'og du byung bas na grangs kyi bye brag go /
NK109(dze)002:3533: da ni le'u drug pa'i don pad+ma kha phye ba ltar bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3534: le'u drug pa rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po nyid zhal chems du bstan pa'i le'u la //
NK109(dze)002:3535: spyi don gnyis kyis bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)002:3536: zhal chems kyi ngo bo bstan pa la /
NK109(dze)002:3537: nang gses kyi don dgus bstan pa'i dang po /
NK109(dze)002:3538: de dag gi 'byung ba'i yan lag bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3540: le'u lnga bstan pa'i de nas yang snang ba chen
NK109(dze)002:3541: po ni yang dag don kyi snang ba rang bzhin
NK109(dze)002:3542: gnas lugs bkod pa chen po ste /
NK109(dze)002:3543: mun pa'i phyogs dang bral bas gsal ba'i snang ba
NK109(dze)002:3544: de gang la snang na 'gro drug 'khrul pa'i yul
NK109(dze)002:3546: chos nyid ni rang bzhin gnas lugs kyi chos nyid 'khrul ba rang dag pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3547: ma bcos rang bzhag gi chos nyid lus ngag rnal du 'bebs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3548: rang snang lhug pa gzhan ma yin pa'i chos nyid de /
NK109(dze)002:3549: 'khrul pa rang dag ma nor ba'i chos nyid dang /
NK109(dze)002:3550: thig le spros bral rang gi ngo bo'i chos nyid dang lnga las /
NK109(dze)002:3551: rang rig bcos pa med pa'i bdag nyid 'du 'bral
NK109(dze)002:3552: med par rtogs pa'i rtogs pa rdo rjee lu gu
NK109(dze)002:3553: rgyud dang ston pa'i thugs chos nyid lnga 'du 'bral
NK109(dze)002:3554: med pa'i ngang las rig pa bzhengs pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:3555: zhes ni shes rab tha dad par rang shar ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:3556: de'i tshe snang ba thams cad kun tu bzang mo'i
NK109(dze)002:3557: rang bzhin du ye nas rgyan dang rol par shar
NK109(dze)002:3558: bas bka' phyin ci ma log par rang rig pa'i
NK109(dze)002:3560: kye kye don nyid rang rdzogs pa'i tshul du bos nas brda' dang zhes pa ni rang bzhin kyi brda'/
NK109(dze)002:3561: 'di ltar snang ba thams cad du shar ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3562: byas pa'i brdas 'khor ba'i chos nyid mi rtag pa'i don du shar ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3563: mi snang ba'i brdas sems kyi byung tshor sna tshogs par shar ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3564: snang ba'i brdas brtags pa thams cad rang bzhin med par shar ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3565: lag gi 'du byed kyi brdas byas pa'i las la don med par shar ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3566: byas pa'i brdas la gsum yod pa las /
NK109(dze)002:3567: lus kyi brdas rang gi bde ba ngo shes par bya ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3568: ngag gi brdas brjod med kyi don rang gi rgyud la brten pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3569: yid kyis brdas 'di ltar brtags pa'i mi rnams 'gags par bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3570: yi ge ni brda' rtags ming gi yi ge a li dang k+aa li'i tshogs dang /
NK109(dze)002:3571: rang bzhin rtsa gnas kyi yi ge brjod pa'i sgra thams cad dang /
NK109(dze)002:3572: snying po 'gyur ba med pa'i yi ge rig pa'i ye shes dang /
NK109(dze)002:3573: yang dag don dam kyi yi ge chos nyid bkas dag pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3574: yon tan rdzogs tshul gyi yi ge lhun grub 'char byed dang bcas pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3575: bsgyur byed ming gi yi ge gang brtags pa de'i srog gnas par byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3576: rnam shes rang srog gi yi ges 'gro ba ris
NK109(dze)002:3577: drug so so'i srog gnas pa dang spel ba dang
NK109(dze)002:3578: / nyams pa dang 'phrog par byed pa dang bdun
NK109(dze)002:3579: gyi dbye ba la sogs pa rab tu spangs la
NK109(dze)002:3580: / / dbyings rig 'du 'bral med par nyams su blang /
NK109(dze)002:3581: tha snyad ni 'khrul pa rang bzhin gyi tha snyad brtags pa rnams dang //
NK109(dze)002:3582: de'i rten 'brel kyi tshogs 'dus pa rnams las mched pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3583: 'jal byed tshad ma'i tha snyad kyis yul rjes su 'gro ldog tu byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3584: sgra tshad rig pa'i tha snyad kyi gang la 'jug pa'i rgyu mtshan dang /
NK109(dze)002:3586: gzhal bya ma yin pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3587: gang gzhal bya yul gyi mtshan nyid gtan la 'bebs bar byed pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3588: grub matha'i blo'i tha snyad kyi rang don bsgrub pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3589: gzhan don 'gog par byed pa so so gshis kyi don nyams su len pas rab tu spangs te /
NK109(dze)002:3590: thams cad ni de dag ma lus par spangs pa /
NK109(dze)002:3591: rang gi sku'i snang ba gsum /
NK109(dze)002:3592: 'og nas ston pas de la ltos shig ces ston pas zhal chems kyi tshul du gdams pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3593: 'di ltar nyams su len pa'i skal ldan dad pa
NK109(dze)002:3594: can kyis phyi'i longs spyod rdzas dang yo byad spangs
NK109(dze)002:3595: la / grogs g.yog 'khor dang 'brel rnams dang bu
NK109(dze)002:3596: dang chung ma la sogs pa thams cad la ma
NK109(dze)002:3598: snying po'i don ston pa'i rang gi bla ma la 'khor gsum yongs su dag par dbul bar bya /
NK109(dze)002:3599: lhag ma rang 'tsho ba'i rdzas khyer la lus rkyen
NK109(dze)002:3600: spangs pa'i dgon pa nas nags mthug po yod pa'i
NK109(dze)002:3601: khrod dag du de'i dkyil na brag yod pa'am spangs
NK109(dze)002:3602: shangs su gang gi grogs med par rang gcig pur
NK109(dze)002:3603: gnas par bya'o // der bsdad nas dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma dang //
NK109(dze)002:3604: rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud dang gnyis dbang
NK109(dze)002:3605: po'i gtad sa nam ka dang gsum 'bral ba med
NK109(dze)002:3606: par gnas par gyis cig ces zhal chems su gdams
NK109(dze)002:3607: pa'o / de yang nyi tshe ba'i stong pa ther zug tu med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3608: rig med stong pa nam ka dang /
NK109(dze)002:3609: rnam par shes pa tsam du sems pa'i rnam shes mtha' yas kyi skye mched dang /
NK109(dze)002:3610: nam ka 'di nyid chos nyid rtogs par bsgom pa
NK109(dze)002:3611: nam ka mtha' yas kyi skye mched dang stong pa
NK109(dze)002:3612: yod pa yang ma yin med pa yang min pa'i
NK109(dze)002:3613: yod min med min kyi skye mched dang /
NK109(dze)002:3614: ci yang med pa'i stong pa cung zad med pa'i skye mched dang /
NK109(dze)002:3615: grangs mtha' zad pa'i stong ba mu med pa la
NK109(dze)002:3616: sogs pa'i phyogs 'dod pa med pa'i snang ba ni
NK109(dze)002:3617: / 'og nas snang ba gsum ston pas de nyid
NK109(dze)002:3618: sgrib byed rnams sel ba'i thabs gyi man ngag dang
NK109(dze)002:3619: bcas pas na de nyid ces bya la /
NK109(dze)002:3620: yang na dbyings kyi nang du rig pa bcug bas
NK109(dze)002:3621: byas pa med pa'i dbyings rig 'du 'bral med pa
NK109(dze)002:3622: ste / 'di rdzas su med pas rtag pa'i phyogs su ma lhung la /
NK109(dze)002:3623: gsal byed gzhan las ma ltos pas chad pa'i phyogs
NK109(dze)002:3624: su ma lhung la shes shing rig par gnas pas
NK109(dze)002:3625: rtag chad mthar 'dzin phyogs su ma lhung la /
NK109(dze)002:3626: rgyu 'bras gzhan la ma ltos pas mtshan nyid kyi
NK109(dze)002:3627: theg pa'i phyogs su ma lhung bsnyen sgrub 'bad rtsol
NK109(dze)002:3628: bya mi dgos bas sngags phyi nang gi phyogs su
NK109(dze)002:3629: ma lhung pa de nyid ltos shig /
NK109(dze)002:3630: ces sngon 'byung ma ston pa'i snang ba 'dis kyi 'khor la gdams pa /
NK109(dze)002:3631: rjes 'jug tu bla mas dad pa dang ldan pa'i 'khor skal ldan la gdams pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3632: gzhi'i mdungs sgyur gyi gdam ngag bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3633: grub pa'i mtha' rnams kyi shin tu bzung bar dka' ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:3634: chos nyid ka dag gi gzhi yin ste /
NK109(dze)002:3635: 'di nyid rgyu zhes tha snyad du grub pa med
NK109(dze)002:3636: pas bdag nyid gcig pa'i ma rig pa yod ma
NK109(dze)002:3637: myong / gcig dang gnyis kyi matha'i grangs dang bral bas /
NK109(dze)002:3638: lhan gcig skyes pa'i ma rig pa yod ma myong ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3639: yul 'di zhes gud du bcad pa med pas /
NK109(dze)002:3640: kun tu brtags ba'i ma rig pa med pas ka dag pa'i gzhis ni /
NK109(dze)002:3641: re shig tshig tsam du gtan la phab na /
NK109(dze)002:3642: ngo bo ka dag gi ye shes su bzhugs pas 'khrul pa'i phyogs su ma lhung la /
NK109(dze)002:3643: de yang gang zag gi rgyud la mtshon du btub pas rgya gar yang ma chad /
NK109(dze)002:3644: rang bzhin kyi cha nas yon tan lhun grub kyi
NK109(dze)002:3645: ye shes su bzhugs bas skyon gyi phyogs su ma
NK109(dze)002:3646: lhung la / 'di nyid 'khor 'das thams cad la khyab pas rgya gar yang ma chad la /
NK109(dze)002:3647: thugs rje kun gyi ye shes su bzhugs pas 'khor 'das gnyis ka'i phyogs su ma lhung la /
NK109(dze)002:3648: 'di nyid kyi gdul bya'i yul tha dad pa la /
NK109(dze)002:3649: 'dul byed kyi sku tha dad pa ltar snang bas rgya gar yang ma chad pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3650: de ltar rgya chad phyogs lhung med pa'i gzhis de /
NK109(dze)002:3651: 'dug tshul rang dag gi ngos nas ngo bor la bzhugs pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:3652: dper na gud bcad nas nam mkha' tha dad pa
NK109(dze)002:3653: rnams nam mkha'i ngo bor gcig pa bzhin du bzhugs
NK109(dze)002:3654: la / chos nyid sgyu ma lta bu'i sgo nas rang bzhin du bzhugs te /
NK109(dze)002:3655: dper na nam mkha' gcig la nyi ma stong shar
NK109(dze)002:3656: yang 'od gcig las dbyer mi phyed pa dang mtshungs
NK109(dze)002:3657: / mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyi cha nas thugs rjer bzhugs te /
NK109(dze)002:3658: dper na 'dus pa gcig pa gru gang gi mi dang 'dra'o //
NK109(dze)002:3659: yang ngo bo ni ka dag pa'i ye shes rab snang la /
NK109(dze)002:3660: sgrib phyogs thams cad bral ba /
NK109(dze)002:3661: spros pa rnams kyis ma spros zhing zang thal 'gags med kyi ngo bor bzhugs la /
NK109(dze)002:3662: mkhyen pa'i ye shes ma 'gag pa'i sgo nas sku'i tha snyad tsam du bzhugs la /
NK109(dze)002:3663: ngo bo zang thal ba'i ngos nas cir yang grub pa med /
NK109(dze)002:3664: spros bral phyogs su ma lhung ba'i sgo nas gang ltar yang shar ba /
NK109(dze)002:3665: de yang ngo bo ka dag gi ye shes su bzhugs pas 'khrul pa'i phyogs su ma lhung ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:3666: shes bya rang gi 'dug tshul kyi sgo nas gang gis kyang thog tu mi phebs la /
NK109(dze)002:3667: chos nyid gzhi la rnam par dag pa'i sgo nas
NK109(dze)002:3668: thams cad kyi 'byung khungs su yang mtshon du btub
NK109(dze)002:3669: / nyag gcig spros pa dang bral ba'i sgo nas
NK109(dze)002:3670: 'di ltar yin no ba'i spros pa mtha' dag dang
NK109(dze)002:3672: des na ngo bo rnam dag zang thal ba zhes bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:3673: rang bzhin ni sna tshogs 'gags pa med pa'i cha nas snang bar yang shar la /
NK109(dze)002:3674: chos sku rang snang gi sgo nas mkhyen pa'i ye shes su tsam du yang gsal /
NK109(dze)002:3675: ye shes lnga'i mkhyen pa'i sgo ma 'gag pa'i cha nas rang gdangs 'od tsam du snang la /
NK109(dze)002:3676: mtshan ma spros gzhi nye bar zhi ba'i sgo nas kha dog tsam du yang snang du btub /
NK109(dze)002:3677: yul rkyen gang la yang ma ltos pa'i sgo nas
NK109(dze)002:3678: snang ba ci'i ngo bor yang grub rgyu med la
NK109(dze)002:3679: / thabs kyi sgo yangs pa'i cha nas tshig sna tshogs pa ltar yang byung /
NK109(dze)002:3680: ngo bo spros pa dang bral ba'i cha nas brjod bya gang gis kyang thog tu mi phebs la /
NK109(dze)002:3681: rang bzhin snang ba'i cha nas skyon yon thams cad las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3682: de yang 'og nas rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i snang ba ni gsal dwangs zhes pas bstan /
NK109(dze)002:3683: thugs rje ni ngo bo bya byed las 'das pa'i
NK109(dze)002:3684: cha nas mdzad pa gang du yang grub pa med
NK109(dze)002:3685: la / rang bzhin snang lugs kyi sgo nas mdzad
NK109(dze)002:3686: pa med pa'i thugs rje phyogs mtha' dag tu shar
NK109(dze)002:3687: la / la / ngo bo ka dag pa'i ye
NK109(dze)002:3688: shes la 'char rgyu ci yang grub pa med do
NK109(dze)002:3689: la / la / // mdzad pa rnam sprul kyi
NK109(dze)002:3690: sgo nas thub pa drug la sogs te sku tha
NK109(dze)002:3692: rang bzhin rnam dag gi sgo nas gdul bya gang du yang grub pa med do //
NK109(dze)002:3693: nyon mongs zhi dag gi sgo nas gdul bya tha dad par shar la /
NK109(dze)002:3694: chos nyid zab pa'i cha nas rnam rtog gi yul thams cad las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3695: rang shugs 'gags med kyi sgo nas 'dul byed kyi sku sna tshogs par sprul par snang ba la /
NK109(dze)002:3696: chos kun rang tha dad par shar la /
NK109(dze)002:3697: chos nyid zab pa'i cha nas rnam rtog gi yul thams cad las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3698: rang shugs 'gags med kyi sgo nas 'dul byed kyi sku sna tshogs par sprul par snang ba la /
NK109(dze)002:3699: chos kun rang dag pa nyid la mdzad pa ci yang med do //
NK109(dze)002:3700: yang ngo bo ci'i ngo bor yang grub pa med la /
NK109(dze)002:3701: rang bzhin 'gags med du gsal ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3702: thugs rje sna tshogs su shar ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:3703: de yang ngo bo zang thal ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3704: ngo bo zang thal bas rang bzhin kun snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3705: rang bzhin kun snang bas thugs rje kun khyab pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3706: de ltar gnas pa'i da so so'i 'dug tshul la /
NK109(dze)002:3707: kha cig ye shes med par 'dod pa yod de /
NK109(dze)002:3708: 'di la ye shes med na yang bem po lta bu'i skyon du 'gyur la /
NK109(dze)002:3709: yang na stong pa nam mkha' lta bu ste /
NK109(dze)002:3710: nam mkhar nyid da so so gshis yin na de
NK109(dze)002:3711: nyid mthong ba dang shes pas rtogs pa yin nam
NK109(dze)002:3713: rtogs mi dgos par de nyid rang yin /
NK109(dze)002:3714: dang po mthong bas chog na sems can thams cad
NK109(dze)002:3715: kyi nam mkha' mthong ba dang shes pa'i phyir grol
NK109(dze)002:3716: bar 'gyur te / 'di ni phyi rol chad par
NK109(dze)002:3717: smra ba rnams dang khyad par ci yang byed do
NK109(dze)002:3718: bar 'gyur te / // sgom dgos pa yin na goms lugs ji ltar goms par byed /
NK109(dze)002:3719: 'di ka ltar yin na nam mkha' nyid kyis nyid goms pas gang zag la phan ba med la /
NK109(dze)002:3720: gang zag gis goms pas 'byongs pa'i ngo bo med pas /
NK109(dze)002:3721: gal te dbang sgyur bar byed na ni 'dab chags rnams su gol bar 'gyur bas /
NK109(dze)002:3722: byol song du slar skye bas bskyed pa'i phyir dang /
NK109(dze)002:3723: 'di la goms pa'i don med par 'gyur ba skyon spang bar mi nus so //
NK109(dze)002:3724: rtogs mi dgos na sems med par ye grol ba yin te /
NK109(dze)002:3725: tha mal pa rnams dang khyad par ci yang med do //
NK109(dze)002:3726: 'di ni de ltar ma yin te ngo bo'i cha nas grub rgyu ci yang med par snang la /
NK109(dze)002:3727: rang bzhin rnam dag gi ngos nas ye shes du mar snang la /
NK109(dze)002:3728: thugs rje yon tan gyi phyogs nas mkhyen pa'i ye shes ma 'gags par shar ba ste /
NK109(dze)002:3729: de yang ngo bo la gzhi gnas kyi ye shes cha la gsal bas /
NK109(dze)002:3730: mkhyen pa nang gsal du yod pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3731: rang bzhin la mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i ye shes lnga
NK109(dze)002:3732: rtsal du snang bas mkhyen pa yul du ma byed
NK109(dze)002:3733: pa dang / thugs rje la shes bya rang rtsal gyi ye shes ma 'gags pas //
NK109(dze)002:3734: shes bya ji lta ba mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis dngos po'i gnas lugs mkhyen pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3735: shes bya ji snyed pa mkhyen pa'i ye shes kyis
NK109(dze)002:3736: gdul bya'i bsam pa mkhyen pa gnyis kyi yul la
NK109(dze)002:3737: snang ba ma 'gag par mkhyen tshul shar ba ni
NK109(dze)002:3738: / ye shes thams cad kyi ngo bo la g.yos pa med kyang /
NK109(dze)002:3739: rang bzhin gsal cha ma 'gags pa'i cha nas 'od du gsal /
NK109(dze)002:3740: thugs rje la mkhyen pa'i ye shes gnyis rtsal du snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:3741: de'i phyir na ngo bo ka dag pa'i ye shes su zang thal ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3742: de nyid zang thal bas rang bzhin lhun grub kyi snang ba tsam du yang snang la /
NK109(dze)002:3743: de nyid lhun grub kyi cha ma 'gags pas thugs
NK109(dze)002:3744: rje mkhyen pa'i ye shes su gnyis gang la yang
NK109(dze)002:3746: de yang ngo bo la mkhyen pa rang gsal du rig pa tsam du bzhugs pas /
NK109(dze)002:3747: sku thams cad kyi bdag nyid las 'das pas zhal phyag gi rnam par grub pa med pas /
NK109(dze)002:3748: rig pa rang ngo rang dag tu bzhugs pas thugs
NK109(dze)002:3749: rje thams cad kyi bdag nyid du rang byung ba'o
NK109(dze)002:3750: // rang bzhin ni mkhyen rig yul la shar bas thugs thams cad kyi bdag nyid las 'das te /
NK109(dze)002:3751: rigs dang rigs kyi gtso 'khor kyi sku ye shes lnga'i rtsal du shar bas /
NK109(dze)002:3752: zhal phyag gi rnam pa sku thams cad kyi rang bzhin du gsal ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3753: thugs rje ma rtog pa rang dag gi zhal phyag
NK109(dze)002:3754: du med pas mkhyen rig gi rtsal phyi nas snang
NK109(dze)002:3755: ba 'ja' tshon lta bu'i sku las 'das pa dang
NK109(dze)002:3756: / rig pa rang ngo la mi gnas pas ye shes kyii mkhyen pa gnyis ma 'gags pas /
NK109(dze)002:3757: don gnyis thogs med du byed pas thugs las 'das te /
NK109(dze)002:3758: gsung rang byung gi yi ge drug longs sku'i mkhyen
NK109(dze)002:3759: pa'i ye shes de yab yum ljags kyi dbang po
NK109(dze)002:3760: 'phros pas // sprul pa nyid gang la gang 'dul ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3761: de dang de'i lus dang mthun par sprul nas gsung gis 'dul ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:3762: de'i 'dug tshul gyi kha nas tshig tsam du sku gsung thugs su yang mtshon du gtub pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:3763: gsung gis ye shes gnyis la brten nas gdul bya
NK109(dze)002:3764: ngag gi chos phyin ci ma log par byed pa
NK109(dze)002:3765: dang / sku mtshan nyid 'dzin pa'i ye shes lnga
NK109(dze)002:3766: la brten nas snang ba phyin ci ma log par
NK109(dze)002:3767: dang / byed pa dang / thugs kyi ngo bo'i
NK109(dze)002:3768: cha nas gzhi gnas kyii ye shes la brten nas
NK109(dze)002:3769: dgongs pa phyin ci log par byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3770: de ltar yin pa ni ngo bo la mdzad pa ma grub ste /
NK109(dze)002:3771: shes bya kha phyir ma bltas pas mkhyen pa rang ngo la gsal /
NK109(dze)002:3772: rang bzhin la mkhyen pa ma grub pas gdos bcas rags pa'i zhal phyag du med /
NK109(dze)002:3773: thugs rje la gnas pa ma grub pas nges pa
NK109(dze)002:3774: med pa'i thugs rje lhun grub las yon tan 'gag
NK109(dze)002:3776: de yang dngos po gshis dang sbyar na ngo bo stong par bzhugs pas /
NK109(dze)002:3777: rtag pa mthar 'dzin pa las rang log pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3778: rang bzhin gsal bar bzhugs pas chad pa'i mthar 'dzin pa las rang log pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3779: thugs rje khyab par bzhugs pas rtag chad gnyis dang gnyis ka ma yin pa las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3780: rang bzhin snang lugs dang sbyar na ngo bo ka
NK109(dze)002:3781: nas dag pas 'khrul pa dang ma 'khrul pa zhes
NK109(dze)002:3782: bya ba'i tha snyad du med pas rang dag pa'o
NK109(dze)002:3783: // rang bzhin rang snang bas sku dang ye shes kyi 'byung khungs yin pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3784: thugs rje kun 'byung bas gdul bya'i yul mi 'dra
NK109(dze)002:3785: ba tha dad pa las 'dul byed kyi sku yang
NK109(dze)002:3786: tha dad par sprul nas don byed pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3787: rang gi ngo bo dang sbyar na ngo bo ni rig pa ste rang gis rang rig pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3788: rang bzhin 'char tshul du bzhugs pas /
NK109(dze)002:3789: de las sku dang ye shes dang 'od dang thig le rnams su rang shar ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:3790: thugs rje 'char byed du bzhugs pas dbyings dang rig pa dang yul dang dbang por snang ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:3791: kun gzhi'i snang tshul dang sbyar na ngo bo sgron
NK109(dze)002:3792: ma bzhir bzhugs pas rang snang mngon gsum du spyod
NK109(dze)002:3793: / rang bzhin snang bar bzhugs pas dmigs gtad gang
NK109(dze)002:3794: la gtad kyang spros pa med pa'i nyams su myong
NK109(dze)002:3795: / ba skye // thugs rje yul du bzhugs pas
NK109(dze)002:3796: rang bzhin rdzogs pa chen po'i rnal 'byor pas tshogs
NK109(dze)002:3797: drug lhug pa nyid dam ji ltar spyod kyang rung
NK109(dze)002:3799: rnam rtog bag chags dang sbyar na ngo bo sems
NK109(dze)002:3800: su bzhugs pas byung tshor ji ltar skyes kyang rang
NK109(dze)002:3801: bzhin gyi bsam gtan la gnas pa dang //
NK109(dze)002:3802: rang bzhin ngag tu bzhugs pas ci brjod pa sngags tshig tu 'byung ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3803: thugs rje lus su bzhugs pas bsgul skyod phyag rgyar gsal ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:3804: rig pa rang ngo dang sbyar na /
NK109(dze)002:3805: rig pa stong pa'i cha nas ngo bor bzhugs pas mtshan ma'i chos las grol ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3806: gsal ba'i cha rang bzhin du bzhugs pas stong pa phyang chad grol ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3807: thugs rje byas spyod du bzhugs pas rig pa rdo
NK109(dze)002:3808: rje lu gu rgyud kyi sku nyid dbugs med pa'i
NK109(dze)002:3812: ma zlum pa'i thig le dang /
NK109(dze)002:3814: rang la gnas pa dang sbyar na /
NK109(dze)002:3815: ngo bo tsi ta na zhi ba'i sku lnga dang /
NK109(dze)002:3816: dung khang khro bo'i sku lnga lnga yab yum gyi tshul du bzhugs la /
NK109(dze)002:3817: rang bzhin thig le'i rtsa gnas kyi nang na rang bzhin gyi thig le dang /
NK109(dze)002:3820: dbyings rnam par dag pa'i thig le dang /
NK109(dze)002:3821: chos nyid kyi thig le dang /
NK109(dze)002:3822: gzhi dang lam gyi thig le dang /
NK109(dze)002:3823: don dam dang kun rdzob kyi thig ler bzhugs pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3824: thugs rje 'od du bzhugs pa ni ye shes lnga'i
NK109(dze)002:3825: rang snang 'od lnga dang ye shes nyer lnga'i 'od
NK109(dze)002:3826: nyer lngar snang ba ni mi gnas shar ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:3827: thabs ldan man ngag dang sbyar na /
NK109(dze)002:3828: ngo bo spros pa dang bral ba'i byang chub kyi sems su bzhugs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3837: snying rje med pa bskal pa las kyi rlung rnams su bzhugs pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3838: thugs rje thig ler bzhugs pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3839: kun rdzob rgyu'i thig le pha ma'i byang sems dang /
NK109(dze)002:3840: don dam chos nyid kyi thig le sgron bzhir gnas pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3841: nyams myong goms shugs dang sbyar na /
NK109(dze)002:3842: ngo bo drod du bzhugs pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3843: rig pa tshad la phebs pas snang ba gang la yang yid mi 'jug pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3844: rang bzhin nyams su bzhugs pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3845: nyams su myong ba phyogs med du shar bas lus
NK109(dze)002:3846: ngag gi bya ba ci byed kyang rkyen ngan grogs
NK109(dze)002:3847: su 'char pa'o // thugs rje rtags su bzhugs pa
NK109(dze)002:3848: ni de ltar goms pa las rig pa tshad la
NK109(dze)002:3849: su 'char pa'o // phebs te / nyams rgyud la shar bas /
NK109(dze)002:3850: lus la 'byung ba'i gnod pas mi tshugs pas /
NK109(dze)002:3851: zas dang gos bral ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3852: skra dkar dang gnyer ma med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3853: rang bzhin kyi snum bag dang ldan pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3854: lus yangs shing 'bu srin med pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3855: skra dang sen mo skye ba'i rgyun chad pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3858: ri brag la zang thal du la sogs pa 'dod pa med kyang rang bzhin gyis 'byung ba ni //
NK109(dze)002:3859: sa bon nas myu gu 'byung ba ni sus kyang dgag bar mi nus par rang 'byung ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3860: bud med sbrum ma zla ba rdzogs nas sus kyang dgag par mi nus par btsal ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3861: nam zla zad pa'i dus kyi rtsi thog sus kyang gsos pas mi 'tsho bar rang skam pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3862: nam zla zhus na chab rom sus kyang dgongs pas mi 'phongs bar rag 'ju ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3863: skyes bu 'byung ba rnying pa ste rgas pa'i dus
NK109(dze)002:3864: na shes pas mi spongs par stobs rang nyams pa
NK109(dze)002:3865: dang / sprin mthong nas thon pa'i nyi ma sus
NK109(dze)002:3866: kyang dgag mi nus par rang snang ba lta bur
NK109(dze)002:3867: 'dod pa med kyang 'byung ba yin no //
NK109(dze)002:3868: de ltar dngos po 'dug tshul de nyid kyang gzhan las ma yin te /
NK109(dze)002:3869: yo ga'i rgyud la gnas pas nyams su blang du btub pas na /
NK109(dze)002:3871: da ltar gnas pas rig pa rdo rje lu gu rgyud kyi sku rlung dang phral te /
NK109(dze)002:3872: thabs dal bar bzung bas 'gro 'og rgyun chad pas /
NK109(dze)002:3873: las kyi rlung dang ye shes kyi rlung gnyis ka
NK109(dze)002:3874: bral bas snang ba'i 'phel bsam gyis mi khyab par
NK109(dze)002:3875: snang ba'o // lta ba mkha' khyab kyi gdam ngag bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3876: de ltar dngos po gshis kyi 'dug tshul nyid rnal
NK109(dze)002:3877: 'byor bas nyams su blang pas rig pa skye med
NK109(dze)002:3878: du rang smin / der smin pas da 'chi ba
NK109(dze)002:3879: med par rdzogs pas skye shi med par dbyings thams
NK109(dze)002:3880: cad gcig tu 'brel pa ste 'di ltar 'dod pas
NK109(dze)002:3881: du rang smin / / dbyings stong gsal gnyis med
NK109(dze)002:3882: du gnas pa la rnam par rtog pa yul can
NK109(dze)002:3883: dri ma tha dad pa rnams rang bzhin gyis dag
NK109(dze)002:3884: pa'am sgron mas 'khor ba'i mun pa sel bar byed
NK109(dze)002:3885: pa ste dper na ri rab kyi 'gul nas nyi
NK109(dze)002:3886: ma shar pas rang bzhin gyis mun pa sel ba
NK109(dze)002:3887: du rang smin / / dang 'dra'o // de nyid
NK109(dze)002:3888: la ma yengs par ltos shig ces pa de la
NK109(dze)002:3889: blta ba'i thabs lus ngag yid kyi gnad gsum mo
NK109(dze)002:3890: du rang smin / / dang 'dra'o // // 'khrul snang rgyas 'debs kyi man ngag bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3891: grogs ni rnal 'byor ba'i grogs dud 'gro dang mi gzhan dag med par dang /
NK109(dze)002:3892: ye shes kyi grogs ma rig pa dang nyon mongs
NK109(dze)002:3893: pa dang bag chags snga phyi med par rnal 'byor
NK109(dze)002:3894: ba'i lus gcig pur dal ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3895: ngag gcig pur smra ba gcad pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3896: yid gcig pur te sgron me la gtad pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:3897: rig pa gcig pur 'byung ba'i rkyen dang bral ba la 'dug par nges par 'dod na /
NK109(dze)002:3898: snang ba 'di shes la dpyad byed ma zhugs pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:3899: dper na gzu po'i blo can lha khang du phyin pa lta bu dang /
NK109(dze)002:3900: skyes bu'i gang slob pa'i yon tan 'byongs pas bslab
NK109(dze)002:3901: bya dang bral ba lta bu cer bzhag du bzhag
NK109(dze)002:3902: pas dgongs pa las ma bral bar gnas pa yin
NK109(dze)002:3903: te // de ltar gyis gshis sngon 'byung du ston pas gdams la rjes su bla mas gdams pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3904: rang dag nyams gong du 'phel ba'i snang ba la
NK109(dze)002:3905: cer bzhag du bzhag pas chos nyid bcos pa med
NK109(dze)002:3906: pa'i dgongs pa dang ma bral bar sangs rgyas pa
NK109(dze)002:3907: yin pas de ltar gyis shig pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3908: 'ub chub rgyas 'debs kyi lta ba bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3909: lta ba rtsol ba dang bral ba med pa'i nyams
NK109(dze)002:3910: gong 'phel kyi sku la mig gis blta bar 'dod
NK109(dze)002:3911: na skal ldan gyis cig pa ni dngos po'i bzhugs
NK109(dze)002:3912: tshul gcig ma grub pas du ma med la /
NK109(dze)002:3913: du ma'i spros pa dang bral bas gcig ma grub la /
NK109(dze)002:3914: gcig dang du ma dang bral bas na thig mi
NK109(dze)002:3915: 'gyur ba dang le rang bzhin gyis brdal ba'i gnas
NK109(dze)002:3916: mig gi de kho na nyid rig pa nyid mi
NK109(dze)002:3917: 'gyur ba dper na ri mo lta ba yul nam
NK109(dze)002:3918: mkha' la cog gis gzhag pa ni ma bcos par
NK109(dze)002:3919: bla ma dag pa'i man ngag bstan pa'i thabs la
NK109(dze)002:3920: mtha' ma spros par gnyis med du bsdus gcig ces
NK109(dze)002:3921: gdams pa'o // 'gro drug rang gzhag gi man ngag bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3922: rkang pa ni 'gro ba dang bskyod pa'i don byed
NK109(dze)002:3923: pa yin pas de med pa ni de so so
NK109(dze)002:3924: gdos bcas ming du grags pa'i rkang pa rig pa
NK109(dze)002:3925: la med de / rang gi ye shes kyi rlung
NK109(dze)002:3926: gi stobs la brten nas nam mkha' rnam par dag
NK109(dze)002:3927: pa la rig pa'i ye shes 'gro ba ste /
NK109(dze)002:3928: de nyid la reg pa gsal ba las ma g.yos
NK109(dze)002:3929: par gnas nas cog gis de'i don la ma 'gyur
NK109(dze)002:3930: bar bzhag pa'i thabs kyi man ngag tu mi 'gul
NK109(dze)002:3932: rtsal rig pa tshad la phebs pa 'byongs pas te /
NK109(dze)002:3933: de nyid tshad la phebs pas rnal 'byor pa de
NK109(dze)002:3934: rkang pa'i rtsol bas bskyod mi dgos par nam mkha'
NK109(dze)002:3935: la 'gro ba dag kyang 'dod pa med kyang 'byung
NK109(dze)002:3936: bas na / sbyongs shig ces gdams pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3937: 'khor 'das rang yan kyi ting nge 'dzin bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3938: phyi nang med par zhes pa ni phyi nas ltas na nang gsal /
NK109(dze)002:3939: nang nas bltas pas phyi gsal ba dper na skyu
NK109(dze)002:3940: ru ra rlon pa lag mthil du bzhag pa lta
NK109(dze)002:3941: bu chos thams cad kyang thal bar rtogs pa ni
NK109(dze)002:3942: / rgya mtsho'i gting ltar lus dag la g.yo 'gul
NK109(dze)002:3943: med par cog gis bzhag pas chos nyid bsam dang
NK109(dze)002:3944: bral ba'i dgongs pa la rtag tu gnas pa yin
NK109(dze)002:3945: / te / 'di la gnas pas bsam pa'i 'phro
NK109(dze)002:3946: 'du rab tu chod pa'i dus na ri brag dang
NK109(dze)002:3947: rtsig pa la sogs pa la phyi nang du mi
NK109(dze)002:3948: snang bar lus kyis kyang thal bar rgyu bar byung
NK109(dze)002:3949: / te / ba ni / 'dod pa med kyang 'byung bas na /
NK109(dze)002:3950: de nyid gnas par gyis shes gdams pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3951: gzung 'dzin rbad chod kyi ye shes ston pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3952: ye shes zang thal ba chos kyi sku thig le
NK109(dze)002:3953: nyag gcig ma spangs la yongs su rdzogs pa'i dgongs
NK109(dze)002:3954: pa dus gsum du gnas pa la bya /
NK109(dze)002:3955: gong du bstan pa'i cog bzhag bzhi'i don rgyud bzhi
NK109(dze)002:3956: lam khyer gyis gdams ngag nyid las ma 'das par
NK109(dze)002:3957: rtse gcig tu sems kyis spros med zang thal kyi
NK109(dze)002:3958: don 'dod pa med kyang khong du tshud par 'gyur
NK109(dze)002:3959: bas de nyid las ma 'das gcig /
NK109(dze)002:3961: 'khor ba g.yul zlog gi sangs rgyas bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:3962: 'khrul pa ni rgyu ma rig pa rnam pa gsum dang /
NK109(dze)002:3963: rkyen bzhi dang ldan pas gcig nas gcig tu 'khrul
NK109(dze)002:3964: zhing 'khor ba dang 'khrul pa'i snang ba de ma
NK109(dze)002:3965: yin la der 'dzin kyi shes pa ste //
NK109(dze)002:3966: dper na skyes bu nam ma dag pa la sgor
NK109(dze)002:3967: thon bas sgo na thag pa gcig yin pa la
NK109(dze)002:3968: dug sbrul du mthong nas sngangs te log pa dang
NK109(dze)002:3969: 'dra bar de ma yin la der 'dzin du bzung
NK109(dze)002:3970: ba'o // de yang dper na grur bzhugs pa'i dbang po dang /
NK109(dze)002:3972: tho yor la mir bzung ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:3973: smig rgyu la chur bzung ba ni bzung ba'i yul de ma yin pas 'khrul pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3974: phyin ci log las 'khrul pa ni shes pa 'khrul pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:3975: mig nad dang ldan pa'i skyes bu'i dbang po la nam mkha' la skra shad 'dzag par snang ba'am /
NK109(dze)002:3976: bar snang la bal gyi 'khor lo 'bab par mthong
NK109(dze)002:3977: ba ni shes pa phyin ci log tu gyur pas
NK109(dze)002:3979: dbang po 'khrul pas shes pa 'khrul lo //
NK109(dze)002:3980: zhen pa'i yul las 'khrul pa ni /
