NK109(dze)002:3981: sngar zhen pa'i stobs kyi gang 'dris pa rmi lam gyi rnam pa ltar snang ba ni 'khrul pa /
NK109(dze)002:3982: zhen pa'i yul kun rdzob kyi rnam pa tsam ste
NK109(dze)002:3983: yang dag ma yin pa las yang dag tu bzung
NK109(dze)002:3984: ba dang 'dzin cing chags pas 'khrul lo //
NK109(dze)002:3985: de ltar 'khrul pa'i snang ba rnams sangs rgyas kyi
NK109(dze)002:3986: zhing khams su 'char bar 'dod pa'i skal ldan gyis
NK109(dze)002:3987: // sgron ma dbyings rnam par dag pa dang rig
NK109(dze)002:3988: pa lu gu rgyud dang gnyis dus thams cad du
NK109(dze)002:3989: ma bral bar gyis shig ces gdams pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3990: da ni rgyud bzhi lam du byas pas skye ba
NK109(dze)002:3991: med pa'i don ye nas yod pa la thabs sngon
NK109(dze)002:3993: rjes 'jug tu bla mas skal ldan la thun mong ma yin par mchog tu gsungs pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:3994: don gnyis pa rig pa snang ba'i dri ma gdams
NK109(dze)002:3995: ngag gi dag par bstan pa la don drug gi
NK109(dze)002:3996: bstan pa'i dang po kun gzhi cig char gyi gdams
NK109(dze)002:3998: e ma ho zhes rang la rang ngo mtshar ba'i tshig tu byung ste /
NK109(dze)002:3999: dngos po ni sa chu me rlung gi dngos po
NK109(dze)002:4000: sgo lnga'i yul zhen pa dang bcas pa med pa'i
NK109(dze)002:4001: snang ba ni dngos po'i 'dug tshul la gnyis kyi
NK109(dze)002:4002: dang po ngo bo ka dag gi snang ba gong
NK109(dze)002:4003: du bstan la / rang bzhin lhun grub ni gzhi
NK109(dze)002:4004: dang gzhi'i shes pa'i khyad par las 'khrul ba 'byung
NK109(dze)002:4005: ba'i gzhi lhun grub skyon gyi rnam par shar la
NK109(dze)002:4006: du bstan la / / rol pa 'gags pa med
NK109(dze)002:4007: pa'i ngos nas yon tan sna tshogs par shar te
NK109(dze)002:4008: du bstan la / / / 'khrul gzhis rtsis dang
NK109(dze)002:4009: bstun na sngon rol du rang rig pa'i rtsal yon
NK109(dze)002:4011: sems kyi byung tshor 'dus pas nga las pha gi
NK109(dze)002:4012: byung ngam pha gi las nga byung snyam pa'i snyam
NK109(dze)002:4014: rang gi de ma dag pa las skyon sa chu me rlung nam mkha'i 'byung bar byung la /
NK109(dze)002:4015: 'khrul ba ldog pa'i sgo nas 'byung lnga ma spangs pas skyon yon du shar bas /
NK109(dze)002:4016: skyon btsal du ma rnyed pas 'khrul pa rang log la /
NK109(dze)002:4017: yon tan bsgrub tu ma rnyed pas 'khrul pa dang ma 'khrul gnyis las 'das pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:4018: yang 'khrul pa 'jug tshul la lhun grub gdags bya ma 'gags bas sku ltar shar la /
NK109(dze)002:4019: de nyid yon tan du ma shes pas 'gro ba rigs drug gi lus tha dad par 'khrul la /
NK109(dze)002:4020: 'khrul ba ldog tshul kyii cha nas 'gro ba ye
NK109(dze)002:4021: sangs rgyas pas skyon nyid yon tan du shar te
NK109(dze)002:4022: / rkyen grogs su shar bas ye nas skyon yon rang dag du grol ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:4023: lhun grub rtsal snang gi ngos nas ye shes ltar 'char bas /
NK109(dze)002:4024: 'khrul pa 'jug tshul gyi nyon mongs lnga skyon gyi rnam par dag 'khrul la //
NK109(dze)002:4025: lhun grub gcig char du 'khrul pa ldog ba'i rtsal las rang ga ma rang gzhag du snang bas /
NK109(dze)002:4026: skyon yon tan du log nas bar dngos chad grub tu gyur pas /
NK109(dze)002:4027: bar du gcod pa'i bdud na nyon mongs pa ma rnyed pas /
NK109(dze)002:4028: skyon rtsal du ma rnyed pas /
NK109(dze)002:4029: ye shes bzhi sbyor du zang thal ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:4030: lhun grub snang tshul gyi cha las gnyis med du shar ba las /
NK109(dze)002:4031: 'khrul ba 'jug tshul la bdag gzhan gnyis su byung la /
NK109(dze)002:4032: 'khrul ba ldog tshul ltar na bdag gzhan gnyis ma bcos par rang bzhag pas /
NK109(dze)002:4033: bdag med stong pa'i yon tan du grub pas skyon
NK109(dze)002:4034: rtsal du ma rnyed de 'khor 'das gnyis med du
NK109(dze)002:4035: sangs rgyas pa'o // yang lhun grub snang tshul las mtha' grol ltar shar la /
NK109(dze)002:4036: 'khor ba 'jug tshul ltar rtog mtha' skyon du mar 'khrul pas /
NK109(dze)002:4037: de nyid bzlog tshul ltar na mtha' gnyis dbus su gyur nas skyon yon tan du shar pas /
NK109(dze)002:4038: 'khrul pa ye shes su rang dag nas sangs rgyas ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:4039: yang lhun grub yon tan gyi cha nas dag pa ye shes kyi sgor byung la /
NK109(dze)002:4040: 'khor ba 'jug tshul ltar na ma dag pa 'khrul par snang ste /
NK109(dze)002:4041: 'khrul pa ldog tshul ltar na ma spangs gnas dag tu grol nas sangs rgya'o //
NK109(dze)002:4042: de yang ngo bo ka dag spros pa dang bral ba la /
NK109(dze)002:4043: lhun grub yon tan rdzogs tshul du byung la /
NK109(dze)002:4044: ma rtogs pa rnams la skyon lhun gyis grub par byung ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:4045: 'di la thim lugs brgyad dang dpe brgyad la sogs pa ci rigs par spro'o //
NK109(dze)002:4046: ye shes phyogs dag gi snang ba ni nyams su blangs pa'i stobs las byung ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:4047: 'od dang thig le dang sku rnams kyi snang ba mngon gsum du gsal ba yin no //
NK109(dze)002:4048: de nyid sna tshogs par snang bas ngo mtshar che ba'o //
NK109(dze)002:4049: de nyid rags pa'i 'byung ba lngas bsgribs nas /
NK109(dze)002:4050: bla ma'i lung med pa'i gang zag skal med la snang ma nus so //
NK109(dze)002:4051: rang ga ma rgyas 'debs kyi man ngag bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:4052: rig pa rang snang gi snang ba ni sngon du
NK109(dze)002:4053: rig pa gtan la phabs pa mngon gsum pa dang
NK109(dze)002:4054: / nyams gong nas gong du 'phel ba'i snang ba bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:4055: rig pa tshad la phebs pa'i snang ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:4056: chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba ste /
NK109(dze)002:4057: lhun grub skyed pa'i rgyu las byung ba ste /
NK109(dze)002:4058: brjid pa ni so so'i rang gdangs yod pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:4059: de'i sgrib byed ni 'phra mo'i nyon mongs pa lngas
NK109(dze)002:4060: gdangs lnga la bsgribs nas nyams su ma blangs pa'i
NK109(dze)002:4061: skyes bu la thog ma bla mas bstan kyang brtags
NK109(dze)002:4062: ma thub ba'o // ye shes kun snang gi man ngag bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:4063: chos nyid ma bkod pa'i snang ba ni rang bzhin
NK109(dze)002:4064: 'byung lugs kyi snang ba 'di ltar snang ba dang
NK109(dze)002:4065: / byas pa med pa'i chos nyid kyi brdas bstan pa lus ngag yid sems kyi snang ba ni /
NK109(dze)002:4066: de nyid brtags pas bla ma'i man ngag tu shar ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:4067: chos nyid bcing pa med par snang ba de nyid
NK109(dze)002:4068: gsal bar snang ba dang thams cad chos nyid du
NK109(dze)002:4070: de rnams la shes pa tshud pa med par sna
NK109(dze)002:4071: tshogs du ma'i lus dang ngag dang yid sems kyi
NK109(dze)002:4073: de nyid la rtag ma thub pas snang ba de
NK109(dze)002:4074: dag mngon sum du yod kyang gang zag gis rig
NK109(dze)002:4075: pa'i mngon gsum du snang ma nus shing med pa'o
NK109(dze)002:4076: // de ltar snang ba gsum ni sku gsum gyi snang ba go rim gyis sbyar ro //
NK109(dze)002:4077: 'chi ka ma'i gcig rdzogs kyi gdams ngag bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:4078: de ltar snang ba gsum la snang ba'i yangs rig
NK109(dze)002:4079: pa'i ngo bo lu gu rgyud du gnas pas gcig
NK109(dze)002:4080: tu mi gnas gnas pas bzung bar dka' ste /
NK109(dze)002:4081: 'di nyid rnal du pheb pa dka' yang /
NK109(dze)002:4082: bla ma'i man ngag gi bcos na de nyid ye
NK109(dze)002:4083: shes rtsal yin pas lus dal bar gnas pas shes
NK109(dze)002:4084: pa gcig tu gnas pa'i gnad yod pas rnal 'byor
NK109(dze)002:4085: pas lus dal bar gnas pa gal che /
NK109(dze)002:4086: de ltar dal ba gsum gyis 'grub pa yin no //
NK109(dze)002:4087: zhing khams rang log kyi man ngag bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:4088: rig pa'i dbyings ni phyi'i nam mkha' mtha' dang dbus mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:4089: nang gi dbyings chos nyid rang bzhin gyis mi 'gyur ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:4090: gsang ba'i dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma dang /
NK109(dze)002:4091: 'du 'bral med pas mi 'gyur ba yin kyang /
NK109(dze)002:4092: rig pa rang gi stobs 'byung ba lnga'i rkyen dang
NK109(dze)002:4093: zad pas dbyings rig 'du 'bral med pa'i dgongs pa
NK109(dze)002:4095: snang ba ma bu sprad pa'i gdams ngag bstan pa ni /
NK109(dze)002:4096: de ltar rig pa'i rang bzhin 'gro ba kun la khyab kyang /
NK109(dze)002:4097: chos sku mngon gsum du rtogs pa bla ma'i gdams ngag mi shes te /
NK109(dze)002:4098: yid spyod kyi lus 'go 'jug tu rtsal kyang mi rnyed de /
NK109(dze)002:4099: 'o na de lus la med pa yin nam ste lus la gnas nges pa yin /
NK109(dze)002:4100: 'o na yid spyod kyis rtsal bas ma rnyed pas med pa min te /
NK109(dze)002:4101: khyod la bla ma'i man ngag med pas mi rnyed te /
NK109(dze)002:4102: dper na gser la bzo shes pas ci yang btub pa yin la /
NK109(dze)002:4103: bzo mi shes shing sbyong byed dang btso sreg gi
NK109(dze)002:4104: rnam pa ma shes pa'i skyes bus yid dpyod kyis
NK109(dze)002:4105: byas na ci yang mi btub pa rnams dang 'dra
NK109(dze)002:4106: ste / 'o na gser la ci yang mi btub pa ma yin te /
NK109(dze)002:4107: sbyongs byed la sogs pa'i man ngag yod pas ci yang btub pa dang 'dra bar /
NK109(dze)002:4108: bla ma'i man ngag med pas sangs rgya ba la re ba med do //
NK109(dze)002:4109: gal te yid spyod kyis btags shing dpyad pas rnyed
NK109(dze)002:4110: kyang de nyid la goms dgos pas brtan par mi
NK109(dze)002:4111: 'byung ste yin min ngo mi shes pa'i phyir ro
NK109(dze)002:4112: // des sngon du bla ma dag pa gal che /
NK109(dze)002:4113: de nas rang gis goms shing 'dres pa gal che'o //
NK109(dze)002:4114: gnyis 'dzoms pas skyes bu'i lag pa dang rtsub shing rang 'dzoms pas me 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK109(dze)002:4115: de yang me rtsub shing la yod pa ma yin /
NK109(dze)002:4116: skyes bu'i lag pa la yod pa yang ma yin /
NK109(dze)002:4117: lag pa dang rtsub shing dang rtsub brten dang gsum dus 'dzoms pas me 'byung ba dang 'dra ba'i //
NK109(dze)002:4118: chos nyid gnyis med du sangs rgyas pa yang rang
NK109(dze)002:4119: gi rig pa gcig pu la yod cing chog pa
NK109(dze)002:4120: ma yin / de bzhin du bla ma gcig pus chog pa ma yin /
NK109(dze)002:4121: bdag gi goms pa gcig pu ma yin /
NK109(dze)002:4122: gsum 'dzom pas sangs rgya bar nges pa yin no //
NK109(dze)002:4123: zhes yi ge med pa'i rgyud ni rang gi rig
NK109(dze)002:4124: pa de bla ma'i man ngag med pa la gsang
NK109(dze)002:4125: ba yin / yod pa la dngos grub chen po yin pa las /
NK109(dze)002:4126: le'u mtshan ni rdzogs pa'i 'byung bzhi'i 'dod yon la bslab pa'i gnad kyis bem po yang rdzogs la /
NK109(dze)002:4127: dbang po'i 'dod yon la bslab pa'i gnad kyis shes pas bsdus pa rnams kyang rdzogs pa chen po //
NK109(dze)002:4128: zhal ston pa'i kha chems phyi rabs la btsas su bstan pa ni rang tu zab pa ste /
NK109(dze)002:4129: dper na skyes bu 'chi ba dus byed pa'i tshe rang gi snying gi gtam smra ba dang /
NK109(dze)002:4131: rgyud 'di dus gcig las 'byung dka' bas na dkon par zung zhes pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:4132: le'u ni gzhung gi don nges par gcod pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:4134: drug kho nar nges pa ci'i phyir yang na bcu la sogs par mi ston pa /
NK109(dze)002:4135: yang na gcig ma yin par drug tu nges pa'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK109(dze)002:4137: thog ma la glengs na mi go bas gleng gzhi bstan la /
NK109(dze)002:4138: de nyid dgongs pa la dgongs par nges shes shig gnas pa dgongs gzhi'i le'ura nges la /
NK109(dze)002:4139: dgongs pa de rtsol bcas su song na rdzogs chen
NK109(dze)002:4140: ma yin pas gsum pa ma 'khrul pa'i rig pa
NK109(dze)002:4141: la ma byas pa'i chos bstan pa'i le'ura nges so
NK109(dze)002:4142: // de ltar ma byas shing ma 'khrul pa'i don
NK109(dze)002:4143: dam yin pas bzhi ba don dam snang ba'i le'ura
NK109(dze)002:4144: // nges la / don dam pa de la tshig dang yi ge'i spros pa dang bral bas /
NK109(dze)002:4145: le'u lnga pa rdzogs pa chen po tshig gis gol bar bstan pas nges /
NK109(dze)002:4146: tshig dang yi ge med pa de'i don gdams pa
NK109(dze)002:4147: zhal chems kyis dgongs pa gzhi'i don mthar sdud nan
NK109(dze)002:4148: cig dang bcas pa bstan pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:4149: grangs ni de las nyung na dgongs pa ma tshang bas rgyu ma yin pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:4150: de las mang na mi dgos pas ldab pa'i skyon du 'gyur bas drug kho nar nges pa'o //
NK109(dze)002:4151: gnas lugs ni ka dag dang lhun grub las byung ba'i rig pa ston par byung la /
NK109(dze)002:4152: snang thabs ni gong gi snang ba gsum kyi tshul
NK109(dze)002:4153: du byung bas 'khor la smras pa ni ston pa
NK109(dze)002:4154: dang 'khor tha mi dad pas nyid la nyid ston
NK109(dze)002:4156: de ltar rgyud bzhi po gzhag thabs bzhi re dril nas bstan pa dang /
NK109(dze)002:4157: de yang mtshan gyi skabs su phyi nang gsang ba
NK109(dze)002:4158: yongs rdzogs bzhir bstan pa'i phyis ldabs pa'i skyon 'di
NK109(dze)002:4159: la med do // snang ba'i dus na lta ba
NK109(dze)002:4160: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i rgyud kyi rang bzhin
NK109(dze)002:4161: gnas pa'i bar do gtan la phab pa /
NK109(dze)002:4162: yi ge med pa'i rgyud shi ka ma'i bar do /
NK109(dze)002:4163: rin po che rgyal mtshan kyi rgyud yon tan 'gag pa med pas chos nyid kyi bar do //
NK109(dze)002:4164: rgyal po'i gdung mi 'gyur ba 'khor ba la chags
NK109(dze)002:4165: pas srid pa'i bar do gtan la phabs te bstan
NK109(dze)002:4166: pa'o // rgyud bzhi sku bzhi dang yang sbyar bar bya'o //
NK109(dze)002:4167: pad+ma kha 'byed gsang ba yi ge med pa'i rgyud
NK109(dze)002:4168: kyi tshig don pad+ma kha phye ba ltar bshad pa
NK109(dze)002:4169: mkhas pa chen po bye ma la mu tras mdzad
NK109(dze)002:4170: pa rdzogs so // phyi rabs las can de dang 'phrod par shog cig //
